NK034(ngi)003:0: gser yig can +aahmh'u +amo m+aum l+aam pyam t+aam +amo
NK034(ngi)003:1: h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah btags pas grol bar bstan pa bu
NK034(ngi)003:2: gcig gii gsang 'grel slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes
NK034(ngi)003:3: mdzad pa bzhugs so rgya yis srungs shig rgya rgya
NK034(ngi)003:5: bud d+ha sarba pu tra e kah gu ya pu
NK034(ngi)003:6: ri sam tan tra ar+tha ka la d+he sha n+aa
NK034(ngi)003:8: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig po /
NK034(ngi)003:9: gsang ba spyod pa sa bon gyi rgyud kyi don gsal bar bstan pa zhes bya ba /
NK034(ngi)003:10: bcom ldan 'das bya bral klong chen ka nas dag pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK034(ngi)003:11: ye nas snying po'i bcud bsdus pa'i //
NK034(ngi)003:12: sangs rgyas bye ba dung phyur gyi //
NK034(ngi)003:13: thugs kyi dgongs pa dag pa'i rgyud //
NK034(ngi)003:14: nam mkha' nyi zla lta bu la //
NK034(ngi)003:15: dgongs pa rang gsal dzo ki bdag /
NK034(ngi)003:16: bla ma nor bu 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:17: bya rtsol bral ba'i gsung la 'dud //
NK034(ngi)003:18: rang byung phrad chog bstan pa'i btsas //
NK034(ngi)003:19: gsang snying nyi ma snang byed kyi //
NK034(ngi)003:21: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig po'i rgyud 'di la spyi don bdun gyis bstan te /
NK034(ngi)003:22: le'u dang pos rgyud che ba'i yon tan bstan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:23: le'u gnyis pas rgyud 'dis sangs rgyas kyi gdung ji ltar spel ba bstan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:24: le'u gsum pas phyis ji ltar 'byung bar bstan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:25: le'u bzhi pas tshe 'dir bsgom zhing nyams rtogs mthar phyin te zag pa med par bstan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:26: le'u lnga pas 'gro ba'i don du thun mong gi las bstan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:27: le'u drug pas btags pas grol ba'i snying po bstan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:28: le'u bdun pas rgyud 'di 'dus ma byas par bstan pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:29: de nas le'u dang po 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:30: dran pa kun gyi thog ma yi //
NK034(ngi)003:32: dran pa zhes pa mi dran dgu dran 'adi'o //
NK034(ngi)003:33: kun gyi zhes pa mi rig dgu rig rnams so //
NK034(ngi)003:34: thog ma'i zhes pa rtogs te sangs rgyas med /
NK034(ngi)003:35: ma rtogs te 'khor ba med de don las phyogs su ma lhung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:36: dngos mdzad sangs rgyas thog ma la //
NK034(ngi)003:38: dngos mdzad ces pa ngo bo ka dag dngos kyis mdzad /
NK034(ngi)003:39: rang bzhin lhun grub dngos kyis mdzad /
NK034(ngi)003:40: thugs rje kun khyab dngos kyis mdzad do //
NK034(ngi)003:42: ngo bo la gzung yul sangs te thig ler rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:43: rang bzhin la sgrib g.yogs sangs te sku ru rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:44: thugs rje la phyogs ris sangs te mkhyen pa rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:51: gnas kyi thog ma chos sku'i gnas chos kyi dbyings /
NK034(ngi)003:52: longs sku'i gnas rnam dag 'thug po bkod pa'i zhing /
NK034(ngi)003:53: sprul sku'i gnas tha dad ma nges te kun khyab bo //
NK034(ngi)003:54: ston pa'i thog ma kun tu bzang po /
NK034(ngi)003:55: longs sku'i ston pa rnam par snang mdzad gangs chen mtsho /
NK034(ngi)003:56: sprul sku'i ston pa rdo rje 'chang ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:57: 'khor gyi thog ma chos sku'i 'khor dran rig /
NK034(ngi)003:59: sprul sku'i 'khor sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:60: bstan pa'i thog ma chos sku'i bstan pa chos nyid mtha' bral /
NK034(ngi)003:61: longs sku'i bstan pa chos nyid rang sgra sangs rgyas sras gcig po /
NK034(ngi)003:62: sprul sku'i bstan pa sgra thal 'gyur rtsa ba'i rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:63: dus kyi thog ma chos sku'i dus 'das pa /
NK034(ngi)003:66: dang po nyid du phyag 'tshal lo //
NK034(ngi)003:68: dang po zhes pas thog ma lnga la /
NK034(ngi)003:69: nyid du zhes pa 'khrul ma myongs pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:70: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa dang po rdo rje 'chang gis ye phyag tu btsal /
NK034(ngi)003:71: de nas sangs rgyas rnams kyis rim pa bzhin gyis phyag mdzad /
NK034(ngi)003:72: da lta dzo ki bdag ye shes 'khrul ma myong ba'i rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig la /
NK034(ngi)003:73: lus ngag yid gsum phyag 'tshal lo //
NK034(ngi)003:80: 'di skad bdag la sogs pa yi //
NK034(ngi)003:82: 'di skad ces pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra /
NK034(ngi)003:85: rnam par snang mdzad gangs chen matsho'o //
NK034(ngi)003:88: gong ma gsum po mtha' med brjod las 'das pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:89: sangs rgyas bye ba dung phyur gyis //
NK034(ngi)003:91: sangs rgyas zhes pa gzung 'dzin sangs nas ka dag tu rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:92: bye ba dung phyur gyis zhes pa grangs so //
NK034(ngi)003:93: gong gis sogs kyi sde tshan no //
NK034(ngi)003:94: dgongs pa nyid dang grangs med par //
NK034(ngi)003:96: dgongs pa zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:98: grangs med par zhes pa bskal pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:99: thugs kyi snying po ji lta bar //
NK034(ngi)003:101: thugs kyi zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:103: ji lta bar zhes pa 'das ma 'ongs gsum dag tu /
NK034(ngi)003:104: gsungs shing bstan pa'i dus gcig na //
NK034(ngi)003:106: gsungs shing zhes pa chos nyid kyi sgra rang byung du /
NK034(ngi)003:107: bstan pa'i zhes pa rig pa'i rang bzhin lu gu rgyud du /
NK034(ngi)003:108: dus gcig na zhes pa chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:109: mya ngan 'das pa'i thog mar ni //
NK034(ngi)003:111: mya ngan zhes pa 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK034(ngi)003:112: 'das pa'i zhes bya ba sangs rgyas kyi bde ba /
NK034(ngi)003:113: thog mar ni zhes pa bde sdug gnyis kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:114: 'di ni nyag gcig rnal ma yin //
NK034(ngi)003:116: 'di ni zhes pa rang babs kyi rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:118: rnal ma yin zhes pa ma bcos pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:119: don gyi sa bon rnams su ni //
NK034(ngi)003:121: don gyi zhes pa yang dag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:122: sa bon ni sangs rgyas par byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:123: rnams su ni zhes thams cad du /
NK034(ngi)003:124: nges pa'i snying po nyid du yang //
NK034(ngi)003:126: nges pa'i zhes pa sangs rgya bar /
NK034(ngi)003:127: snying po ni chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:128: nyid du yang zhes pa bstan pa thams cad kyi bu gcig po'i rgyud 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:129: gsungs so bstan to bshad pa ni //
NK034(ngi)003:131: gsungs so ni chos nyid kyi sgra rang byung du /
NK034(ngi)003:132: bstan to ni sku dang gsung dang thugs ye zhes rang shar du /
NK034(ngi)003:133: bshad pa ni zhes pa byin rlabs rang babs su /
NK034(ngi)003:134: bstan pa'i gsung ni rgya mtsho kun //
NK034(ngi)003:136: bstan pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:137: gsung ni zhes pa 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa
NK034(ngi)003:138: mdor na theg pa dgu'i chos bsam las 'das pa'o
NK034(ngi)003:139: // rgya mtsho kun zhes pa gong ma'i gsung mtha' med brjod las 'das pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:140: la la gnas skabs yul don du //
NK034(ngi)003:143: gnas skabs zhes pa sems kyi skyid sdug /
NK034(ngi)003:144: yul don du zhes pa khams gsum sems can gyi don gsungs so //
NK034(ngi)003:149: 'jug don yin zhes pa sems can rnams chos la 'dzud pa'i don du gsungs so //
NK034(ngi)003:150: la la 'dul don tha dad nyid //
NK034(ngi)003:153: 'dul don zhes pa blo che chung gi sems can /
NK034(ngi)003:154: tha dad nyid ces pa theg pa'i mtho dman /
NK034(ngi)003:155: snying gi snying po tshig 'ga' las //
NK034(ngi)003:157: snying gi zhes pa chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:158: snying po zhes pa yang gsang bla med snying thig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:159: tshig 'ga' las zhes pa rgyud lung thams cad du gsungs kyang 'thor te go dka' /
NK034(ngi)003:160: kun gyis grub pa ma yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:162: kun gyis zhes pa theg pa thun mong ba'i chos /
NK034(ngi)003:163: grub pa zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:164: ma yin no zhes pa sangs rgyas nus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:165: bstan pa 'phel byed sa bon du //
NK034(ngi)003:167: bstan pa ni sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:168: 'phel byed ces pa grangs las 'das par /
NK034(ngi)003:169: sa bon du zhes pa rgyud 'adi'o //
NK034(ngi)003:170: ci ste zhes na btags pas sangs rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:174: thos pas sangs rgya bas so //
NK034(ngi)003:175: 'di kun bzhag cing byin brlabs las //
NK034(ngi)003:177: 'di kun zhes pa rgyud 'di'i tshig rnams so //
NK034(ngi)003:178: bzhag cing zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:179: byin brlabs las zhes pa sangs rgyas rnams kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:180: rang byung nyid du thugs las rdol //
NK034(ngi)003:182: rang byung ni byas pa med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK034(ngi)003:183: nyid du zhes pa skad cig ma /
NK034(ngi)003:184: thugs las rdol zhes pa rdo rje 'chang gi thugs /
NK034(ngi)003:185: kun bzang shes rig gi rgyal po las thig le rdol /
NK034(ngi)003:187: sku zhi khro las gsung rang byung bstan pa'i bu gcig rdol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:188: de phyir sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK034(ngi)003:190: de phyir zhes pa gong ltar rang babs su rdol ba /
NK034(ngi)003:191: sangs rgyas ni gong dang mtshungs /
NK034(ngi)003:192: thams cad kyi zhes pa sngar 'das pa /
NK034(ngi)003:195: thugs kyi sras ni gcig par yang //
NK034(ngi)003:197: thugs kyi zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:198: sras ni zhes pa rgyud 'dis sangs rgyas spel bas /
NK034(ngi)003:199: gcig par yang zhes pa bstan pa thams cad du gang sangs rgyas kyang 'di'i byin brlabs so //
NK034(ngi)003:202: rang byung chen po 'phel dang bcas //
NK034(ngi)003:204: rang byung zhes 'dus ma byas pa ni 'dus ma byas pa'i chos sku'i thig le nyag gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:205: chen po ni 'di'i gong na med pa'i yang rtse /
NK034(ngi)003:207: sangs rgyas kyi gdung 'di btags tshad sangs rgya ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:208: 'byung ba'i dgra dang bral bar gyur //
NK034(ngi)003:210: 'byung ba'i zhes pa sa chu me rlung gi /
NK034(ngi)003:211: dgra dang zhes pa gnod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:212: bral bar 'gyur zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:213: 'di ni bstan pa gang byung du //
NK034(ngi)003:216: bstan pa ni sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:217: gang byung du zhes pa mtha' med de /
NK034(ngi)003:220: 'od dang zhes pa mthing ka dkar ser dmar ljang sna tshogs par /
NK034(ngi)003:222: 'byung ba yin zhes pa byin brlabs rang babs su sngar byon /
NK034(ngi)003:226: gang la babs par gyur pa'i mi //
NK034(ngi)003:229: babs par zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:230: gyur pa'i mi zhes pa skal ldan te /
NK034(ngi)003:231: bstan pa kun gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK034(ngi)003:233: bstan pa zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:234: kun gyi zhes pa mtha' med brjod las 'das pa /
NK034(ngi)003:235: bdag por 'gyur zhes pa rgyud 'di thogs tshad /
NK034(ngi)003:236: bar dor 'di'i byin rlabs kyis sad byed byas nas /
NK034(ngi)003:237: rang ngo shes nas sangs rgyas te skad cig gcig la 'dzam bu'i gling bye ba phrag brgyar /
NK034(ngi)003:238: sprul pa'i sku bye ba phrag brgya dus gcig la 'gyed nus so //
NK034(ngi)003:239: 'di la ldem por bstan pa med //
NK034(ngi)003:241: 'di la zhes pa rgyud 'di'i tshig la /
NK034(ngi)003:242: ldem por zhes pa ldem rgyu dang po rgyu med
NK034(ngi)003:243: de thams cad rang byung chos nyid kyi rang sgra'o
NK034(ngi)003:244: // bstan pa med ces pa rdo rje 'chang la sogs pas /
NK034(ngi)003:245: sus kyang bshad cing nyan med par //
NK034(ngi)003:247: sus kyang zhes pa sangs rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:248: bshad cing zhes pa tshig tu /
NK034(ngi)003:250: rang byung dgongs pa klong rdol du //
NK034(ngi)003:252: rang byung zhes pa byas pa med pa'i sku dang ye shes /
NK034(ngi)003:253: dgongs pa zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:254: klong rdol du zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:255: nyi ma sprin las 'thon pa bzhin //
NK034(ngi)003:257: nyi ma ni ye shes lnga ldan gyi thig le /
NK034(ngi)003:258: sprin las zhes pa sems can las kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:259: 'thon pa bzhin zhes pa ni dpe ste /
NK034(ngi)003:260: 'khrul snang sangs nas ye shes su rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:261: sus kyang ma bsgribs rang byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:263: sus kyang zhes pa las dang bag chags ngan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:266: ma bsgribs zhes pa thig le /
NK034(ngi)003:267: rang byung ngo zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:270: 'di la zhes rgyud kyi don la /
NK034(ngi)003:271: 'byung bzhi'i zhes pa sa chu me rlung gi /
NK034(ngi)003:272: gnod med pas zhes pa ye nas /
NK034(ngi)003:273: sas mi non chus mi 'jig mes mi 'tshig rlung gis bskyod par mi nus so //
NK034(ngi)003:274: nam mkha' bdag la 'phar bar snang //
NK034(ngi)003:277: dbyings rgyan bu ga chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:278: dag la zhes pa thig le /
NK034(ngi)003:279: 'phar bar snang zhes pa gong nas gong mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:280: sangs rgyas 'bras bu sus thob pa //
NK034(ngi)003:282: sangs rgyas zhes pa nyon mongs pa sangs ye shes lnga rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:283: 'bras bu zhes pa gzhi ka dag go //
NK034(ngi)003:284: sus thob pa zhes pa skal ldan /
NK034(ngi)003:285: 'di nyid de las snang ba yin //
NK034(ngi)003:287: 'di nyid ces pa rgyud don thig le nyag gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:288: de las zhes pa rgyud btags pa'i byin rlabs las /
NK034(ngi)003:289: snang ba yin zhes pa bar dor sku gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:290: 'di ma mthong ba'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK034(ngi)003:292: 'di ma bcos pa rang byung gsum ste /
NK034(ngi)003:294: gsung rang byung bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:295: thugs rang byung thig le gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:296: mthong ba'i zhes pa sems ma bcos pas /
NK034(ngi)003:297: sangs rgyas ni zhes pa gang du /
NK034(ngi)003:298: gcig kyang 'byung ba snga phyir med //
NK034(ngi)003:300: gcig kyang zhes pa med pa'i tha tshig go //
NK034(ngi)003:301: 'byung srid kyang 'di dang phrad pa'i rtags so //
NK034(ngi)003:302: 'byung ba zhes pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:303: snga phyir med ces pa 'das ma 'ongs da lta gsum kar 'byung re kan no //
NK034(ngi)003:305: de phyir bstan pa rnams kyi btsas //
NK034(ngi)003:307: de phyir zhes pa rab tu dkon pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:308: bstan pa zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:309: rnams kyi zhes pa ma lus pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:311: sangs rgyas kun gyi sras gcig po //
NK034(ngi)003:313: sangs rgyas ni nyon mongs pa sangs ye shes rgyas pa la bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:314: kun gyi zhes pa ma lus pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:315: sras gcig po zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi gdung spel ba'i rgyud 'adi'o //
NK034(ngi)003:316: myang 'das thob pa'i sna thag yin //
NK034(ngi)003:318: myang 'das zhes pa sdug bsngal chos nyid du /
NK034(ngi)003:319: thob pa'i zhes pa bar dor /
NK034(ngi)003:320: sna thag yin ces pa rgyud 'dis 'gro ba sems
NK034(ngi)003:321: can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi sar 'khrid par byed
NK034(ngi)003:322: pas 'di dbugs la sleb pas chog go //
NK034(ngi)003:323: dgongs pa rang thog phebs pa yi //
NK034(ngi)003:325: dgongs pa ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:327: phebs pa'i zhes pa skad cig la /
NK034(ngi)003:328: gnad kyi tshig tu 'di nyid byung //
NK034(ngi)003:330: gnad kyi zhes pa chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:331: tshig tu zhes pa 'gro ba gang gi yang tshig dang yi ger /
NK034(ngi)003:332: 'di nyid byung zhes pa bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di rang babs su byon no //
NK034(ngi)003:333: 'jig rten khams ni gang du yang //
NK034(ngi)003:335: 'jig rten zhes pa 'jig chags can no //
NK034(ngi)003:336: khams ni 'byung ba lnga'i sems can dang bcas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:337: gang du yang zhes pa mtha' med de sprul sku'i zhing khams gang byung bar /
NK034(ngi)003:338: des thub pa'i zhing khams 'di dang mtshungs so //
NK034(ngi)003:339: sangs rgyas nyid ni sus thob pa //
NK034(ngi)003:341: sangs rgyas zhes pa nyon mongs pa sangs ye shes rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:342: nyid ni zhes pa skad cig la /
NK034(ngi)003:343: sus thob pa zhes pa 'gro ba skal ldan des /
NK034(ngi)003:344: de tshe 'di ni lan gsum du //
NK034(ngi)003:346: de tshe zhes pa 'gro ba skal ldan de la babs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:348: lan gsum du zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra
NK034(ngi)003:349: las sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i byang
NK034(ngi)003:351: da lta bkod par bgyid do //
NK034(ngi)003:353: zhes pa'i sgra thos tshad sngar sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:355: phyis 'tshang rgya ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:356: nam mkha' dag la 'phar ba dang //
NK034(ngi)003:360: 'phar ba dang zhes pa sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das pa la yang brjod /
NK034(ngi)003:361: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gcig rdzogs pa dang gzhan
NK034(ngi)003:362: du gong ltar bstan pa spel ba la yang dgongs
NK034(ngi)003:366: lnga po ni dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:367: 'di las 'byung zhes brgyud 'di sngar yod pa 'das tsam na dang /
NK034(ngi)003:368: phyis rgyud 'di babs tsa na nam mkha' gang nas 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:369: gnas dang mi dang ro la zug par yang 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:370: de'i tshe 'ja' 'od mthong tshad 'khor ba las grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:373: 'di 'dzin ces pa bstan pa bu gcig gi rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:374: rnal 'byor zhes pa dbugs chen 'byin pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:375: skal che bas zhes pa btags pa tsam thos pa tsam mthong ba tsam reg pa tsam gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:379: ka la pi ka'i gnas su sgra thos pa tsam gyis 'khor ba stongs par byas so //
NK034(ngi)003:380: 'bring bar dor grol ba la the tshom med /
NK034(ngi)003:381: tha ma yang mngal sgo mi 'grim ste /
NK034(ngi)003:382: pad+ma lnga las bardzusa te skyes nas lo lnga brgya na sangs rgya ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:383: lan gsum 'di yi tshig kun yang //
NK034(ngi)003:386: 'di yi zhes pa sangs rgyas sras gcig po'i rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:387: tshig kun yang zhes pa rang byung gi //
NK034(ngi)003:388: lhag dang chad pa med par ni //
NK034(ngi)003:392: med par ni zhes pa shin tu dag par mos pa gus pas /
NK034(ngi)003:393: rdo rje'i lce yis sus brjod na //
NK034(ngi)003:395: rdo rje'i zhes pas rigs lnga po mtshon te /
NK034(ngi)003:396: rdo rje ni 'gyur ba med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:397: rin po che ni dgos 'dod 'byung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:398: pad+ma ni skyon gyis ma gos pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:399: ral gri ni gzung 'dzin gcod pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:400: 'khor lo ni sku gsum rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:401: lce yis zhes pa ni rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi lce /
NK034(ngi)003:402: rin po che rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum /
NK034(ngi)003:403: pad ma snang ba mtha' yas yab yum /
NK034(ngi)003:404: ral gri don yod grub pa yab yum /
NK034(ngi)003:405: 'khor lo rnam par snang mdzad yab yum /
NK034(ngi)003:406: gtso 'khor dang lce ru bsgoms pa /
NK034(ngi)003:407: sus brjod na zhes pa skal ldan byang sems can gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:409: nad gdon sdig sgrib sad ser mu ge 'khrug pa zhi bar 'dod na /
NK034(ngi)003:410: rdo rje sems dpa'i tshom bur bsgom /
NK034(ngi)003:411: tshe bsod rgyas pa la rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK034(ngi)003:412: dbang la snang ba mtha' yas /
NK034(ngi)003:413: drag po la don yod grub pa /
NK034(ngi)003:414: thams cad la rnam par snang mdzad yab yum gtso 'khor du bsgoms te /
NK034(ngi)003:415: kha shar lho nub byang du bltas la /
NK034(ngi)003:416: ngag bcad la tshar gsum gsum bco lnga dag par brjod na /
NK034(ngi)003:417: de'i dus su 'ja' 'od kha char khu rlangs 'brug la sogs pa'i ltas ci byung yang rung ste /
NK034(ngi)003:418: mthong ba thos pa reg pa /
NK034(ngi)003:419: 'di yang de dang mnyam par yong /
NK034(ngi)003:421: 'di yang zhes pa gong ma'i tshig lhag ste /
NK034(ngi)003:422: gong gi 'ja' 'od 'brug sgra thos mthong reg pa'i sems can thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:425: tha ma mngal sgo mi 'grim ste gong ma dang /
NK034(ngi)003:426: mnyam par yong zhes pa dgongs pa dang rtags /
NK034(ngi)003:429: 'gyur bar zhes pa sangs rgya bar /
NK034(ngi)003:431: the tshom yod re kan no //
NK034(ngi)003:432: mngon sum rig pa rtogs pas smos ci dgos /
NK034(ngi)003:433: de phyir bstan pa'i rgyud rnams kun //
NK034(ngi)003:435: de phyir zhes pa rgyud 'di min pa /
NK034(ngi)003:436: bstan pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:437: rgyud rnams kun ces pas sngags phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:438: thams cad dus gcig bsgom shes kyang //
NK034(ngi)003:441: dus gcig ces pas sa gcig par /
NK034(ngi)003:442: bsgom shes kyang zhes pa gang zag gis /
NK034(ngi)003:443: 'di ma snang bar grol ba med //
NK034(ngi)003:446: snang bar ces pa rgyud don rig pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:447: grol ba med ces pa chos gzhan mkhas pa pan+di tar gyur kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:451: sa bon ni sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:452: rang 'phel bas zhes pa rgyud 'di'i byin brlabs las /
NK034(ngi)003:453: bstan pa'i bdag po gang sangs rgyas //
NK034(ngi)003:455: bstan pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:456: bdag po zhes pa dngos dpe sh+aakya thub pa lta bu'o //
NK034(ngi)003:457: gang sangs rgyas zhes pa 'jig rten gyi khams gang du sangs rgyas gang byon kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:458: 'di nyid sa bon med par ni //
NK034(ngi)003:460: 'di nyid ces pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:461: sa bon zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:462: med par ni zhes pa rgyud rang byung 'di'i byin rlabs ma thos ma mthong ma reg par /
NK034(ngi)003:463: bstan pa'i gsung ni tshig tsam yang //
NK034(ngi)003:465: bstan pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:466: gsung ni zhes pa mdo rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:467: tshig tsam yang zhes pa gsung /
NK034(ngi)003:468: lce yi dbang pos brjod mi nus //
NK034(ngi)003:470: lce yi zhes pa 'gro ba tha dad pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:471: dbang pos zhes pa smra byed kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:472: brjod mi nus zhes pa tshig gcig tsam yang /
NK034(ngi)003:473: de tshig 'di la ma brten par //
NK034(ngi)003:475: de tshig ces pa chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:476: 'di la zhes pa bstan pa'i bu gcig gi rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:477: ma brten par zhes pa byin rlabs rang babs la /
NK034(ngi)003:478: rdul cha tsam yang 'byung ba med //
NK034(ngi)003:480: rdul cha ni phra rab brgyar bshags pa'i cha /
NK034(ngi)003:481: tsam yang zhes pa med pa'i tshad /
NK034(ngi)003:482: 'byung ba med ces pa sangs rgyas kyi gsung /
NK034(ngi)003:483: bstan pa gcig gi snyigs ma la //
NK034(ngi)003:486: gcig gi zhes pa gang rung /
NK034(ngi)003:487: snyigs ma la zhes pa bstan pa mar 'grib dus na 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:488: de nyon mongs pa cha cha nas rags su song ba las byung zhing lan no //
NK034(ngi)003:489: byin rlabs tshig ni 'di kun yang //
NK034(ngi)003:491: byin brlabs ni ye gdod ma nas chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:492: tshig ni zhes pa 'di rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:493: 'di kun yang zhes pa le'u bdun pa 'adi'o //
NK034(ngi)003:494: gang la snang ba'i mi des kyang //
NK034(ngi)003:497: snang ba'i zhes pa byin rlabs mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:498: mi des kyang zhes pa skal ldan pho mo /
NK034(ngi)003:499: dpe dga' rab rdo rjee bdag dang mtshungs so //
NK034(ngi)003:500: ma mthong rgyud dang bstan bcos ni //
NK034(ngi)003:503: rgyud dang zhes pa sngags phyi nang du grags pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:504: bstan bcos ni zhes pa rig 'dzin 'phags pa rnams kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:505: lce yi dbang pos brjod par nus //
NK034(ngi)003:507: lce yi zhes pa brjod pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:508: dbang pos zhes pa rang dbang thob par /
NK034(ngi)003:509: brjod par nus zhes pa tshig don 'brel can du /
NK034(ngi)003:510: sems can kun gyi bsam pa dang //
NK034(ngi)003:512: sems can ni khams gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:513: kun gyi zhes pa ma lus pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:514: bsam pa dang zhes so so rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:515: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa ni //
NK034(ngi)003:517: sangs rgyas zhes pa ni chos sku'i sangs rgyas kun bzang yab yum /
NK034(ngi)003:518: longs sku'i sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad gangs chen mtsho /
NK034(ngi)003:519: sprul sku'i sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang /
NK034(ngi)003:520: kun gyi zhes pa ni sangs rgyas de dag /
NK034(ngi)003:521: dgongs pa ni zhes pa ni de rnams kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:522: ji ltar mthun pa'i chos kun ni //
NK034(ngi)003:524: ji ltar zhes pa blo che chung /
NK034(ngi)003:525: mthun pa'i zhes pa so sor /
NK034(ngi)003:526: chos kun ni zhes pa ma lus pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:527: 'di yis ston par nus pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:530: ston par zhes pa so so rang rang gi skad du /
NK034(ngi)003:531: nus pa yin zhes byin rlabs kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:532: 'dzam bu gling bye ba phrag brgyas thog drangs nas mtha' med brjod las 'das par /
NK034(ngi)003:533: sangs rgyas rnams ni thugs dang gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:535: sangs rgyas ni ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi dri ma ye nas sangs /
NK034(ngi)003:536: sku dang ye shes mkhyen pa ye nas rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:537: rnams kyi zhes pa brjod pa las 'das pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:538: thugs dang gcig ces pa snying po lnga ldan no //
NK034(ngi)003:539: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dgongs pa dang //
NK034(ngi)003:541: rdo rje ni stong rig lnga ldan no //
NK034(ngi)003:542: 'dzin pa'i zhes pa rdo rje 'chang gi brgyud pa bla ma mtshan ldan no //
NK034(ngi)003:543: dgongs pa dang zhes pa sangs rgyas dang mnyam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:546: dbyer mi zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs bla ma'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:547: phyed par zhes pa rgyud 'di btags mthong thos dran reg gi 'gro ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:549: de phyir bstan pa'i me ro yin //
NK034(ngi)003:552: bstan pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:553: me ro yin zhes pa dpe nags tshig pa'i me ro de /
NK034(ngi)003:554: rlung ser bu byung ba dang me ro langs nas
NK034(ngi)003:555: gzhan du mched par 'dra bar rgyud 'di sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)003:556: kyi bstan pa gcig rdzogs pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:557: yang gzhan du 'bar nas bstan pa 'phel ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:558: rang byung tshig gi rgyal po 'di //
NK034(ngi)003:560: rang byung ni ma byas pa'i rig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:561: tshig gi zhes pa ni 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:562: rgyal po 'di zhes pa gong na med pa'i rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:563: so so'i sems can skye gzugs la //
NK034(ngi)003:565: so so'i zhes pa rigs drug /
NK034(ngi)003:566: sems can ces pa bcud kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:567: skye gzugs la zhes par bardzusa skyes /
NK034(ngi)003:571: gzugs che chung tha dad pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:572: so so'i brda skad ji lta bar //
NK034(ngi)003:574: so so'i zhes pa sems can /
NK034(ngi)003:575: brda skad ces pa rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:576: ji lta bar zhes pa mthun par /
NK034(ngi)003:577: 'di nyid de ltar snang ba yin //
NK034(ngi)003:580: de ltar zhes pa gong ma bzhin /
NK034(ngi)003:581: snang ba yin zhes pa so so rang rang gi yi ger rgyud don thig le yang brjod do //
NK034(ngi)003:582: de phyir rang byung yi ger ni //
NK034(ngi)003:584: de phyir ces pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:585: rang byung zhes pa yul so so rang rang las /
NK034(ngi)003:586: yi ger ni zhes pa rigs mi gcig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:587: thog ma babs kyis grub nas byung //
NK034(ngi)003:589: thog ma ni sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi ming med de las /
NK034(ngi)003:591: grub nas byung zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgrar byung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:592: rang byung bcom ldan 'das la yang //
NK034(ngi)003:594: rang byung ni rig pa'i ye shes /
NK034(ngi)003:595: bcom ldan ni nyon mongs pa lnga bcom /
NK034(ngi)003:597: 'das la yang zhes pa sku gsum gyi 'dzin pa las 'das pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:598: 'di ltar rdzogs pa'i lugs su snang //
NK034(ngi)003:600: 'di ltar zhes pa chos thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:602: lugs su snang zhes pa ye gdod ma nas mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:603: chos kyi sde snod nyid du ni //
NK034(ngi)003:605: chos kyi zhes pa sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:606: sde snod ni 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:607: nyid du ni zhes pa sngags phyi nang /
NK034(ngi)003:608: 'di tshig ye nas rang shar bas //
NK034(ngi)003:610: 'di tshig ces pa bstan pa'i bu gcig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:611: ye nas zhes pa sus kyang byas pa med par /
NK034(ngi)003:612: rang shar bas zhes pa gsal stong dbyer med thig ler /
NK034(ngi)003:613: thog ma dran pa'i gzhir gyur te //
NK034(ngi)003:615: thog ma zhes pa ye shes gsum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:616: ye shes gsum ni ngo bo ka dag /
NK034(ngi)003:618: thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes so //
NK034(ngi)003:619: dran pa'i zhes pa rig pa rang dwangs su /
NK034(ngi)003:620: gzhir gyur te zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:621: dran pa thams cad ma stongs par //
NK034(ngi)003:623: dran pa zhes pa mi dran dgu dran 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:624: thams cad ces pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:625: ma stongs par zhes pa dran med du /
NK034(ngi)003:626: tshig 'di kun kyang snang ba yiin //
NK034(ngi)003:629: kun kyang zhes pa ma lus par /
NK034(ngi)003:630: snang ba yin zhes pa thams cad kyi yi ger /
NK034(ngi)003:631: dran zad tshig 'di zad par ni //
NK034(ngi)003:634: tshig 'di zhes pa bstan pa'i bu gcig gis /
NK034(ngi)003:635: zad par ni sku gsum gyi 'dzin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:636: rdo rje zhes ni tshig 'di kun //
NK034(ngi)003:638: rdo rje ni 'gyur med 'dzin zad ka dag de'o //
NK034(ngi)003:639: zhes ni de la bya zhes pa'i tshig go //
NK034(ngi)003:640: tshig 'di kun zhes pa dang rang byung gi //
NK034(ngi)003:641: 'byung ba'i rkyen dang bral bas na //
NK034(ngi)003:643: 'byung ba'i zhes pa sa cu me rlung gi //
NK034(ngi)003:644: rkyen dang zhes pa sa rlung lta bu'am me chu'am gnyis 'dom gyi sgra min tshig min /
NK034(ngi)003:645: bral bas na zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:646: rdo rje kun 'byung gsang sngags yin //
NK034(ngi)003:649: kun 'byung ni gong ma grangs las 'das pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:650: gsang sngags yin zhes pa rgyud 'di log lta can la /
NK034(ngi)003:651: thabs lam du ma mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:653: thabs lam ni sangs rgya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:654: du ma ni rtsa la brten pa dang rlung la
NK034(ngi)003:655: brten pa dang thig le dang las rgya la brten
NK034(ngi)003:656: pa dang phyag dang bskor ba bya ba la brten
NK034(ngi)003:657: pa'o // mtshon pa'i phyir zhes pa rgyud 'di la /
NK034(ngi)003:658: rang babs bsgom pa 'di las byung //
NK034(ngi)003:660: rang babs zhes pa sangs rgyas sgam ste ma mdzad sems can sgrin pos mi bcos pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:661: bsgom pa ni ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum dbyer med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:662: 'di las byung zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:663: snying po rang 'dul bstan pa'i bcud //
NK034(ngi)003:665: snying po ni chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:668: gzhi nyid kyi ni babs yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:670: gzhi nyid ces pa dang po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:671: kyi ni zhes pa thams cad ma lus pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:672: babs yin no zhes pa dngos po gshis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:673: chos kun mnyam pa'i nan tan tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:675: chos kun zhes pa theg pa dgu'i /
NK034(ngi)003:676: mnyam pa'i zhes pa mtha' mnyam pa mtho dman med par /
NK034(ngi)003:677: nan tan tshig ces pa rgyud 'dis sems can sangs rgya bar byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:678: rang gnad du ni 'di kun shar //
NK034(ngi)003:680: rang gnad ces pa'i don ni sems can /
NK034(ngi)003:681: du ni zhes pa sangs rgya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:682: 'di kun shar ces pa rgyud kyi tshig don gcig par mkha' la mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:683: 'di la nub pa gcig nyid med //
NK034(ngi)003:685: 'di la zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:686: nub pa ces pa rtogs rung ma rtogs rung /
NK034(ngi)003:690: gcig nyid med ces pa gang du yang /
NK034(ngi)003:691: ci ste na 'di la 'byung bzhi'i gnod med pas zhes pas gsal lo //
NK034(ngi)003:692: bsgom dang bsgrub pa'i rtsa bar yang //
NK034(ngi)003:694: bsgom dang zhes pa rtsa dang rlung dang thig le /
NK034(ngi)003:695: bsgrub pa'i zhes pa sku dang gsung thugs la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:696: rtsa bar yang zhes pa bstan pa'i bu gcig gi rgyud byung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:700: 'khrul pa'i zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:701: tshig ma yin zhes pa ka dag 'khrul med kyi snying po /
NK034(ngi)003:702: yab kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:703: yum kun tu bzang mo'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:704: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:705: 'ja' 'od lha sku ring bsrel gyi snying po /
NK034(ngi)003:706: longs sku zhi khro'i rang sgra yi ge drug /
NK034(ngi)003:707: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi snying po yig 'bru gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:708: grags stong sprul pa'i sku'i yang snying a li k+aa li /
NK034(ngi)003:709: bstan pa mi 'gyur ba'i yang snying rten 'brel snying
NK034(ngi)003:710: po phrin las mtha' rgyas kyi sham bu dang bcas
NK034(ngi)003:711: pa'o // ma 'khrul sngon thog nyid kyi gzhi //
NK034(ngi)003:713: ma 'khrul zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:714: sngon thog ces pa sangs rgyas dang sems can rgyab ma gyes pa'i dus /
NK034(ngi)003:715: nyid kyi gzhi zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:719: spros pa'i rgyud ces pa chos kyi sgo mo ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:720: rgyu las 'bras bu rang byung bzhin //
NK034(ngi)003:722: rgyu las zhes pa 'khrul med snying po /
NK034(ngi)003:724: rang byung bzhin zhes pa sems can la /
NK034(ngi)003:725: 'di dag las ni tshig kun yang //
NK034(ngi)003:728: las ni zhes pa byin brlabs /
NK034(ngi)003:729: tshig kun yang zhes pa thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:730: dran bsam bral ba'i ngang nyid las //
NK034(ngi)003:732: dran bsam zhes pa bams mnos pa lta bu yin te /
NK034(ngi)003:733: bral ba'i zhes pa blo dang /
NK034(ngi)003:734: ngang nyid las zhes pa chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:735: byas pa med par byung ba yin //
NK034(ngi)003:737: byas pa zhes pa sus kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:738: med par zhes pa 'jig rten gyi khams gang du yang /
NK034(ngi)003:739: byung ba yin zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgrar /
NK034(ngi)003:742: 'od zer zhes pa rig mdangs zhi khro rang gsal gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:743: 'dzin pa'i zhes pa nam mkha' la /
NK034(ngi)003:744: skyes bu la zhes pa skal ldan /
NK034(ngi)003:747: 'di ni rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:748: snang bar zhes pa mngon sum /
NK034(ngi)003:749: 'gyur ba 'o zhes pa rtags tshad gong du 'phel ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:752: de las zhes pa skal ldan sems kyi bu rig pa mngon sum du mthong ba /
NK034(ngi)003:754: grangs 'ga' 'byung zhes pa sangs rgyas 'jig rten gyi khams su /
NK034(ngi)003:755: gsang ba'i bden pa gcig pa nyid //
NK034(ngi)003:757: gsang ba'i zhes pa log lta can la /
NK034(ngi)003:758: bden pa ni don dam pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:759: gcig pa nyid ces pa rgyud 'di //
NK034(ngi)003:760: grangs med rdo rje 'chang rnams kyi //
NK034(ngi)003:762: grangs med ces pa rjod las 'das pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:763: rdo rje zhes pa stong rig lnga ldan no //
NK034(ngi)003:764: 'chang rnams kyi zhes pa rgyun chad med par /
NK034(ngi)003:765: thugs rdol nyag gcig dgongs don gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:767: thugs rdol zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:768: nyag gcig ces pa thig le /
NK034(ngi)003:769: dgongs don gcig ces pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:770: 'dzin med yangs pa'i rtod phur yin //
NK034(ngi)003:773: yangs pa'i zhes pa lta ba /
NK034(ngi)003:774: rtod phur yin zhes 'gyur ba med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:775: thod rgal thog babs kun gyi gnad //
NK034(ngi)003:777: thod rgal ces pa rig pa mngon sum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:778: thog babs zhes pa a ma na se'o //
NK034(ngi)003:779: kun gyi gnad ces pa rgyud 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:780: rang sa 'byed pa'i lde mig mchog /
NK034(ngi)003:782: rang sa zhes pa theg pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:784: lde mig mchog ces pa rgyud 'dis don khrol cing rtogs par byed pa /
NK034(ngi)003:788: bde ba'i zhes pa zad pa med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:791: sangs rgyas rnams kyi shes rab yin //
NK034(ngi)003:793: sangs rgyas zhes pa nyon mongs pa sangs ye shes rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:794: rnams kyi zhes pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:795: shes rab yin zhes pa mkhyen pa rnams kyi gtso bo /
NK034(ngi)003:796: mkha' mnyam dag pa'i gnam gzer 'dis //
NK034(ngi)003:798: mkha' mnyam zhes pa chos nyid /
NK034(ngi)003:800: gnam gzer 'dis zhes pa thig le 'phyugs med kyi rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:801: bstan pa kun gyi rtsa ba 'dzin //
NK034(ngi)003:803: bstan pa ni sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:804: kun gyi zhes pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:805: rtsa ba 'dzin ces pa rgyud 'dis gang thams cad du /
NK034(ngi)003:806: 'di yi grangs sna bzung bas na //
NK034(ngi)003:808: 'di yi zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:809: grangs sna zhes pa lhag chad med par /
NK034(ngi)003:810: bzung bas na zhes pa 'gro ba skal ldan gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:811: lha min g.yul rnams rang log tu //
NK034(ngi)003:813: lha min ces pa lha dang lha ma yin dang mi'i /
NK034(ngi)003:814: g.yul rnams zhes pa 'thab rtsod dang pha rol gyi dmag tshogs /
NK034(ngi)003:815: rang log tu zhes pa phar la /
NK034(ngi)003:819: bzung ba zhes pa skal ldan gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:820: bstan pa'i bdag po gang yin pa de'i sku mdog
NK034(ngi)003:821: dang mthun pa'i rin po ches bris te spyi bor
NK034(ngi)003:824: khams gsum g.yul kun 'dis bzlog go //
NK034(ngi)003:826: khams gsum zhes pa 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams so //
NK034(ngi)003:827: g.yul kun zhes pa gsum por 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK034(ngi)003:828: 'dis bzlog go zhes pas dbang bskur ba'i dus su rgyud 'di spyi bor btags na /
NK034(ngi)003:829: dbang bskur thob pa dang thos pa mthong ba reg pa thams cad sangs rgya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:830: chos 'chad pa'i dus su rgyud mgrin par btags na /
NK034(ngi)003:831: chos 'chad pa mthong thos mos reg thams cad sangs rgya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:832: ngo sprod byed pa'i dus su rgyud 'di snying gar btags na /
NK034(ngi)003:833: ngo sprod thob mthong thos reg mos thams cad sangs rgya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:834: lar rgyud 'di btags pa'i mi la srog chags 'byung mi srid /
NK034(ngi)003:835: byung ba srid na yang las sad pa'i rigs te grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:838: rigs drug ces pa 'gro ba ste lus bzang ngan gyi byed pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:839: rnams kyi zhes pa grangs las 'das te ma lus pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:840: 'bros khung 'gegs zhes pa sangs rgyas las 'bros te las ngan sna tshogs bsags nas /
NK034(ngi)003:841: 'khor ba ngan song gsum du zag par byed pa'i
NK034(ngi)003:842: khung bu rgyud 'di btags pa tsam gyis 'gegs pa'o
NK034(ngi)003:843: // mya ngan 'das pa'i grong khyer du /
NK034(ngi)003:845: mya ngan zhes pa 'khor ba ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal lo //
NK034(ngi)003:846: 'das pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi bde ba zag pa med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:847: grong khyer du zhes pa dpe de sangs rgyas kyi
NK034(ngi)003:848: zhing khams rnam par dag pa rigs lnga tshom bu'i
NK034(ngi)003:849: dkyil 'khor mtha' med brjod las 'das par /
NK034(ngi)003:852: 'jug par zhes pa gong gi zhing khams su /
NK034(ngi)003:855: tha ma sprul sku'i zhing khams su mngal sgo mi 'grim ste /
NK034(ngi)003:856: lo lnga brgya na zag pa med par 'tshang rgya /
NK034(ngi)003:857: 'khor lo yin ces pa sangs rgyas myur te dpe nam mkha' la nyi ma gcig shar bas /
NK034(ngi)003:858: gling bzhi mun pa rang sangs pa ltar /
NK034(ngi)003:859: rgyud 'di thogs pa tsam gyis bskal par bsags pa'i
NK034(ngi)003:860: las sgrib 'joms pas 'di las 'tshang rgya bar myur
NK034(ngi)003:862: byung ba 'dug na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyis nga'i mgo khos zhes pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:863: srid pas bcings pa rnams las ni //
NK034(ngi)003:865: srid pas zhes pa nga bdag gi 'dzin pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:866: bcings pa zhes pa sdug bsngal gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:867: rnams las ni zhes pa sems can ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:870: 'di yis zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:871: grol bar zhes pa gzung 'dzin las /
NK034(ngi)003:872: byed pa'o zhes pa rgyud mthong thos reg tshad /
NK034(ngi)003:873: dam pa'i snying po gdung rgyud du //
NK034(ngi)003:875: dam pa'i zhes pa rigs brgya'i /
NK034(ngi)003:877: gdung rgyud du zhes pa sangs rgyas zam ma chad par byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:878: rang bzhin du ni babs las byung //
NK034(ngi)003:880: rang bzhin zhes pa ye gdod ma nas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:882: babs las byung zhes pa sku gsum rang chas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:883: 'dis ni bla ma'i sku mi spong //
NK034(ngi)003:886: bla ma'i zhes pa gdams ngag /
NK034(ngi)003:887: sku mi spong zhes pa bla mas 'di nyid /
NK034(ngi)003:888: 'di nyid ni bla ma gcig la gcig rang babs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:889: des na 'gro ba'i bla ma grangs las 'das pa 'phel zhing de'i rgyud spel te /
NK034(ngi)003:890: yang 'gro ba'i bla mas spel lo //
NK034(ngi)003:891: snying la nyi ma'i 'od brdal bas //
NK034(ngi)003:893: snying la zhes pa 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:894: nyi ma'i zhes pa ye shes thig le lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:895: 'od brdal bas zhes pa dung khang na khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK034(ngi)003:896: snying ga na lha sum cu rtsa bdun /
NK034(ngi)003:897: lar lus mgo gzhug la sangs rgyas sum stong bzhugs pa la dgongs te /
NK034(ngi)003:898: 'od mthing kha dkar ser dmar ljang sna tshogs pas phyi nang med par ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:899: phyogs bcur khyab pa'i mun pa ni //
NK034(ngi)003:901: phyogs bcur zhes pa phyogs bzhi dang mtshams bzhi ste brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcu'o //
NK034(ngi)003:902: khyab pa'i zhes pa chos nyid la nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pas /
NK034(ngi)003:903: mun pa ni zhes pa chos can spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK034(ngi)003:904: thams cad chos nyid rang mdangs su ma rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)003:907: 'di yis zhes rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:908: rang sangs zhes pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba tag tag tig tig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:909: nyid du 'gro zhes pa 'di'i byin rlabs kyis 'khrul snang zhing khams su /
NK034(ngi)003:910: lhag par gnas pa'i ye shes ni //
NK034(ngi)003:913: gnas pa'i zhes pa lus mgo gzhug la sangs rgyas sum stong /
NK034(ngi)003:914: ye shes ni zhes pa sngon rdo rje 'chang gis rang mdangs su ye nas shes pa bzhin du /
NK034(ngi)003:915: 'di yis mchog tu ston par byed //
NK034(ngi)003:917: 'di yis zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:918: mchog tu zhes pa thun mong ma yin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:919: ston par byed ces pa sangs rgyas sum stong gi zhal dus gcig la /
NK034(ngi)003:920: dkon pa'i mchog rnams bskyed pa'i yum //
NK034(ngi)003:922: dkon pa'i zhes pa 'jig rten khams su /
NK034(ngi)003:923: mchog rnams zhes pa bstan pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:924: bskyed pa'i yum zhes pa rgyud 'di yis /
NK034(ngi)003:925: sems dal bsam gtan ngang gis grub //
NK034(ngi)003:927: sems dal zhes pa ngo bo stong par shes pas /
NK034(ngi)003:928: bsam gtan zhes pa rang bzhin gyis zhing khams shar bas /
NK034(ngi)003:929: ngang gis grub ces pa chos nyid kyi byin brlabs rgyud 'dis /
NK034(ngi)003:930: chos sku'i snang ba dus gcig tu //
NK034(ngi)003:932: chos ni stong zhing bdag med pa'i rig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:933: sku ni de'i rang mdangs sangs rgyas sum stong /
NK034(ngi)003:934: snang ba ni ngo bo stong pa rang bzhin gsal ba thugs rjes ma khyab pa med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:935: dus gcig tu zhes pa thams cad dbyer med thig le nyag gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:936: ston par byed pa'i sgron ma'o //
NK034(ngi)003:938: ston par zhes pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:939: byed pa'i zhes pa skad cig la /
NK034(ngi)003:940: sgron ma'o zhes pa ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:941: dpe bskal par yod pa'i mun pa yang sgron me
NK034(ngi)003:942: gcig gis 'joms pa ltar bskal par bsags pa'i las
NK034(ngi)003:943: sgrib kyang rgyud 'di btags pas 'dags par 'gyur ba'o
NK034(ngi)003:944: // phyin ci log las yang dag tu //
NK034(ngi)003:946: phyin ci zhes pa mu stegs so //
NK034(ngi)003:947: log las zhes pa lta ba /
NK034(ngi)003:948: yang dag tu zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:949: dag par byed pa'i chu rgyun yin //
NK034(ngi)003:951: dag par zhes pa dam grib /
NK034(ngi)003:952: byed pa'i zhes pa rgyud 'di btags na /
NK034(ngi)003:953: chu rgyun yin ces pa ka dag gnas lugs kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:954: theg pa kun gyi mthar thug tu //
NK034(ngi)003:958: mthar thug tu zhes pa yang gsang bla na med pa'i snying thig tu /
NK034(ngi)003:959: skyel bar byed pa'i shing rta'o //
NK034(ngi)003:962: byed pa'i zhes pa bar dor /
NK034(ngi)003:963: shing rta'o zhes pa sa lam mthong thos reg pas chod pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:964: thos bsam sgom pa'i rgyangs shing du //
NK034(ngi)003:966: thos bsam zhes pa theg pa mtha' dag gi chos la /
NK034(ngi)003:967: sgom pa'i zhes pa de'i don /
NK034(ngi)003:968: rgyangs shing du zhes pa dpe ste don la sangs
NK034(ngi)003:969: rgyas kyi mkhyen pa mtha' dag la ma rmongs par
NK034(ngi)003:970: / 'jug par byed pa'i dngos po yin //
NK034(ngi)003:972: 'jug par zhes pa sems can skal ldan rnams sangs rgyas kyi sar /
NK034(ngi)003:973: byed pa'i zhes pa rgyud 'di mthong thos reg pas /
NK034(ngi)003:974: dngos po yin zhes pa chos thams cad kyi yang snying dril ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:975: sde snod thams cad 'dzin pa'i chos //
NK034(ngi)003:977: sde snod ces pa 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:978: thams cad ces pa sems can gyi dug gsum re
NK034(ngi)003:979: re la rtog pa mi 'dra ba nyi khri chig
NK034(ngi)003:980: stong 'gyu / dug gsum cha mnyam gyi rtog pa
NK034(ngi)003:981: mi 'dra ba nyi khri chig stong 'gyu bas de'i
NK034(ngi)003:982: stong 'gyu / gnyen por / 'dul ba mdo sde
NK034(ngi)003:983: mngon pa gsum po re re la chos kyi sgo
NK034(ngi)003:984: mo mi 'dra ba nyi khri chig stong chig stong
NK034(ngi)003:985: stong 'gyu / gnyen por / gsungs / sde snod
NK034(ngi)003:986: gsum po cha mnyam gyi chos nyi khri chig stong
NK034(ngi)003:988: 'dzin pa'i zhes pa chos kyi sgo mo de dag
NK034(ngi)003:990: mnyen lcug ldan pa'i lcags kyu'o //
NK034(ngi)003:992: mnyen lcug ces pa zhi ba'i lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:993: ldan pa'i zhes pa rang gi rig pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:994: lcags kyu'o zhes pa dpe ste /
NK034(ngi)003:995: rgyud 'di'i byin brlabs kyis bar dor rang gi rig pa'i mdangs su zin par byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:998: rnal 'byor zhes pa ye gdod ma nas rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1000: dkyil 'khor gyi zhes pa rig mdangs zhi khro'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1001: lam du 'jug pa'i sa mkhan yin //
NK034(ngi)003:1003: lam du zhes pa thar ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1005: sa mkhan yin zhes pa dpe ste /
NK034(ngi)003:1006: ngam grog g.yang sa can lam rgyus yod pas mi nor ba ltar /
NK034(ngi)003:1007: rgyud 'di mthong thos reg pas lam mi nor te sangs rgya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1008: mngal rnams khung sgo 'gog par byed //
NK034(ngi)003:1010: mngal rnams zhes pa rigs drug gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1011: khung sgo zhes pa de ru phyis tshud par byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1012: 'gog par byed ces pa rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:1013: thar pa'i skas ni rang 'dzugs yin //
NK034(ngi)003:1015: thar pa'i zhes pa 'khor ba las /
NK034(ngi)003:1017: rang 'dzugs yin zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:1021: 'od kyi zhes pa mthing ga dkar ser dmar ljang sna tshogs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1022: mthongs 'byed pa zhes pa rgyud 'di btags pa'i 'gro ba de 'das pa'i tshe /
NK034(ngi)003:1023: nang du ye shes kyi mthongs sku dang 'od dang thig le 'char /
NK034(ngi)003:1024: phyi ru 'ja' dang sku gdung ring bsrel du 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1025: de la yang 'od lnga gyen 'greng dang rtsibs shar dang /
NK034(ngi)003:1026: nas 'dra ris dang gdugs phub pa ltar 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:1027: de thig le dang sku dang dbyings zin pa'i mthongs so //
NK034(ngi)003:1028: 'ja' dkar po dar dkar brgyangs pa lta bu 'byung ste /
NK034(ngi)003:1029: de byang chub sems 'byongs pa'i mthongs so //
NK034(ngi)003:1030: chos rnams kyi ni re gnas sa //
NK034(ngi)003:1032: chos rnams zhes pa theg dgu'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1033: kyi ni zhes pa de dag thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1034: re gnas sa zhes pa 'bras bu /
NK034(ngi)003:1035: bdud dang mu stegs mgo gnon yin //
NK034(ngi)003:1037: bdud dang zhes pa bar du gcod pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1038: mu stegs zhes pa lta ba log pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1039: mgo gnon yin zhes pa rgyud 'di yi byin rlabs
NK034(ngi)003:1040: kyis bcom ldan 'das kyi mdzad pa dang mtshungs te
NK034(ngi)003:1042: shes rab rmugs pa'ii gsal 'debs so //
NK034(ngi)003:1044: shes rab ces pa yang dag pa'i don /
NK034(ngi)003:1045: rmugs pa'i zhes pa byol song la sogs pa la rgyud 'di btags na /
NK034(ngi)003:1046: gsal 'debs zhes pa ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)003:1047: kyi snying po 'khrul med de sems can thams cad
NK034(ngi)003:1048: la bzhugs pas / rgyud 'di yi byin rlabs kyis sad par byas nas grol bas /
NK034(ngi)003:1049: des na bag chags srab 'thug med pa'i chos so //
NK034(ngi)003:1050: smon 'jug kun gyi srog shing yin //
NK034(ngi)003:1052: smon zhes pa sems can thams cad sangs rgyas par smon pa de /
NK034(ngi)003:1053: 'jug ces pa rgyud 'di btags pa tsam mthong ba
NK034(ngi)003:1054: tsam thos pa tsam reg pa tsam gyis sangs rgya
NK034(ngi)003:1055: bar nus so // kun gyi zhes pa rgyud 'di btags pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1056: srog shing yin zhes pa 'chi ba yang zlog ste /
NK034(ngi)003:1057: gza' bdud rgyal po bsen mo sa bdag klu gnyan
NK034(ngi)003:1058: lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi rbod gtong gnod pa
NK034(ngi)003:1059: thams cad bzlog / tshe ring ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:1062: des na smon lam la mi ltos pa'i chos so //
NK034(ngi)003:1063: lha dang sngags kyi mdo mdud do //
NK034(ngi)003:1065: lha dang zhes pa phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1066: sngags kyi zhes pa phyi nang lha'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1067: mdo mdud do zhes pa rgyud 'di mthong thos reg
NK034(ngi)003:1068: pa'i byin rlabs kyis bskyed rim ma bsgoms par lha
NK034(ngi)003:1070: sngags ma zlos par sangs rgyas kyi phrin las grub pas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1071: des na bskyed rim dang sngags bzlas pa la mi ltos pa'i chos so //
NK034(ngi)003:1072: dkyil 'khor rnams kyi skyed shing ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:1074: dkyil 'khor zhes pa stong rig thig le'i dkyil la rang mdangs ye shes lnga yi 'khor /
NK034(ngi)003:1075: rigs lnga rigs kyi gtso bo yab yum la rigs bzhi so so'i yab yum sbrags ma'i 'khor /
NK034(ngi)003:1076: rigs lnga tshom bu'i dkyil la sems dpa' sems ma
NK034(ngi)003:1077: sgo bzhi yab yum 'khor bas na dkyil 'khor zhes
NK034(ngi)003:1078: pa'o // rnams kyi zhes pa phyi nang thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1079: skyed shing ngo zhes pa dpe ste don la rig pa'i rang mdangs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:1080: da lta rnam smin sgyu lus kyi rtsa nang du 'khums pa rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:1081: rgyud 'di btags pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:1082: bar dor nam mkhas gar khyab thams cad du mtha' med las 'das pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1083: des na thos pa dang dpe cha la mi ltos pa'i chos so //
NK034(ngi)003:1084: lta sgom log pa'i dag byed khrus //
NK034(ngi)003:1086: lta sgom zhes pa phyogs lhung dang gnyis su med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1087: log pa'i zhes pa lta ba sgom pa spyod pa
NK034(ngi)003:1088: log pa'i mu stegs pa 'bras bu log ste lha
NK034(ngi)003:1089: dang dbang phyug thob pa la dgongs kyang dmyal ba
NK034(ngi)003:1090: bsgrub bya'o // dag byed khrus zhes pa sngar mu
NK034(ngi)003:1091: stegs lta bu yin yang phyis rgyud 'di dang 'phrad
NK034(ngi)003:1092: bsgrub bya'o // na grol te / des na lus
NK034(ngi)003:1093: kyi bya ba dang sgom pa la mi ltos pa'i
NK034(ngi)003:1094: bsgrub bya'o // na grol te / chos so // man ngag snying po rdzogs pa'i sa //
NK034(ngi)003:1096: man ngag ces pa sangs rgya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1097: snying po zhes pa chos thams cad kyi snying po stong pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1098: stong pa'i snying po rig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1101: sku lnga'i snying po rang mdangs su shes pa'i shes rab /
NK034(ngi)003:1102: rdzogs pa'i sa zhes pa sangs rgyas sras gcig po 'di sngar 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:1104: phyis kyang 'di las zab pa yod re kan no zhes pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1105: rdo rje theg pa'i grangs rdzogs nas //
NK034(ngi)003:1107: rdo rje ni stong rig lnga ldan 'gyur med de'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1108: theg pa'i zhes pa a ti'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1109: grangs rdzogs nas zhes pa a ti la sde gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:1110: de la klong dgu shwa lo ka 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK034(ngi)003:1111: le'u stong phrag sum cu rtsa lnga /
NK034(ngi)003:1112: bam po nyi khri chig stong gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:1113: brjod bya nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1114: rjod byed nye bar bsdus pas gzer bu brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK034(ngi)003:1115: grangs ni stong phrag phyed dang gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:1116: gnad chen bsdus pa stong phrag gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:1117: gol sgrib khri phrag bzhi bcu tham pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1118: ming thogs pa'i rgyud khri phrag gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:1119: de dag gi yang snying rgyud bcu bdun /
NK034(ngi)003:1120: de dag gi yang snying rgyud rang byung rang babs
NK034(ngi)003:1121: sangs rgyas sras gcig gser gyi snying po nyi ma
NK034(ngi)003:1123: 'di ni thig le nyag gcig go //
NK034(ngi)003:1124: thig le nyag gcig ni ka nas dag go //
NK034(ngi)003:1127: 'gro rnams zhes pa khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:1128: lam la zhes pa sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1129: 'dzud pa'o zhes pa rgyud 'dis sngar tshangs pa chen
NK034(ngi)003:1130: po'i gnas su thams cad grol te 'khor ba stongs
NK034(ngi)003:1131: par byas / de nas khyab 'jug gi gnas su thams cad grol te stongs par byas /
NK034(ngi)003:1132: de nas ka la ping ka'i gnas su thams cad grol te stongs par byas /
NK034(ngi)003:1134: thog drangs nas mtha' med brjod las 'das pa grol bar byed do //
NK034(ngi)003:1135: theg pa'i rgyal po yongs rdzogs kyi //
NK034(ngi)003:1138: rgyal po zhes pa gong na med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1139: yongs rdzogs kyi zhes pa ma rdzogs dgu rdzogs pa
NK034(ngi)003:1140: yod pa min pa yin pa med pa snang ba
NK034(ngi)003:1141: mi snang ba / gsal ba mi gsal ba rtag pa mi rtag pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1142: gnyis dang gnyis med ma yin pa thams cad yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i bu gcig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1143: yon tan byung tshul rang byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:1145: yon tan zhes pa sangs rgyas ni /
NK034(ngi)003:1146: byung tshul zhes pa rgyud 'di btags mthong thos reg pa'i sems can la /
NK034(ngi)003:1147: rang byung ngo zhes pa yon tan gyi tshigs su
NK034(ngi)003:1148: bcad pa rnams kyang byas pa lta bu ma yin
NK034(ngi)003:1149: te / dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs las mngon sum du snang ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1150: des na sngar yang 'di las zab pa byon re kan no //
NK034(ngi)003:1151: da ltar yang 'di las zab pa bzhugs re kan no //
NK034(ngi)003:1152: phyis kyang 'di las zab pa 'byon re kan no //
NK034(ngi)003:1153: des na 'di yod sangs rgyas dngos so //
NK034(ngi)003:1154: 'gro ba rnams kyi bla ma dam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1156: rgyud 'di dang bla ma phu dud du khur bar bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1162: zhes che ba yon tan gyi le'u ste dang po rdzogs so ////
NK034(ngi)003:1163: da ni le'u gnyis pa 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:1164: e ma hoh zhes pa'i don ni /
NK034(ngi)003:1165: e ni ngo bo ka dag gi dbyings /
NK034(ngi)003:1166: ma ni rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dbyings /
NK034(ngi)003:1167: hohni thugs rje kun khyab kyi dbyings so //
NK034(ngi)003:1168: gsang mdzad rang bzhin tshig 'di yang //
NK034(ngi)003:1170: gsang mdzad ces pa log lta can la gong ma'i
NK034(ngi)003:1171: yon tan rngams po che rnams brjod na mi dga'
NK034(ngi)003:1172: bar / mi bden nges so brdzun no zhes /
NK034(ngi)003:1173: theg pa thun mong ba rnams sdig gsog pa 'byung /
NK034(ngi)003:1174: sdig bsags na sems can stong bsgral bas 'di la
NK034(ngi)003:1175: skur pa btab pa brgya'i char yang mi nye stong
NK034(ngi)003:1176: gi char yang mi nye bar sdig che bas /
NK034(ngi)003:1177: sangs rgyas la rgyab kyis phyogs pas gsang bar bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1178: rang bzhin zhes pa dngos po gshis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1179: tshig 'di yang zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1180: rang byung ye dag chen por ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1182: rang byung zhes pa dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs la /
NK034(ngi)003:1183: ye dag ces pa 'khrul pa'i dri ma /
NK034(ngi)003:1184: dpe nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang mtshungs so //
NK034(ngi)003:1185: chen por ni zhes pa theg pa thams cad kyi
NK034(ngi)003:1186: yang rtse sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa gong
NK034(ngi)003:1187: na med pa sus kyang ma byas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1188: spel tshig gsang ba 'di ltar snang //
NK034(ngi)003:1190: spel tshig ces pa sangs rgyas ji ltar /
NK034(ngi)003:1191: gsang ba zhes pa log lta can la /
NK034(ngi)003:1192: 'di ltar snang zhes pa 'di na mar gsungs pa
NK034(ngi)003:1193: bzhin nam mkha' la phyis 'byung bar la yang brjod
NK034(ngi)003:1194: do // ye thog dang po'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1196: ye thog ces pa gar yang rgya ma chad pa'i ming med de'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1197: dang po'i zhes pa dngos po gshis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1198: sangs rgyas ni zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:1199: dang po mngon 'phags dran pa mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1201: dang po zhes pa sangs rgyas dang sems can rgyab
NK034(ngi)003:1202: ma gyes pa'i dus su shes rig kun bzang yum
NK034(ngi)003:1203: gyi / mngon zhes pa sgron ma sku gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:1204: 'phags zhes pa gzhi las thugs rje /
NK034(ngi)003:1205: dran pa zhes pa rang mdangs su /
NK034(ngi)003:1206: mgon zhes pa khams gsum sems can gyi mgon du ye gdod ma nas byon no //
NK034(ngi)003:1207: ji ltar du byon na chos sku las longs sku /
NK034(ngi)003:1208: longs sku las sprul pa'i sku rdo rje 'chang /
NK034(ngi)003:1209: sku gsum gyi mdzad pa sum cu rtsa drug mthar phyin par byon no //
NK034(ngi)003:1210: phyag rgya rang dran 'khor lo ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1212: phyag rgya zhes pa zhi khro'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1213: rang dran zhes pa rang mdang su /
NK034(ngi)003:1214: 'khor lo ni zhes pa sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1215: gzhi las 'phags pa'i khyad par tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:1217: gzhi las zhes pa dang po chos nyid ka dag las /
NK034(ngi)003:1218: 'phags pa'i zhes pa rig pa sku dang 'od du /
NK034(ngi)003:1219: khyad par tshig ces pa 'dus ma byas ye shes
NK034(ngi)003:1220: gsum gyi gsung bstan pa thams cad kyi bu gcig
NK034(ngi)003:1221: po 'adi'o // spyi phud sngon gyi thog mar byung //
NK034(ngi)003:1223: spyi phud ces pa gong na med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1224: sngon gyi zhes pa bskal pa kun gyi thog mar byung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1225: thog mar byung zhes pa mdo rgyud kun gyi thog mar rang byung gi rgyud 'di byung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1226: 'di dus khrag khrig bdun cu yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1228: 'di dus zhes pa chos nyid kyi nam mkha' la
NK034(ngi)003:1229: dbyings gsum bsdus pa'i rang sgrar rgyud 'di byon no
NK034(ngi)003:1230: // khrag khrig bdun cu yis zhes pa 'gro ba
NK034(ngi)003:1231: de tsam zhig gis sgra thos pa tsam gyis sangs
NK034(ngi)003:1232: // rgyas so // phyag rgya 'di ni dam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1234: bstan pa thams cad kyi btsas 'di rang gcig pu'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1237: snying pos brgyan pa'i bskal ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:1240: sde snod dang po'i sangs rgyas mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1241: bstan pa thams cad kyi bu gcig po 'di'i mtshan /
NK034(ngi)003:1242: mnga' mdzad phyag rgya 'khor lo las //
NK034(ngi)003:1244: zhes pa grangs de tsam zhig byung ste sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1246: zhes pa ni gong ma'o yang rtse 'o mchog go ces so //
NK034(ngi)003:1248: spyi mes dang po pha rol mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1250: dkyil 'khor snying po rang spros pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1251: bskal pa gser gyi yi ge la //
NK034(ngi)003:1252: sa ya drug gi phyag rgyar bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:1254: sngon thog dang po 'phags pa mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1256: phyag rgya dngos po nyid snang bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1259: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1261: 'jig rten d+r+wa ba mgon po yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1262: spros bral phyag rgya 'di spros te //
NK034(ngi)003:1263: bskal pa me tog mdzes pa la //
NK034(ngi)003:1264: bstan pa'i 'bras bu phyal yas pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1266: snying po stong gi spyi phud mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1268: snying po dam pa'i 'khor lo las //
NK034(ngi)003:1269: bskal pa rtsod pa'i snying po la //
NK034(ngi)003:1270: grangs med bzhi yi snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1271: 'od ldan dang po sems can mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1272: spros med snying po rang sgra las //
NK034(ngi)003:1273: bskal pa snang ba'i sgron ma la //
NK034(ngi)003:1274: ban bun stong phrag phyag rgyar bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:1275: mdzes pa'i dang po 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1276: yang dag snying po rnams spros te //
NK034(ngi)003:1277: bskal pa rags pa'i yan lag la //
NK034(ngi)003:1278: nyar nyer brgya yi grangs kyis ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1279: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1282: 'di bzung nas sangs rgyas phyag rgya mdzad do //
NK034(ngi)003:1284: thugs brtse snying po nyan thos mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1285: phyag rgya yang dag lam spros te //
NK034(ngi)003:1287: bskal pa dung gi sgra dag la //
NK034(ngi)003:1288: greng greng bcu yi dam par ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1289: zhes pa gsungs pa sangs rgya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1291: mi pham zang ma sgra bral mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1292: yang dag nges pa'i rgyud las ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1294: bskal pa d+r+wa ba'i 'od zer la //
NK034(ngi)003:1295: dung phyur gsum rtsa bar bdun /
NK034(ngi)003:1297: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1299: snying po sems rnal bdud rtsi mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1300: nges pa'i sa bon rab bsgrags pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1302: bskal pa tshangs pa'i dbyangs can la //
NK034(ngi)003:1303: 'bur rdul bdun gyis nges par bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:1304: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1306: rang bzhin drag po ting 'dzin mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1307: phyag rgya 'khor lo bden spros te //
NK034(ngi)003:1308: zhes pa rgyud kyi thugs rje /
NK034(ngi)003:1309: bskal pa smra ba'i gzhi dag la //
NK034(ngi)003:1310: phyal phyol dgu yis dam par bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:1311: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1313: gas nga ba phyag rgya lha min mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1314: yang gsang 'khor lo rnams spros te //
NK034(ngi)003:1315: zhes pa rgyud kyi thugs rje /
NK034(ngi)003:1316: bskal pa 'bum pa reg ldan la /
NK034(ngi)003:1317: yal yol drug cus snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1318: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1320: rim pa lnga pa gtsug phud mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1322: bla med snying po yongs spros pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1323: zhes pa sems can rnams la rgyud 'di gsungs shing reg pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1324: bskal pa yang gsal rab 'byams la //
NK034(ngi)003:1325: khrag khrig bye ba dgu brgya yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1327: bla na med pa'i gsang ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1330: 'jig rten thog ma shes rab mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1331: bde chen snying po yongs spros te //
NK034(ngi)003:1332: zhes pa rgyud gsungs shing bsgrags pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1333: bskal pa bkod pa chen po la //
NK034(ngi)003:1334: 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhi yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1335: zhes pa lha tshangs chen gyi 'gro ba'i grangs /
NK034(ngi)003:1336: lha yi lhar ni 'di nyid do //
NK034(ngi)003:1337: zhes pa 'dus byas kyi lha rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:1338: 'dus ma byas rigs lnga'i tshom bur grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:1340: 'chang ba rnams kyis thog ma mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1342: zhes pa rgyud 'di 'gro ba rnams btags pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1343: bskal pa rin chen spungs pa la //
NK034(ngi)003:1344: sa ya dgu bcu'i mgon po yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1345: rgyas par basngagasa te dam par ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1346: zhes pa sa ya dgu bcu grol te sangs rgyas par ston pas don rgyas par grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:1349: dngos po bsgyur ba'i phyag rgya ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1350: zhes pa zag bcas zag med du sangs rgya ba la zer ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1351: snying po nyid du spros pa la //
NK034(ngi)003:1352: zhes pa chos thams cad kyi yang snying du gsungs pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1353: bskal pa rab tu g.yo med la //
NK034(ngi)003:1354: rab mtha' bcu yi mgon po yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1356: snying po snying gi dwangs mar ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1357: zhes pa rgyud 'di shes rig kun bzang gi rang mdangs thig le lnga'o zhes pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1359: chags med rdul bral dri med mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1360: gsang chen nges pa'i nyid du ste //
NK034(ngi)003:1361: zhes pa rgyud chen 'di babs te /
NK034(ngi)003:1362: bskal pa g.yo sgyu bral ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:1363: bye ba dgu khri'i grangs mgon gyis //
NK034(ngi)003:1364: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1368: dran pa dri med bsam gtan mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1369: dri med nges pa'i gsang tshig spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1371: bskal pa mtha' ldan seng ge la //
NK034(ngi)003:1372: nyal nyil sum cu'i rgyal ba yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1373: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1374: 'di ni bden tshig dam par ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1375: zhes pa don dam pa'i gsung rab byon no //
NK034(ngi)003:1377: dam pa'i skyes bu chos kyi mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1378: sangs rgyas shes rab sa bon spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1379: zhes rgyud 'di gsungs shing btags pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1380: bskal pa gdung ba sel ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:1381: sang seng dgu khri'i gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1382: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1383: dam pa'i phyag ni yang dam du'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1386: spyi phud stong gi ye thog mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1387: sngags kyi rtsa ba 'di basngagasa pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1389: bskal pa dung gi snying po la //
NK034(ngi)003:1390: kha yel stong gi gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1391: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1392: gsang chen dam par rab bzung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1393: zhes pa phyag gi gnas mdzad do //
NK034(ngi)003:1395: sangs rgyas d+r+wa ba mgon po yis //
NK034(ngi)003:1396: phyag rgya nyid du gdung bzung bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1398: bskal pa bye ba'i snying po la //
NK034(ngi)003:1399: nyag thag khri yi gdung 'dzin pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1402: zhes pa nges pa'i 'gro don la dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1404: yang dag gsang ba pad+ma mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1405: snying gi snying po dkyil bzung bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1406: zhes pa rgyud 'di gsang ba bla med kyi yang snying yin pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1407: bskal pa yongs su brtse ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:1408: deng ding stong gi yang 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1409: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1410: 'di ni snying la yang dag spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1411: zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gcig tu dril ba bstan pa'i bu gcig po /
NK034(ngi)003:1413: sems can snying brtse me tog mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1414: dran gzhi dang po rab bzung bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1416: bskal pa yod pa rab mchog la //
NK034(ngi)003:1417: rdul med dgu yi gsang 'dzin pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1418: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1419: gsang chen stong gi dam par ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1420: zhes pa sangs rgyas stong gis phyag mdzad pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1422: bskal pa d+r+wa ba nyi 'od mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1423: dam pa'i snying po nges phab pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1425: bskal pa glang po yongs rdzogs la //
NK034(ngi)003:1426: rab rdul nyid kyi rjes 'dzin pas //
NK034(ngi)003:1427: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas shing phyag mdzad do //
NK034(ngi)003:1428: stong nyid gsal ba'i mig tu spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1429: zhes pa phyogs su ma lhung ba'i lta ba /
NK034(ngi)003:1430: gnyis su med pa'i sgom pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1431: gol sgrib bral ba'i spyod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1435: yongs rdzogs 'khor lo rigs kyi mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1436: sems kyi dngos po dam par bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:1438: bskal pa bla na med pa la //
NK034(ngi)003:1439: khri phrag drug cu'i gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1440: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1442: zhes pa sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo //
NK034(ngi)003:1444: dri med dag pa chos kyi mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1445: yang gsang nges pa'i lung 'di spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1446: zhes pa rgyud 'di gsungs shing btags pas /
NK034(ngi)003:1447: bskal pa rtsod pa rang grol la /
NK034(ngi)003:1448: nyal nyil nyid kyi 'phel gdung gis //
NK034(ngi)003:1449: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1450: rim pas mngon par rab spros pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1451: zhes pa dam pa rigs brgya rig pa'i mdangs yin yang theg pa'i blo dang lha ngo bstun no //
NK034(ngi)003:1453: yang gsang dang po thog ma mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1454: rdo rje yang dag dam bzung bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1456: bskal pa khyung chen gshog rdzogs la //
NK034(ngi)003:1458: zhes pa 'gro de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1459: phyag rgya rang rdzogs nyid du'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1460: zhes pa phyag mdzad pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1462: snang mdzad dang po mar me mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1463: bla med rdo rje snying po spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1464: zhes pa rgyud 'di gsungs shing spel bas /
NK034(ngi)003:1465: bskal pa mda' yis yongs bzung la //
NK034(ngi)003:1466: rnga yab gsum gyi gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1467: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1468: rigs ldan rnams kyi phyag tu bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:1471: yid shes dang po gnas gsum mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1473: snying thig rtsa ba'i dwangs mar spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1475: bskal pa rig pa'i stobs can la //
NK034(ngi)003:1476: kha yel drug gi gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1477: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas par byas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1478: gong 'phel phyag rgya dam par spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1479: zhes pa nyams su blang tshad dang bcas par gsungs so //
NK034(ngi)003:1481: dpa' bo 'jigs sangs dang po'i mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1482: dri ma med pa'i snying du babs //
NK034(ngi)003:1484: bskal pa dran bsam bral ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:1485: yal yol stong gi gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1486: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas par byas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1487: 'di kun skyon dang bral bar ro //
NK034(ngi)003:1488: zhes pa dri ma med pa'i rgyud la phyag mdzad do //
NK034(ngi)003:1490: drag po chags bral bde ba'i mgon //
NK034(ngi)003:1491: chags med rang rig phyag rgya spros //
NK034(ngi)003:1492: zhes pa rgyud 'di gsungs shing spel bas /
NK034(ngi)003:1493: bskal pa mya ngan bral ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:1494: dung phyur gsum gyi gdung 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1495: zhes pa 'gro ba de tsam zhig sangs rgyas par byas so //

NK034(ngi)003:1840: chen po yi zhes pa thugs rjes kun khyab /
NK034(ngi)003:1841: babs las 'di kun rang byung shar //
NK034(ngi)003:1843: babs las zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1845: rang byung shar zhes pa sus kyang byas pa med
NK034(ngi)003:1846: par nam mkha' la sgra don dbyer med mi phyed
NK034(ngi)003:1847: par / byin rlabs rim pa 'di kun yang //
NK034(ngi)003:1848: zhes byin rlabs zhes pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1849: rim pa zhes pa le'u bdun pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1851: thog ma babs las rang bstan no //
NK034(ngi)003:1853: thog ma zhes pa rgya ma chad pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1854: babs las zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1855: rang bstan no zhes pa ye gdod ma nas so //
NK034(ngi)003:1856: sangs rgyas kyi gdung ji ltar spel ba bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa rdzogs so ////
NK034(ngi)003:1857: da ni le'u gsum pa 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:1858: e ma zhes pa'i don ni /
NK034(ngi)003:1861: gnas lugs dang snang lugs kyi rang sgras sangs rgya ba ngo mtshar che'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1862: zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1863: rang byung chen po'i tshig las kyang //
NK034(ngi)003:1865: rang byung zhes pa sus kyang byas pa med par /
NK034(ngi)003:1866: chen po'i zhes pa gong na med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1867: tshig las kyang zhes pa ngo mtshar che ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1868: 'di ltar rang byung khyad par tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:1871: rang byung zhes pa byas pa med par /
NK034(ngi)003:1872: gzhi gsum las dus gsum kar 'byung ba la brjod do //
NK034(ngi)003:1873: khyad par tshig ces pa chos thams cad la /
NK034(ngi)003:1874: babs las byung zhing shar ba las //
NK034(ngi)003:1876: babs las zhes pa gzhi ka dag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1877: byung zhing zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:1878: shar ba las zhes pa sku dang thig ler /
NK034(ngi)003:1879: rang gsal chos rnams rang byung tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:1881: rang gsal ni sku'i snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:1882: chos rnams zhes pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1883: rang byung tshig ces pa rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs las /
NK034(ngi)003:1884: phyis ni 'di ltar yang dag go //
NK034(ngi)003:1886: phyis ni zhes pa ma 'ongs pa'i dus su lung bstan pa'i rang sgra /
NK034(ngi)003:1887: 'di ltar zhes pa 'di na mar gsungs pa bzhin /
NK034(ngi)003:1888: yang dag go zhes pa rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs las byung ba /
NK034(ngi)003:1889: rgyud dang de yi rang 'grel lo //
NK034(ngi)003:1891: rgyud dang zhes pa sngags phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1892: de'i zhes pa rgyud so so /
NK034(ngi)003:1893: rang 'grel lo zhes pas go lugs so sor phye nas brtsams pa rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:1894: lha sngags la sogs phyag rgya bcu //
NK034(ngi)003:1896: lha sngags zhes pa phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1897: la sogs zhes pa zhi rgyas dbang drag gis drangs pa'i las mtha' bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:1898: ma lus pa la yang brjod /
NK034(ngi)003:1900: de las 'di tshig phrag yas su //
NK034(ngi)003:1902: de las zhes pa gong ma la brten nas /
NK034(ngi)003:1903: 'di tshig ni rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1904: phrag yas su zhes pa grangs /
NK034(ngi)003:1905: snang ba yin no don la sems //
NK034(ngi)003:1907: snang ba zhes pa gang zag gi thugs la /
NK034(ngi)003:1909: don la sems zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1910: snang mdzad don kun rang rdzogs te //
NK034(ngi)003:1912: snang mdzad ces pa thugs la /
NK034(ngi)003:1913: don kun zhes pa ma nor ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1914: rang rdzogs te zhes pa skal ldan de yi sems la /
NK034(ngi)003:1915: tshig kun bdag por rang byung bas //
NK034(ngi)003:1917: tshig kun zhes pa 'khor 'das ma lus pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1918: bdag por zhes pa shin tu mkhas par /
NK034(ngi)003:1919: rang byung bas shes pa sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1920: dgongs pa nyid ni dang po las //
NK034(ngi)003:1922: dgongs pa zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1923: nyid ni zhes pa ma nor bar /
NK034(ngi)003:1924: dang po las zhes pa 'grel ba /
NK034(ngi)003:1925: tshig rtsom mkhas pa 'di las ni //
NK034(ngi)003:1927: tshig rtsom zhes pa dgongs pa 'grel ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1928: mkhas pa zhes pa ma nor bar /
NK034(ngi)003:1929: 'di las ni zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:1932: 'jig rten gyi khams su rig 'dzin 'phags pa rnams dang /
NK034(ngi)003:1934: rnal 'byor pa dang rgyal po dang khyim bdag dang
NK034(ngi)003:1935: bud med dang khye'u chung dang bu mo'i gzugs su
NK034(ngi)003:1936: sprul nas / mtha' med brjod las 'das pa byon no //
NK034(ngi)003:1937: bdag 'dzin bdag med sngon thog las //
NK034(ngi)003:1940: bdag med ces pa rang sangs rgyas la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1941: sngon thog las zhes pa ka dag gi dgongs pa rgyud 'di las /
NK034(ngi)003:1944: mthar 'dzin zhes pa yod med gnyis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1945: 'dod pa zhes pa mu stegs so so rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1946: dgag pa'i phyir zhes pa de dag gi 'dod pa log pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1947: mngon sum rjes su dpags pa yi //
NK034(ngi)003:1949: mngon sum zhes pa mthong byed kyis mthong ba la bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1950: rjes su zhes pa shes byed kyis gnas lugs shes pa la bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1951: dpags pa yi zhes pa sngar mthong byed kyi gnas
NK034(ngi)003:1952: lugs go bas ma mthong yang rtags kyis mtshon pa
NK034(ngi)003:1953: la bya'o // gtan tshigs cha 'dzin tshig kun 'byung //
NK034(ngi)003:1955: gtan tshigs zhes pa dri ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1957: tshig kun 'byung zhes pa pha rol mu stegs sun 'byin pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1958: yid dpyod blo zhen dgag pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:1960: yid dpyod ces pa lha bsgom /
NK034(ngi)003:1961: blor zhen zhes pa rang gi lha sgom la /
NK034(ngi)003:1962: dgag pa'i phyir zhes pa nyan thos rang rgyal gyi 'dod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1963: kun rdzob don dam grangs phye sogs //
NK034(ngi)003:1965: kun rdzob ces pa snang grags kyi chos thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:1966: don dam zhes pa rang gi sems su 'dod pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1967: de'i don dam sems tsam du yang ma grub la mtha' las 'das pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1968: grangs phye sogs zhes pa chos rnams kyi rnam grangs ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1969: tshig ni 'di kun byin rlabs las //
NK034(ngi)003:1971: tshig ni zhes pa theg pa'i 'jug sgo mtha' dag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1973: byin rlabs las zhes pa sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:1974: 'di ltar rtsom pa'i dpa' bo mkhas //
NK034(ngi)003:1976: 'di ltar zhes pa kun rdzob dang don dam du /
NK034(ngi)003:1977: rtsom pa'i zhes pa bstan bcos /
NK034(ngi)003:1978: dpa' bo mkhas zhes pa 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo zlog pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1979: rig 'dzin 'phags pa rnams lung bstan pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1980: sems ni mthar zhen blo dgag phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:1982: sems ni zhes pa ngo bo stong pa'i rtsal ma 'gags par kun la 'jug /
NK034(ngi)003:1983: mthar zhen zhes pa ma dag pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:1984: blo dgag phyir zhes pa mi gtsang ba'i rdzas su 'dod pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1985: phung po grangs dang khams sogs dang //
NK034(ngi)003:1987: phung po zhes pa gzugs kyi phung po /
NK034(ngi)003:1988: grangs dang zhes pa mi gtsang ba lnga po rgyal ba rigs lngar bsgom pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1989: khams sogs dang zhes pas la sogs par yum lngar bsgom pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1990: bstod dang yod med chos dang ni /
NK034(ngi)003:1992: bstod dang zhes pa bla ma dang sangs rgyas dang gnas la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:1993: yod med ces pa thams cad la 'jug pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:1994: chos dang ni zhes pa yod med kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:1995: chos min ji ltar rtsi ba yi //
NK034(ngi)003:1997: chos min zhes pa yang dag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:1998: ji ltar zhes pa snang ngo ma 'gags par /
NK034(ngi)003:1999: rtsi ba yi zhes pa dus tshod ma nor bar /
NK034(ngi)003:2002: tshig kun zhes pa 'khor 'das ma lus pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2004: rab brtson thob ces pa rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs las bslab mi dgos par /
NK034(ngi)003:2007: 'jig rten zhes pa chags 'jig can gyi snang ba la /
NK034(ngi)003:2008: skye 'chi can gyi sems can rten pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2009: mthun 'jug ces pa so so rang rang dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2010: drang ba'i phyir zhes pa chos la /
NK034(ngi)003:2011: sgra dang rig pa du ma yang //
NK034(ngi)003:2013: sgra dang zhes pa brjod pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2015: du ma yang zhes pa ci dang ci'i rnam pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2016: 'di yi rang byung tshig las shar //
NK034(ngi)003:2019: rang byung zhes pa byas pa med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2020: tshig las shar zhes pa rang babs su /
NK034(ngi)003:2021: phyir 'gyur theg pa'i rang grangs kyis //
NK034(ngi)003:2023: phyir 'gyur zhes pa mu stegs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2025: rang grangs kyis zhes pa so so rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2026: dbang po'i 'jug sgo gsal ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:2028: dbang po'i zhes pa rno rtul /
NK034(ngi)003:2029: 'jug sgo zhes pa theg pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:2030: gsal ba'i phyir zhes pa ma nor bar /
NK034(ngi)003:2031: rim pa'i 'jug srol bcu gcig ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2033: rim pa'i zhes pa mas 'dzeg tu /
NK034(ngi)003:2034: 'jug srol zhes pa shan phyed par /
NK034(ngi)003:2035: bcu gcig ni zhes pa theg pa dgu 'jig rten pa gnyis dang bcu gcig go //
NK034(ngi)003:2036: 'di yi yon tan babs las snang //
NK034(ngi)003:2039: yon tan zhes pa sangs rgyas kyii /
NK034(ngi)003:2040: babs las snang zhes pa skal pa can la /
NK034(ngi)003:2041: rang 'od ji ltar yod pa'i tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:2043: rang 'od ces pa rig pa'i rang mdangs mthing ga
NK034(ngi)003:2044: dkar po ser po dmar po ljang khu sna tshogs
NK034(ngi)003:2045: pa / ji ltar zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2046: yod pa'i tshig ces pa sems can thams cad la /
NK034(ngi)003:2047: 'di las spros so nye bar bsdus //
NK034(ngi)003:2050: spros so zhes pa mdo rgyud thams cad kyi nang du /
NK034(ngi)003:2051: nye bar bsdus zhes pa rdzogs pa chen po thig le'i skor du /
NK034(ngi)003:2052: grags dang ma grags tshig bcud ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2054: grags dang zhes pa rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud rnams su /
NK034(ngi)003:2055: ma grags zhes pa mdo rgyud kun dang khyad par mtshan brjod do //
NK034(ngi)003:2056: tshig bcud ni zhes pa chos thams cad kyi khyad
NK034(ngi)003:2057: par du rdzogs pa chen po 'bum phrag drug cu
NK034(ngi)003:2058: rtsa bzhi / 'di las yang gsang chen por yang //
NK034(ngi)003:2061: yang gsang zhes pa zab pa'i yang zab /
NK034(ngi)003:2062: chen por yang zhes pa gong na med pa'i yang rtse rgyud bcu bdun no //
NK034(ngi)003:2063: gyur te snang bar 'gyur ba yin //
NK034(ngi)003:2066: snang bar zhes pa rim pa bzhin du /
NK034(ngi)003:2067: 'gyur ba yin zhes pa'i phyis kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:2068: lha mis ji ltar 'dod pa'i tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:2070: lha mis zhes pa mtho ris gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2071: ji ltar zhes pa rang rang 'dod pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2072: tshig ces pa so sor go ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2073: sgo drug thob 'dod rang bkod tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:2075: sgo drug ces pa rnam par thar pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2077: rang bkod tshig ces pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:2078: sngags lung sems dpa'i lung rab snang //
NK034(ngi)003:2080: sngags lung zhes pa phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2081: sems dpa'i zhes pa rdo rje /
NK034(ngi)003:2082: lung rab snang zhes pa bka' mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:2083: 'di la gsang chen gnad du grags //
NK034(ngi)003:2086: gsang chen zhes pa bcu bdun gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2087: gnad du grags zhes pa rtags mngon du 'byin pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2088: de bzhin skye 'jig bstan bcos dang //
