NK034(ngi)003:2090: de bzhin zhes pa 'di dag la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2091: skye 'jig ces pa nang bcud dang phyi snod kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2092: bstan bcos zhes pa bstan dang bzhag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2093: yod dang med smra sde grangs spros //
NK034(ngi)003:2095: yod par smra ba'i sde sogs /
NK034(ngi)003:2096: sde pa bzhi ru gsungs pa rnams so //
NK034(ngi)003:2097: mtha' gnyis rab 'byed yod snang phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:2099: mtha' gnyis zhes pa yod med kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2100: rab 'byed ces pa dngos por 'dzin pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2102: yod snang phyir zhes pa gzung yul du med kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:2104: dran sems nyid kyi sde grangs ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2106: dran sems zhes pa sems can gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2107: nyid kyi zhes pa de'i don /
NK034(ngi)003:2108: sde grangs ni zhes pa sems med bco brgyad la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2109: 'di kun las byung sems kyi lung //
NK034(ngi)003:2112: las byung zhes pa gong gi tshig thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:2113: sems kyi lung zhes pa chos sku thig le nyag gcig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2114: 'jug sgo chen po'i shing rta yang //
NK034(ngi)003:2117: chen po'i zhes pa mi lus /
NK034(ngi)003:2118: shing rta yang zhes pa khyab pa khams gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:2119: snang ba'i mdzad 'phros kha lo ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2121: snang ba'i zhes pa chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2123: kha lo ni zhes pa sems can 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2127: dam pa'i zhes pa chos la /
NK034(ngi)003:2128: 'khor lo zhes pa sgyur bar byed pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2129: sangs rgyas myur bar yang brjod do //
NK034(ngi)003:2130: grags pa'i sngags dang de spel tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:2132: grags pa'i zhes pa yongs su /
NK034(ngi)003:2133: sngags dang zhes pa phyi nang gnyis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2134: de spel tshig ces pa de'i 'grel pa la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2135: rim pa mdo sde rang grags tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:2137: rim pa zhes pa theg pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2138: mdo sde zhes pa mtshan nyid /
NK034(ngi)003:2139: rang grags tshig ces pa gsang sngags phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2140: bkod pa rnams kyi thog mar ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2142: bkod pa zhes pa yi ge ris su /
NK034(ngi)003:2143: rnams kyi zhes pa chos thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:2144: thog mar ni zhes pa de dag thams cad kyi mdun du /
NK034(ngi)003:2149: phan sems ldan zhes pa rdo rje 'chang gis thog
NK034(ngi)003:2150: drangs pa'i brgyud pa zam ma chad pas 'khor ba
NK034(ngi)003:2151: stongs par bgyis pa'i rang sgra'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2152: lung rgyal theg pa kun dngos so //
NK034(ngi)003:2154: lung rgyal zhes pa chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2155: theg pa zhes pa so so rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2156: kun dngos so zhes pa thams cad gcig tu dril ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2157: gzhi rtsa rtsal gyi nan tan tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:2159: gzhi rtsa zhes pa rang rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:2160: rtsal gyi zhes pa rgyud la /
NK034(ngi)003:2161: nan tan tshig ces pa rgyud 'di 'phyugs pa med pa'i gnad do //
NK034(ngi)003:2162: 'di kun rgyan gyi rgyal po las //
NK034(ngi)003:2165: rgyan gyi zhes pa chos thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2166: rgyal po las zhes pa byas pa med par rang byon /
NK034(ngi)003:2167: gong na med pa'i yang rtse /
NK034(ngi)003:2168: bya rtsol med pa'i dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2169: kha lo sgyur ba'i dpa' bo yin //
NK034(ngi)003:2171: kha lo zhes pa sems can gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2172: sgyur ba'i zhes pa sangs rgyas la /
NK034(ngi)003:2173: dpa' bo yin zhes pa rgyud 'di btags pa tsam gyis 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo bzlog pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2176: byed pa'i zhes pa lto gos gnyis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2177: las rgyas zhes pa de gnyis kyi zhar la /
NK034(ngi)003:2178: dkyil 'khor 'jug ces pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK034(ngi)003:2179: sems can rnams kyang rgyud 'di dang 'phrad na gnas
NK034(ngi)003:2180: lugs don gyi / dpe med bris pa'i sgra yig zer //
NK034(ngi)003:2182: dpe med ces pa dang po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2183: bris pa'i zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2184: sgra yig zer zhes pa chos nyid bya rtsol med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2185: su zer na ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum 'dus pa'i rdo rje 'chang /
NK034(ngi)003:2186: grangs mtha' 'geg byed seng phrug go //
NK034(ngi)003:2188: grangs mtha' zhes pa theg pa dgu'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2190: seng phrug go zhes pa rgyud 'dis thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2191: bcos ma'i yang cha de 'phel bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:2193: bcos ma'i zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:2194: yang cha zhes pa nyan thos rnams kyi don /
NK034(ngi)003:2195: yang dag pa'i don rtogs par 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:2196: de 'phel bzung zhes pa byang chub sems dpas /
NK034(ngi)003:2197: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i las rgyas so //
NK034(ngi)003:2199: dpa' bar zhes pa gong nas gong du /
NK034(ngi)003:2200: 'gro ba'i zhes pa skad cig la /
NK034(ngi)003:2201: las rgyas so zhes pa don la thabs dam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2202: mtho dman snyoms pa'i dge 'bras lung //
NK034(ngi)003:2204: mtho dman zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang sems can gyi rang rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:2205: snyoms pa'i zhes pa thig le nyag gcig tu /
NK034(ngi)003:2206: dge 'bras lung zhes pa rgyud 'di dang phrad pa rnams tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2208: sangs rgyas pa'i dus la slebs pa'i skal ba can no //
NK034(ngi)003:2209: des na bla ma sangs rgyas su lta'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2210: dpe bral rnams kyi dang po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2212: dpe bral zhes pa yang dag pa'i don la /
NK034(ngi)003:2213: rnams kyi zhes pa rig stong gsal stong grags stong bde stong snang stong la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2214: dang po'o zhes pa ming dang bral ba'i chos nyid /
NK034(ngi)003:2215: ka nas dag pa dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2217: de ltar spros tshig du ma yis //
NK034(ngi)003:2219: de ltar zhes pa thams cad kyi byung khungs /
NK034(ngi)003:2220: spros tshig ces pa thams cad kyi gzhi /
NK034(ngi)003:2221: du ma yis zhes pa ma khyab pa med pa'i dgongs tshig 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:2225: 'dzin pa'i zhes pa rgyun chad med par /
NK034(ngi)003:2226: sprul pa'o zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dngos so //
NK034(ngi)003:2227: 'di gnas na bstan pa gnas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2229: mkha' gsal mkha' dag klong chen gyi //
NK034(ngi)003:2231: mkha' gsal zhes pa mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2232: mkha' dag ces pa 'dzin pa zad pa'i ye shes so //
NK034(ngi)003:2233: klong chen gyi zhes pa chos nyid cer mthong mngon sum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2234: spros pa rnams kyi yang spros las //
NK034(ngi)003:2236: spros pa zhes pa yang gsang bla med /
NK034(ngi)003:2237: rnams kyi zhes pa rdzogs chen skor /
NK034(ngi)003:2238: yang spros las zhes pa mdo rgyud thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:2239: skye sgo rab tu spangs pa yis //
NK034(ngi)003:2241: skye sgo zhes pa skye ba rnam bzhi'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2242: rab tu zhes pa mthong thos reg pa tsam gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2243: spangs pa yis zhes pa a ti'i dgongs pas /
NK034(ngi)003:2244: bla med 'dren pa'i dang por byung //
NK034(ngi)003:2246: bla med ces pa yongs su rdzogs par /
NK034(ngi)003:2248: dang por byung zhes pa nam mkha'i mi mjed yang stengs su /
NK034(ngi)003:2250: bde bas bde ba 'byed pa yi //
NK034(ngi)003:2252: bde bas zhes pa rgyud 'khrul med kyi byin rlabs kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2253: bde ba zhes pa gzhi 'khrul med rtogs par byed pas /
NK034(ngi)003:2254: 'byed pa yi zhes pa rgyud 'di yod med la phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi rtags /
NK034(ngi)003:2255: rigs mthun kun gyi gsang chen yin //
NK034(ngi)003:2257: rigs mthun zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2258: kun gyi zhes pa skal ba can /
NK034(ngi)003:2259: gsang chen yin zhes pa log lta can la gsang ste rang nyid bcang bar bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2260: rigs la gnas shing rigs 'byed pa'i //
NK034(ngi)003:2262: rigs la zhes pa rigs lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2263: gnas shing zhes pa dus rgyun chad med par thig le nyag gcig tu /
NK034(ngi)003:2264: rigs 'byed pa'i zhes pa phyi nang gnyis kar kha dog so sor /
NK034(ngi)003:2265: gtso bo gtso bos blang ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2267: gtso bo zhes pa rang rgyud la nyon mongs pa lnga po gang shas che ba ste /
NK034(ngi)003:2268: gtso bos zhes pa rigs lnga /
NK034(ngi)003:2269: blang pa'o zhes pa rigs kyi bdag por sangs rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:2270: phyir rtags kyang de ltar 'byung ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2271: ka dang rtogs dang rab tu dgongs //
NK034(ngi)003:2273: ka dang zhes pa gzhi'i ka /
NK034(ngi)003:2274: rtogs dang zhes pa rang la ye nas gnas pa de /
NK034(ngi)003:2275: rab tu dgongs zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum ya ma bral bar /
NK034(ngi)003:2276: rim par rgyas dang de rjes ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2278: rim par zhes pa chos sku las longs sku longs sku las sprul sku la /
NK034(ngi)003:2279: rgyas dang zhes pa byang phyogs g.yo ba ldan dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2280: lho phyogs tshal pa skyob dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2281: shar phyogs de ba'i rlung dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2282: nub phyogs brtse ba'i gling dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2283: de rjes ni zhes pa sku'i zhing khams thog ma nas skye ba bzhis gzugs kyi don byed cing /
NK034(ngi)003:2287: rab tu zhes pa rig 'dzin phung po lhag med dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2288: 'phel ba yin zhes pa gang zag gi brgyud pa zam ma chad par /
NK034(ngi)003:2289: rab tu rtogs phyir dkyil 'khor ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2291: rab tu zhes pa phung po lhag med /
NK034(ngi)003:2292: rtogs phyir zhes pa tshe 'di nyid la /
NK034(ngi)003:2293: dkyil 'khor ni zhes pa dbyings gsum 'dus pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2294: dam pa rnams ni 'di las sprul //
NK034(ngi)003:2296: dam pa zhes pa rigs brgya /
NK034(ngi)003:2297: rnams ni zhes pa rig pa tshad la phebs te
NK034(ngi)003:2298: zhi khro mtha' bral gyi sku dang gnyis su med
NK034(ngi)003:2299: pa'i rig 'dzin brgyud pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2300: 'di las sprul zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:2301: thams cad las kyi mtha' rgyas kyang //
NK034(ngi)003:2303: thams cad ces pa khams gsum gyi sems can /
NK034(ngi)003:2304: las kyi zhes pa tshe 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa nas bsags pa'i rnam smin /
NK034(ngi)003:2305: mtha' rgyas kyang zhes pa bsod nams kyi stobs nyams shing bri ste /
NK034(ngi)003:2306: tshe lo yang bcu la thug pa'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:2310: rab tu zhes pa de'i dus su dar ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2311: yang 'phel lo zhes pa ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma dpal 'dzin ma bya bas /
NK034(ngi)003:2312: bstan pa'i snying po rnams bzung ste rgyas par byas nas thams cad grol bar byed do //
NK034(ngi)003:2313: de nas mi gnas rang sa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:2314: 'di tshig byin rlabs brgyud pa yang //
NK034(ngi)003:2317: byin rlabs zhes pa rang bzhin babs kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2318: brgyud pa yang zhes pa de nas bskal pa bye ba na /
NK034(ngi)003:2321: rab tu zhes pa bstan pa'i snying po snying thig gsang ba 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:2322: 'phel phyir zhes pa de'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:2323: 'byung ba'o zhes pa 'khor lo glog gi phreng ba
NK034(ngi)003:2324: bya ba'i bcom ldan 'das la snang zhing babs te
NK034(ngi)003:2325: / yang bstan pa'i me ro langs so //
NK034(ngi)003:2326: 'dul ba'i bstan pa bskal pa gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:2327: mdo sde'i bstan pa bskal pa brgya /
NK034(ngi)003:2328: de nas ston pa 'da' tshul bstan te mun pa'i bskal pa gnyis 'byung /
NK034(ngi)003:2329: de nas ston pa sku 'khrungs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2330: mngon pa'i bstan pa bskal pa brgya 'byung ste /
NK034(ngi)003:2331: de'i dus su mngon sum snying thig gi dgongs pa rang bzhin babs kyi byin brlabs las /
NK034(ngi)003:2332: rang ngo shes nas thams cad tshe gcig la sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu thob bo //
NK034(ngi)003:2333: 'di nas 'khor ba dong sprug ste 'gro ba drug tu snang ba med do //
NK034(ngi)003:2334: bskal pa stong phrag nyi shur sems can 'khor ba rgyun chad nas lus can rnams mi snang ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:2335: de nas las kyi bye brag nyon mongs pa bag
NK034(ngi)003:2336: la nyal phra mo langs nas sngar gyi 'khor 'das
NK034(ngi)003:2338: phyis ji ltar 'byung ba bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa rdzogs so ////
NK034(ngi)003:2341: da ni le'u bzhi pa 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:2342: e ma hoh zhes pa'i don ni /
NK034(ngi)003:2343: e bya rtsol med pa'i don la /
NK034(ngi)003:2344: ma rang gsal gting bkrag phyed pa'i mtshar ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2345: ho mtha' dbus phyogs dang bral ba'i chen po'i rang sgra'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2346: 'di ltar yang gsang don nyid la //
NK034(ngi)003:2348: 'di ltar zhes pa rgyud don rig pa mngon sum gyi gnas bstan pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2349: yang gsang zhes pa chos nyid mngon sum gyi don
NK034(ngi)003:2350: log lta can gyi rigs la gsang ba bas kyang
NK034(ngi)003:2351: ches gsang ste rlung gi phyogs tsam du yang brjod
NK034(ngi)003:2352: par mi bya'o // don nyid la zhes pa bar
NK034(ngi)003:2353: do dang tshe phyi ma tsam la mi ltos par
NK034(ngi)003:2354: par mi bya'o // / dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gnas lugs /
NK034(ngi)003:2355: dge sdig kun dang bral ba'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2358: 'jug par zhes pa theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK034(ngi)003:2359: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi lta phugs /
NK034(ngi)003:2360: man ngag thams cad kyi nying khu /
NK034(ngi)003:2361: 'bras bu thams cad kyi mnga' bdag /
NK034(ngi)003:2362: yod med gcig bral gyi lta ba nam mkha'i mdung skor /
NK034(ngi)003:2363: sku gsum lag 'chang zag bcas mi snang bar lo
NK034(ngi)003:2364: bcu na gdon mi za bar sangs rgya ba'i gsang
NK034(ngi)003:2365: ba snying thig yang gsang dam pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:2366: 'dod pa'i zhes pa rtogs ldan nam rnam 'byor pa'am /
NK034(ngi)003:2377: skal pa rab ces pa tshogs gnyis bsags bsags pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2379: sems can gyi don du thugs bskyed bskyed pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2380: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyis smin zin zin pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2381: sngon du lus ngag yid rnams kyi //
NK034(ngi)003:2383: sngon du zhes pa zag bcas mi snang bar grol bar byed pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2384: lus ngag ces pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2385: yid rnams kyi zhes pa gsum po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2386: mngon par zhes pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:2389: zhen pa zhes pa tshe 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa nas lus ngag yid gsum la /
NK034(ngi)003:2390: bzlog pa'i phyir zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag gi gnad kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2391: sngon du spyod pa brtsam par bya //
NK034(ngi)003:2393: sngon du zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum gyi zhen pa bzlog par bya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2394: spyod pa zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2395: brtsam par bya zhes skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:2396: gcig nas gnyis gsum las mang na mkha' 'gro ma'i bka' chad 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:2399: tha ma yang dben pa'i ri la phyin te /
NK034(ngi)003:2400: tshogs gtor bshams la lus dur khrod kyi rus pa dang dung dang kar sha pa nis brgyan la /
NK034(ngi)003:2401: cang te'u dkrol zhing tshogs dang gtor ma bla ma
NK034(ngi)003:2402: yi dam d+h+aa ki la phul la gsol ba btab
NK034(ngi)003:2403: / yul bdag la gtor ma zhig byin te spyod
NK034(ngi)003:2404: pa rtsom pa la bar chod ma byed cig byas
NK034(ngi)003:2405: / la bka' bsgo / 'byung po la gtor ma zhig byin te brtul shugs kyis bskrad la btang /
NK034(ngi)003:2406: rang nyid phyag na rdo rje'am d+h+aa ki mar bsgoms la /
NK034(ngi)003:2407: e la ma la sogs pa'i yi ges rgyas btab la /
NK034(ngi)003:2408: phata sgra drag po zhig brjod la /
NK034(ngi)003:2409: sngon du lus kyi spyod pa zhag gsum brtsams par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2410: lus ni rgyug dang nyal ba dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2412: lus ni zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2413: rgyug dang zhes pa yar mar phar tshur la /
NK034(ngi)003:2414: nyal dang zhes pa kha sbub dang gan rkyal dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2416: rkang lag bskum pa dang brkyang ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2417: langs dang yan lag bskyod pa dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2419: langs dang zhes pa lkog rtser langs 'phro la thang la sdod pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2421: yan lag ces pa rkang lag bzhi /
NK034(ngi)003:2422: bskyod dang zhes phar tshur dang brkyang bskum dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2423: bskor ba dang ni phyag bya dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2425: bskor ba zhes pa bla ma'i sku rten dang chos khug dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2426: mchod rten dang ri dang brag dang rdo dang sa dang chu dang phyugs dang mi phal pa la'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2427: dang ni zhes pa de rnams la yang /
NK034(ngi)003:2428: phyag bya dang zhes pa shar lho nub byang steng
NK034(ngi)003:2429: 'og lha mi phyugs sa rdo la sogs pa la
NK034(ngi)003:2430: / res rang gi bla ma la yang phyag mi bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2431: yan lag bskor dang mgo sgril dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2433: yan lag ces pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2434: bskor dang zhes pa nang dang phyin ga log dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2435: g.yas g.yon gnyis res mos kyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2436: mgo sgril dang zhes phar hril tshur hril yar kyog mar kyog bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2437: ji ltar dran pa'i las rnams dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2439: ji ltar zhes pa rang gis /
NK034(ngi)003:2440: dran pa'i zhes pa snying la /
NK034(ngi)003:2441: las rnams dang zhes pa lhag ma med par /
NK034(ngi)003:2442: gar dang phyag rgya bsgyur ba dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2444: gar dang zhes pa zhi khro dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2446: phyag rgya zhes pa zhi khro dang yod pa med pa tshogs dang gtor ma dang 'khrig pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2447: shog cig pa dang ma yong zhig bya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2448: bsgyur ba dang zhes pa phyag 'tshal 'phro la bang
NK034(ngi)003:2449: rgyug pa dang rgyug 'phro la mgo sgril ba la
NK034(ngi)003:2450: sogs pa'o // ji ltar dmigs pa'i las rnams bya //
NK034(ngi)003:2452: ji ltar zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2453: dmigs pa'i zhes pa yid la /
NK034(ngi)003:2454: las rnams bya zhes pa dran tshad /
NK034(ngi)003:2455: 'di ltar su yis byas pa'i mi //
NK034(ngi)003:2457: 'di ltar zhes pa lus kyi spyod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2458: su yis zhes pa skal ldan /
NK034(ngi)003:2459: byas pa'i zhes pa nyams len /
NK034(ngi)003:2460: lus kyi mngon zhen rang bcad nas //
NK034(ngi)003:2462: lus kyi zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2463: mngon zhen zhes pa tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2464: rang bcad nas zhes pa de ltar byas pas /
NK034(ngi)003:2465: lus kun ru shan phyed par ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2467: lus kun zhes pa bzang ngan dang mdzes sdug dang
NK034(ngi)003:2468: mi phyugs kyi chags sdang thams cad tig med du
NK034(ngi)003:2471: phyed par ni zhes pa 'di nyid du /
NK034(ngi)003:2475: 'gyur ro zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra bzhin nyams su blangs na /
NK034(ngi)003:2476: sprul pa'i sku zhes pa rdo rje 'chang nas brgyud
NK034(ngi)003:2477: pa zam ma chad pa la chos nyid kyi rang
NK034(ngi)003:2478: sgra byung ba'o // des ni lus bya rtsol med par rtogs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2479: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsal stong dbyer med
NK034(ngi)003:2480: gnyis su med par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod do
NK034(ngi)003:2481: // de 'das ngag gi spyod pa brtsam //
NK034(ngi)003:2483: de 'das zhes pa lus kyi dri ma dag pa'i rtags /
NK034(ngi)003:2484: nam mkha' la sprin dang khu rlangs kha char dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2486: dgra dang chom rkun med par /
NK034(ngi)003:2487: nam mkha' dwangs pa rlung dang ser bu med par
NK034(ngi)003:2488: 'ja' dang 'od du 'khrugs pa byung na lus kyi
NK034(ngi)003:2490: gong ma rnams log nas byung na bskyar la bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2492: ngag gi zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2493: spyod pa brtsam zhes pa zhag gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:2494: sngags dang kha ton chos kyi sgra //
NK034(ngi)003:2496: sngags dang zhes pa lha thams cad dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2498: kha ton zhes pa bstod pa dang smon lam dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2501: chos kyi sgra zhes pa 'chad pa slob pa'i lad mo bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2502: yod dang med dang snang ba dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2504: yod dang zhes pa chos yod nor yod grogs yod zas yod ces pa smra'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2505: de'i mjug la nad yod gdon yod mi dge ba yod ces smra'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2506: med dang zhes pa chos med nor med grogs med
NK034(ngi)003:2507: zas med gos med las med sems med mi dge
NK034(ngi)003:2509: snang ba dang zhes pa sangs rgyas snang ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:2511: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' snang ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:2513: mi snang ngo zhes pa sangs rgyas dang 'khor ba mi snang ba bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2514: yid dpyod tshig ni sna tshogs brjod //
NK034(ngi)003:2516: yid dpyod ces pa dran tshad /
NK034(ngi)003:2517: tshig ni zhes pa ci byung byung /
NK034(ngi)003:2518: sna tshogs kha ru thon tshad gdon no //
NK034(ngi)003:2520: byol song sna tshogs brda skad dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2522: byol song zhes pa yang dag pa'i don la byol
NK034(ngi)003:2523: nas ngan pa sdug bsngal gyi las la song ba'o
NK034(ngi)003:2524: // sna tshogs zhes pa rta dang glang po la sogs pa'i dud 'gro thams cad dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2525: dom dred spre'u ce spyang khyi la sogs pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2526: kang ka rma bya rgod la sogs pa'i bya thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2527: brda skad dang zhes pa de rnams kyi zas za ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2528: 'khrig pa spyod pa dang phrug gu yod pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2529: skad ni rnam pa sna tshogs pa //
NK034(ngi)003:2531: skad ni zhes pa gong ma rnams kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2532: rnam pa zhes pa so so rang rang gi 'dra ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2533: sna tshogs pa zhes pa de dag thams cad kyi skad gdon no //
NK034(ngi)003:2534: 'di ltar su yis byas pa'i mi //
NK034(ngi)003:2536: 'di ltar zhes pa skad sna tshogs dang yod med dang chos 'chad pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2537: sngags brjod pa la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2538: su yis zhes pa skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:2539: byas pa'i mi zhes pa nyams su blangs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2540: ngag gi mngon zhen rang chod nas //
NK034(ngi)003:2542: ngag gi zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2543: mngon zhen zhes pa tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2544: rang chod nas zhes pa spyod pa byas /
NK034(ngi)003:2547: 'khor 'das zhes pa gtan gyi bde sdug gnyis so //
NK034(ngi)003:2548: ru shan zhes pa 'dzin pa yod med do //
NK034(ngi)003:2549: 'dis phyed do zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra bzhin nyams su blangs na /
NK034(ngi)003:2550: ngag bya rtsol med par rtogs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2551: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung brjod du med pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2552: gnyis su med par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK034(ngi)003:2553: de ltar rang nyid nyams su blangs par 'gyur la
NK034(ngi)003:2554: gzhan dag bden zhen gyi ko long dang rang bral
NK034(ngi)003:2555: bar 'gyur ro // de 'das nyid kyi 'og tu yang //
NK034(ngi)003:2557: de 'das zhes pa ngag ni ru shan phyed pa'i rtags thon nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2558: nyid kyi zhes pa bar du lus ngag yid gsum rnal du dbab bo //
NK034(ngi)003:2559: de yang lus kyi zhag gsum thal nas zhag gcig lus rnal du dbab ste /
NK034(ngi)003:2560: mal stan bde ba la nyal la bsdad do //
NK034(ngi)003:2561: ngag gi zhag gsum song ba dang zhag gcig gis
NK034(ngi)003:2562: ngag rnal du dbab ste su la'ang mi smra bar
NK034(ngi)003:2563: brda tsam yang mi bya bar lus dang bstun no
NK034(ngi)003:2564: // de bzhin sems ru shan 'byed pa zhag gsum tshar nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2565: yang zhag gcig sems rnal du 'bebs tsam na lus ngag yid gsum phrugs la /
NK034(ngi)003:2566: dran bsam 'phro bcad la bzhag go //
NK034(ngi)003:2567: 'og tu yang zhes pa zhag brgyad song ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2568: sems kyi spyod pa brtsam par bya //
NK034(ngi)003:2570: sems kyi zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2571: spyod pa zhes pa zhen pa 'brel ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2572: brtsam par bya zhes pa zhag gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:2573: dga' dang mi dga' bde sdug dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2575: dga' dang zhes pa yod pa la bsam pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2576: mi dga' zhes pa med pa dang shi na snyam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2577: bde sdug dang zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum bde bar bsgom sdug par bsgom pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2578: rtag dang mi rtag la sogs pa //
NK034(ngi)003:2580: rtag dang zhes pa thams cad rtag par bsgom pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2581: mi rtag ces pa thams cad mi rtag par bsgom pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2582: la sogs pa zhes pa bsam spyod kyi sgom dran par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2583: lta sgom spyod pa'i bsam pa dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2585: lta sgom zhes pa mtha' dang bral ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2586: gsal 'grib med par khyer bsgom bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2587: res 'dus pa dang rmugs par khyer bsgom bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2588: spyod pa'i zhes pa shugs 'byung dang 'dus par bsgom mo //
NK034(ngi)003:2589: bsam pa dang zhes pa yar log mar log tu bsgom mo //
NK034(ngi)003:2590: chos dang chos min la sogs dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2592: chos dang zhes pa dge ba'i phyogs bsam pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2593: chos min zhes pa mi dge ba bsam pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2594: la sogs dang zhes pa thams cad bsam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2595: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2597: 'dod chags zhes pa lus kyi yul du reg bya 'jam pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2598: mig gi yul du gzugs sdug pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2599: rna ba'i yul du sgra snyan pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2600: sna'i yul du dri zhim pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2601: lce'i yul du ro mngar ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2602: de dag thams cad dril nas pho mo'i 'khrig pa'i bde ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2603: de dag la sogs pa bsam mo //
NK034(ngi)003:2604: zhe sdang zhes pa 'thab pa dang rtsod pa 'phrog pa'i bsam pa bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2605: gti mug ces pa mi shes pa mi gsal ba 'thibs pa nyog pa bying ba'i bsam pa bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2606: dge dang mi dge la sogs pa //
NK034(ngi)003:2608: dge dang zhes pa bsod nams kyi tshogs gsog pa dang chos bya ba'i bsam pa bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2609: mi dge zhes pa sdig dang rku ba dang 'phrog pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2610: la sogs pa'i zhes pa bsam ngan la sogs pa bsgom par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2611: bsam spyod rnam pa sna tshogs bya //
NK034(ngi)003:2613: bsam spyod ces pa dran tshad la /
NK034(ngi)003:2614: rnam pa zhes pa mi 'dra ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2615: sna tshogs bya zhes pa spro zhing bsgom par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2616: de yang dge 'phro la mi dge ba yags 'phro la mi yags pa bsgom par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2617: 'di ltar su yis byas pa'i mi //
NK034(ngi)003:2619: 'di ltar zhes pa sems kyi spyod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2620: su yis zhes pa skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:2621: byas pa'i mi zhes pa nyams su blangs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2622: sems kyi mngon zhen rang chod nas //
NK034(ngi)003:2624: sems kyi zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2625: mngon zhen zhes pa tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2626: rang chod nas zhes pa nyams su blangs pa tsam gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2629: 'khor 'das zhes pa khams gsum gyi sems can dang sku dang zhing khams so //
NK034(ngi)003:2630: ru shan zhes pa dag ma dag gnyis so //
NK034(ngi)003:2631: phyed pa'o zhes pa 'dzin pa bral ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2632: de nas zhag gcig sems rnal du phab la zhag
NK034(ngi)003:2633: bcu gnyis su ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa brtsam
NK034(ngi)003:2634: mo // de ltar lo re lan re ci la thug kyang bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2635: des ni sems bya rtsol med par rtogs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2636: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs bsam du med pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2637: gnyis su med par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK034(ngi)003:2638: de ltar sngon du 'gro byas nas //
NK034(ngi)003:2640: de ltar zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum ru shan phye bas /
NK034(ngi)003:2641: sngon du zhes pa chos nyid mngon sum du ngo sprod pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2642: 'gro byas nas zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK034(ngi)003:2643: zhen pa log par de ma byas na zhen pa
NK034(ngi)003:2644: ma log pas bsgom du mi 'dod do //
NK034(ngi)003:2645: des na spyod pa rtsom pa gnad rab tu che'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2646: mngon sum don la lta ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:2648: mngon sum zhes pa dbang po'i spyod yul du mngon
NK034(ngi)003:2649: la gang mngon na chos sku longs sku sprul sku
NK034(ngi)003:2650: gsum / don la zhes pa ma nor ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2651: lta ba'i phyir zhes pa nang gi nam mkha' rig pa'i ye shes tsit+ta nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2652: bar gyi nam mkha' rtsa sbug la btsud de /
NK034(ngi)003:2653: phyi'i nam mkha' rlung dang ser bu med pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:2655: lus dang ngag yid rab tu gcun //
NK034(ngi)003:2657: lus dang zhes pa 'dug stangs gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:2658: ngag yid ces pa bslab par bya ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2660: gtad pa'i 'ben dang ma bral bar /
NK034(ngi)003:2661: rab tu gcun zhes pa bya ba dgu phrugs su btang la /
NK034(ngi)003:2662: lus ni seng ge lta bu dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2664: lus ni zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2665: seng ge zhes pa chos sku'i bzhugs stangs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2666: lta bu dang zhes pa tsog tshugs su 'dug ste
NK034(ngi)003:2667: lag pa gnyis rkang pa'i nang na mar btsugs la
NK034(ngi)003:2668: / mjing pa en tsam dgye bar bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2669: drang srong dang ni glang chen tshul //
NK034(ngi)003:2671: drang song zhes pa ni sprul sku'i bzhugs stangs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2672: dang ni zhes pa ni sprul sku'i bzhugs stangs tsog
NK034(ngi)003:2673: pu byas la lag pa gnyis pus mo la bsnol
NK034(ngi)003:2674: la 'khyud do // glang chen tshul zhes pa longs sku'i bzhugs stangs te /
NK034(ngi)003:2675: glos phabs la nyal te lag pa gnyis kyi gru
NK034(ngi)003:2676: mo sa la btsugs la lag pa'i mthil gyis og
NK034(ngi)003:2677: ko brten / rkang pa gnyis pus brang sbyar la phyir phul ba bzhin bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2678: 'di las g.yo bar ma byas na //
NK034(ngi)003:2680: 'di las zhes pa bzhugs stangs gsum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:2681: g.yo bar zhes pa dus rgyun du /
NK034(ngi)003:2682: ma byas na zhes pa gzhan /
NK034(ngi)003:2683: sangs rgyas sum stong nyid dang yang //
NK034(ngi)003:2685: sangs rgyas zhes pa sku gsum gyi 'dzin pa sangs nas phyogs bral ka dag tu rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2686: sum stong zhes pa grangs so //
NK034(ngi)003:2687: nyid dang yang zhes pa rang la ye nas gnas pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2688: skal ba dag ni mnyam pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:2690: skal ba zhes pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2691: dag ni zhes pa rang dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2692: mnyam pa yin zhes pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:2693: ngag ni ji ltar lkugs pa bzhin //
NK034(ngi)003:2695: ngag ni zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2697: lkugs pa bzhin zhes pa gzhan la mi smra bar /
NK034(ngi)003:2698: su dang brda tsam nyid mi bya //
NK034(ngi)003:2700: su dang zhes pa 'gro ba che chung med par /
NK034(ngi)003:2701: brda tsam zhes pa yi ge dang lag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2702: nyid mi bya zhes pa rbad kyis bcad do //
NK034(ngi)003:2703: chags sdang gi dmag srung ba'i lcags ri yin pas gal che'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2704: ma tshugs na ngag ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa brtsam par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2705: des ngag gi chags sdang rang grol la /
NK034(ngi)003:2707: 'di ltar su yis byas pa'i mi //
NK034(ngi)003:2709: 'di ltar zhes pa smra ba bcad pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2710: su yis zhes pa skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:2711: byas pa'i mi zhes pa nyams len /
NK034(ngi)003:2714: sems kyi zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2716: rang chod do zhes pa ngag bcad pas /
NK034(ngi)003:2717: 'di ltar lus ngag sus gcun pa //
NK034(ngi)003:2719: 'di ltar zhes pa gong du bstan pa'i gnad /
NK034(ngi)003:2720: lus ngag ces pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2721: sus gcun pa zhes pa dben pa'i gnas su /
NK034(ngi)003:2722: chos kyi dbyings kyi snang ba la //
NK034(ngi)003:2724: chos kyi zhes pa ngo bo brjod las 'das pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2725: dbyings kyi zhes pa rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2726: snang ba la zhes pa thugs rje kun khyab kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2729: 'di yis zhes pa nyams su len tshul /
NK034(ngi)003:2730: goms par zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:2731: 'gyur ba yin zhes pa 'di nyid du /
NK034(ngi)003:2732: de ltar lus la sogs pa yi //
NK034(ngi)003:2734: de ltar zhes pa nyams len /
NK034(ngi)003:2735: lus la zhes pa wa mo'i zur 'gros /
NK034(ngi)003:2739: sogs pa yi zhes pa bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs gang 'thad pa bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2740: gnad kun rab tu gzir ba yis //
NK034(ngi)003:2742: gnad kun zhes pa nyams su len pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2743: rab tu zhes pa lus dang ngag dang yid dang rlung dang sgo dang yul /
NK034(ngi)003:2744: gzir ba yis zhes pa rab tu dben zhing btsan pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2745: dom dred dang ni mi rgod kyi 'gyu ba med pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2746: kha shar lho'am lho nub bam lhor lta ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2747: ha cang dma' zhing 'thibs pa ma yin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2748: ha cang mtho zhing grang ba ma yin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2749: rlung ser bu'i bshor med cing nam mkha' rgya che ba'i gnas su /
NK034(ngi)003:2750: rig pa nyid dang mngon sum du //
NK034(ngi)003:2752: rig pa zhes pa gzhi 'dzin pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2754: nyid dang zhes pa 'byed byed kyi shes rab dang bcas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2755: mngon sum du zhes pa dbang po'i spyod yul du mngon pas gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:2756: bla ma'i lung las shes pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:2758: bla ma'i zhes pa chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2759: lung las zhes pa ngo sprod pa'i dus su slob
NK034(ngi)003:2760: ma bzhugs stangs dang gzigs stangs byed du bcug la
NK034(ngi)003:2761: nam mkha' la ci mthong shod cig byas pas /
NK034(ngi)003:2762: shes pa yin zhes pa snang ba gzhan dang mi 'dra ste /
NK034(ngi)003:2765: dper na gayu'am gser sbram rnyed pa'am /
NK034(ngi)003:2766: mdzes mthun nang 'phrad pa lta bu 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:2767: dbyings dang rig pa'i lta stangs ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2769: dbyings dang zhes pa nang dbyings tsit+ta /
NK034(ngi)003:2770: bar dbyings rtsa shel gyi sbu gu /
NK034(ngi)003:2771: phyi'i dbyings nam mkha' stong pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2772: rig pa zhes pa lu gu rgyud kyi gnad /
NK034(ngi)003:2773: lta stangs ni zhes pa chos sku'i lta stangs ldog pa'i tshul du lta ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2774: longs sku'i lta stangs zur gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2775: sprul sku'i lta stangs phab pa'i tshul gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2776: sgrib byed bral ba'i nam mkha' ltar //
NK034(ngi)003:2778: sgrib byed ces pa ri dang sprin dang khu rlangs kha char gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2779: bral ba'i zhes pa de rnams med cing rgya che la dwangs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2780: nam mkha' ltar zhes pa dus rgyun du /
NK034(ngi)003:2782: ngag gi gnad smra ba bcad pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2783: rlung gi gnad dal pa brtan pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2784: sgo'i gnad phab dang ldog dang zur gyis lta ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2785: sems kyi gnad gtad sa'i 'ben dang ma bral bar /
NK034(ngi)003:2786: dbyings kyi nang du lu gu rgyud //
NK034(ngi)003:2788: dbyings kyi zhes pa nam mkha'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2789: nang du zhes pa mthongs la /
NK034(ngi)003:2790: lu gu rgyud ces pa dper na rin po che
NK034(ngi)003:2791: la mkhas pas byas pa'i lu gu rgyud 'dra ba'am
NK034(ngi)003:2792: / shel dkar gyi me long 'dra ba'am /
NK034(ngi)003:2793: nya mig gi rnam pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:2795: rta rnga'i mdud pa lta bu 'ja' tshon gyi rnam par 'char ro //
NK034(ngi)003:2796: rnam par bzhag cing 'bral mi bya //
NK034(ngi)003:2798: rnam par zhes pa shes pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2799: bzhag cing zhes pa nam mkha' /
NK034(ngi)003:2800: 'bral mi bya zhes pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma dang rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:2801: 'di ltar su yis mthong ba'i mi //
NK034(ngi)003:2803: 'di ltar zhes pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma /
NK034(ngi)003:2804: su yis zhes pa skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:2805: mthong ba'i mi zhes pa nam mkha' la /
NK034(ngi)003:2806: thog ma'i kun tu bzang po dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2808: thog ma'i zhes pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2809: kun tu zhes pa dus gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:2810: bzang po dang zhes pa 'khrul ma myong ba'i sangs rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:2811: skal pa nyid ni mnyam pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:2813: skal pa zhes pa thog ma med pa nas bsod nams bsags stobs /
NK034(ngi)003:2814: nyid ni zhes pa yang dag pa'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2815: mnyam pa yin zhes pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las thams cad do //
NK034(ngi)003:2816: de nas thig le mthong ba yiin //
NK034(ngi)003:2818: de nas zhes pa bsgoms pas /
NK034(ngi)003:2819: thig le zhes pa mi 'gyur zhing kun la khyab pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2820: mthong ba yin zhes pa dang po thig le stong pa'i sgron ma rta rnga lta bu /
NK034(ngi)003:2821: de gtad snang ba gong 'phel bas //
NK034(ngi)003:2823: de gtad ces pa stong pa'i sgron ma tsak+shu /
NK034(ngi)003:2824: snang ba zhes pa chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2825: gong 'phel bas zhes pa nyams so //
NK034(ngi)003:2826: rang ngo mthong las 'di ltar ro //
NK034(ngi)003:2828: rang ngo zhes pa khregs chod ltos med kyi steng du /
NK034(ngi)003:2829: mthong las zhes pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma /
NK034(ngi)003:2830: 'di ltar ro zhes pa gong nas gong du /
NK034(ngi)003:2831: yar mtshams las ni sor bzhi las //
NK034(ngi)003:2833: yar mtshams zhes pa mig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2834: las ni zhes pa dpral ba nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2835: sor bzhi las zhes pa phar nam mkha' la /
NK034(ngi)003:2836: bral ba'i skyes bu skal bzang ba //
NK034(ngi)003:2838: bral ba'i zhes pa dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma /
NK034(ngi)003:2839: thog ma dkar po lang long las 'od lnga'i snang ba dum bu dum bur snang ba yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:2840: skyes bu zhes pa nyams su len pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2841: skal bzang ba zhes pa tshogs gnyis mthar phyin pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2844: 'khor bar zhes pa de lta bu'i nyams dang ldan nas shi yang /
NK034(ngi)003:2845: 'jug pa zhes pa 'gro ba drug gi mngal du /
NK034(ngi)003:2846: ga la srid ces pa 'di ni phyi'i rtags ston te /
NK034(ngi)003:2847: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing khams su pad+ma las bardzusa te skyes te /
NK034(ngi)003:2848: lo lnga brgya na sangs rgya ba la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:2849: gru chad rnam pa gang snang ba //
NK034(ngi)003:2851: gru chad ces pa yul gru tsam /
NK034(ngi)003:2853: gang snang ba zhes pa 'od lnga'i snang ba gyen 'greng dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2854: rtsibs la shar ba nyin mo dang mtshan mo med bar snang ba yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:2857: sprul pa'i zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2858: yon tan zhes pa 'dzam bu'i gling bye ba phrag
NK034(ngi)003:2859: brgya na sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bye ba phrag
NK034(ngi)003:2860: brgya 'gyed pa / 'di yis 'grub ces pa gong
NK034(ngi)003:2861: ma'i nyams de lta bu dang ldan nas shi yang
NK034(ngi)003:2862: brgya 'gyed pa / / mthong ba'i yul tsam gang snang ba //
NK034(ngi)003:2864: mthong ba'i zhes pa rang gnas nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2865: yul tsam zhes pa nam mkha' dang yul khams /
NK034(ngi)003:2866: gang snang ba zhes pa thig le 'khar phor ram 'khar gzhong ngam /
NK034(ngi)003:2869: tshom bu la ni de bzhin ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2871: tshom bu zhes pa rigs lnga yab yum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2872: la ni zhes pa de lta bu'i nyams dang ldan na /
NK034(ngi)003:2873: de bzhin no zhes pa rig pa tshad la phebs nas 'agro'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2874: phyir snang 'gags pa gang yin pa //
NK034(ngi)003:2876: phyir snang zhes sa rdo ri brag dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2877: rtsi shing nags tshal sa chu me rlung nyi zla skar ma'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2878: 'gags pa zhes pa 'od dang thig le /
NK034(ngi)003:2879: thig le'i nang du rdo rje sems dpa' sku rkyang gis /
NK034(ngi)003:2880: gang yin pa zhes pa skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:2881: lus sems phyed pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK034(ngi)003:2882: skad cig ma ni bcu drug la //
NK034(ngi)003:2884: skad cig ma ni zhes pa kun /
NK034(ngi)003:2885: bcu drug la zhes bzla ba gsum na /
NK034(ngi)003:2888: 'di yang zhes pa lus sems phyed pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK034(ngi)003:2889: de ltar zhes pa rigs lnga tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK034(ngi)003:2890: 'gyur ba'o zhes pa snang ba thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:2891: ma smin la sogs thig le dang //
NK034(ngi)003:2893: ma smin zhes pa thig le stong pa'i sgron ma mthong nas /
NK034(ngi)003:2894: la sogs zhes pa dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma rtsibs shar dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2897: re lde'i rnam pa tsam dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2898: rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2902: mchod rten dang lcags kyu dang mda' dang nya mig dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2903: za 'og gi gur khyim lta bu dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2904: de nas dbyings thog ma dkar po lang long bas /
NK034(ngi)003:2905: de brtags pas kha dog gsal ba'i 'od lngas /
NK034(ngi)003:2906: rang gnas pa'i lung pa tsam mi snang ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:2907: dbyings dang rig pa la nyin mtshan med par snang ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2908: thig le dang zhes pa nyung 'abru'am sran ma'i rdog po'am /
NK034(ngi)003:2911: bse phub tsam du snang ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2912: de bzhin sku la thug gi bar //
NK034(ngi)003:2914: de bzhin zhes pa gong ma'i thig le de rnams
NK034(ngi)003:2915: yul khams tsam du gang ste 'od lnga'i mu khyud
NK034(ngi)003:2917: sku la zhes pa thig le re re'i nang du
NK034(ngi)003:2918: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku rkyang re re snang ngo
NK034(ngi)003:2919: // thug gi bar zhes pa sku rkyang gi snang ba man chod la /
NK034(ngi)003:2920: drug dang bcu dang lnga gsum la //
NK034(ngi)003:2922: drug dang zhes pa dbang po 'bring gis so //
NK034(ngi)003:2923: bcu dang zhes pa dbang po tha mas so //
NK034(ngi)003:2924: lnga gsum la zhes pa dbang po rab kyis so //
NK034(ngi)003:2925: gdon mi za ste longs sku'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2928: za ste zhes pa the tshom /
NK034(ngi)003:2929: longs sku'o zhes pa rig pa tshad la phebs te snang ba thams cad zhing khams su grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:2930: nang lus zad pa'i sar phyin tshe //
NK034(ngi)003:2932: nang lus zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2933: zad pa'i zhes pa zag pa rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:2934: sar phyin tshe zhes pa phyi zad de zhing khams rang snang ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:2935: nang zad de chos med ka dag go //
NK034(ngi)003:2936: bar zad de 'od lus zang thal lo //
NK034(ngi)003:2937: sor mo la sogs de bzhin snang //
NK034(ngi)003:2939: sor mo zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:2940: la sogs zhes pa lus kyi rkang lag thams cad /
NK034(ngi)003:2941: de bzhin snang zhes pa rigs lnga tshom bu'i zhing khams su /
NK034(ngi)003:2944: 'di gtad ces pa rig pa rang gi lus kyi zhing khams la /
NK034(ngi)003:2945: 'byung ba zhes pa sa chu me rlung gis bsdus pa'i sa rdo ri brag dang rang lus 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:2946: rang dengs so zhes pa nam mkha' 'od phung gis
NK034(ngi)003:2947: bkang ste zag bcas mi snang bar thog ma ka
NK034(ngi)003:2949: skye dang 'jug pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK034(ngi)003:2951: skye dang zhes pa rang dbang thob pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2952: 'jug pa'i zhes pa rang dbang thob pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2953: khyad par gyis zhes pa gzhi gcig pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2954: chos kun zad pa'i rang sa la //
NK034(ngi)003:2956: chos kun zhes pa nyams su blang rgyu'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2957: zad pa'i zhes pa gong du 'phel rgyu /
NK034(ngi)003:2958: rang sa la zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2959: ci yang 'dzin pa med par ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2962: 'dzin pa zhes pa sku gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:2963: med par ni zhes pa gang du yang ma grub pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2964: gnas pa yin no sprul pa'i sku //
NK034(ngi)003:2966: gnas pa zhes pa ka dag la /
NK034(ngi)003:2967: yin no zhes pa de'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:2968: sprul pa'i sku zhes pa rdo rje 'chang nas brgyud
NK034(ngi)003:2969: pa zam ma chad par lung bstan pa'i rang sgra'o
NK034(ngi)003:2972: 'di ni zhes pa gdams ngag gi gnad /
NK034(ngi)003:2973: 'jug pa'i zhes pa ma dag pa'i 'khrul pa'i sems dag pa ye shes la /
NK034(ngi)003:2974: shugs kyis dbang zhes pa yang dag pa'i grong 'jug gcig yiin te /
NK034(ngi)003:2975: sems can sum stong la rig pa bcug pas grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:2976: skye ba'i rang dbang sus thob pa //
NK034(ngi)003:2978: skye ba'i zhes pa mtshams med pa'i las byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:2980: rang dbang zhes pa de nyid kyis sangs rgya bar byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2981: sus thob pa zhes chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:2982: de yang de la gtad nas ni //
NK034(ngi)003:2985: de la zhes pa rig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:2986: gtad nas ni zhes pa rang gi sor mo la /
NK034(ngi)003:2987: yang dus 'di ltar byas pa na //
NK034(ngi)003:2989: yang dus zhes pa yang yang /
NK034(ngi)003:2991: byas pa na zhes pa sems can gyi don bya bar dgongs pa yod pa des /
NK034(ngi)003:2992: snang ba'i rang sgra sil skad de //
NK034(ngi)003:2994: snang ba'i zhes pa 'byung ba bzhi'i /
NK034(ngi)003:2995: rang sgra zhes pa 'byung ba so so'o //
NK034(ngi)003:2996: sil skad de zhes pa 'ur shwol /
NK034(ngi)003:2997: sngon du log ste 'khrul par snang //
NK034(ngi)003:2999: sngon du zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3000: log ste zhes pa sa rdo ri brag tu /
NK034(ngi)003:3001: 'khrul par snang zhes pa dang po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3003: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan tsam du /
NK034(ngi)003:3004: 'dis ni sems can don kun byed //
NK034(ngi)003:3006: 'dis ni zhes pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK034(ngi)003:3008: don kun byed ces pa ngo bo'i 'gro don 'khor ba ma stongs par /
NK034(ngi)003:3009: rig pa mnyam par gcig pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3011: rig pa zhes pa gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:3012: mnyam par zhes pa kun tu bzang po nas 'jag ma'i srin bu yan chod /
NK034(ngi)003:3013: gcig pa'i phyir zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3014: stong phrag gsum rnams sems can gyi //
NK034(ngi)003:3016: stong phrag gsum rnams zhes pa grangs so //
NK034(ngi)003:3017: sems can gyi zhes pa 'gro ba che chung med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3020: 'pho ba zhes pa sems can rnams dag pa ye shes kyi sku ru /
NK034(ngi)003:3021: chen po zhes pa ma rdzogs dgu rdzogs /
NK034(ngi)003:3023: 'dis 'grub bo zhes pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3024: de bzhin rim dang cig char gyis //
NK034(ngi)003:3026: de bzhin zhes pa sems can sum stong grol /
NK034(ngi)003:3027: rim dang zhes pa 'das grongs med par bzhugs nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3028: cig char gyis zhes pa rang zag bcas mi snang bar lhag med la grol ba'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:3029: lus ni 'di yis grub pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:3031: lus ni zhes pa zag bcas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3032: 'di yis zhes pa zag med du /
NK034(ngi)003:3033: grub pa yin zhes pa sems can sum stong la /
NK034(ngi)003:3034: rang gi rig pa bcug pas de dag thams cad phung po lhag med du /
NK034(ngi)003:3035: de kun lus zad mtshan las grol //
NK034(ngi)003:3037: de kun zhes pa rig pa bcug pa'i sems can /
NK034(ngi)003:3038: lus zad ces pa zag bcas mi snang bar /
NK034(ngi)003:3039: mtshan las grol zhes pa dngos po dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3043: 'bras bu zhes pa yang dag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3044: nges pa'o zhes pa mthar thug gi don /
NK034(ngi)003:3047: sa mchog ces pa bcu drug rdo rje ka dag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3048: dkyil 'khor zhes pa rang bzhin lhun grub rigs lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3049: chen po 'grub ces pa mtha' bral gong na med pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3050: 'di ltar thabs las yang dag byung //
NK034(ngi)003:3052: 'di ltar zhes pa nyams su len pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3053: thabs las zhes pa chos nyid rang sgra'i gdams ngag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3054: yang dag byung zhes pa phung po lhag med du sangs rgya ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3055: sangs rgyas bsgrub par 'dod pa'i mis //
NK034(ngi)003:3057: sangs rgyas zhes pa ngo bo la gzung yul sangs te thig ler rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:3058: rang bzhin la sgrib g.yogs sangs te sku ru rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:3059: thugs rje la phyogs ris sangs te mkhyen par rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:3061: 'dod pa'i mis zhes pa bka' sdod las kyi rnal 'byor /
NK034(ngi)003:3062: 'di thabs ldan na de bzhin no //
NK034(ngi)003:3064: 'di thabs zhes pa chos nyid rang sgra bstan pa'i bu gcig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3065: ldan na zhes pa skal ba can la /
NK034(ngi)003:3066: de bzhin no zhes pa gong ma sangs ji ltar rgyas pa bzhin nyams su blangs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3067: gzhan spyod snyems byed nyid yin pas //
NK034(ngi)003:3069: gzhan spyod ces pa theg pa thun mong ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3070: snyems byed ces pa ya bral yid dpyod kyi lta sgom /
NK034(ngi)003:3071: nyid yin pas zhes pa sku gsum dbyer med du ma rtogs pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3072: dngos po mthong ba ma yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:3074: dngos po zhes pa rig pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3075: mthong ba zhes pa mngon sum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:3076: ma yin no zhes pa ya ma bral bas so //
NK034(ngi)003:3077: de phyir 'di kun dkon pa'i tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:3079: de phyir zhes pa yid dpyod kyi lta sgom gyis sangs mi rgya bas /
NK034(ngi)003:3080: 'di kun zhes pa yang dag pa'i don /
NK034(ngi)003:3081: sku gsum ya ma bral ba'i gnad /
NK034(ngi)003:3082: rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud mngon sum du ston pa'i rang sgra /
NK034(ngi)003:3083: dkon pa'i tshig ces pa gang na'ang /
NK034(ngi)003:3084: rtag tu rin chen gter 'di ltos //
NK034(ngi)003:3087: rin chen zhes pa dkon pa'i nor bu /
NK034(ngi)003:3088: gter 'di ltos zhes pa sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3089: 'di ltar zad pa la spyod na //
NK034(ngi)003:3091: 'di ltar zhes pa sngar sangs rgyas pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3092: zad pa zhes pa 'od phung du /
NK034(ngi)003:3093: la spyod na zhes pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK034(ngi)003:3094: 'di ni sangs rgyas stong phrag gsum //
NK034(ngi)003:3096: 'di ni zhes pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3097: sangs rgyas zhes pa gong du bshad pa dang mthun no //
NK034(ngi)003:3098: stong phrag gsum zhes pa grangs /
NK034(ngi)003:3099: 'di yis legs par zhal mthong yiin //
NK034(ngi)003:3101: 'di yis zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig gi gnad /
NK034(ngi)003:3102: legs par zhes pa nyams su blangs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3103: zhal mthong yin zhes pa the tshom med par mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:3104: de ltar du sangs rgyas sum stong zhal mthong ba'i nus pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3105: sems can sum stong grol bar nus pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3106: 'di tshig gsang ba nyid las byung //
NK034(ngi)003:3108: 'di tshig ces pa yang dag pa'i don /
NK034(ngi)003:3109: gsang ba zhes pa ma tshor bar nyams su blangs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3110: nyid las byung zhes pa phung po lhag med du sangs rgya ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3111: skyes bu rnams kyis 'di ltar bya //
NK034(ngi)003:3113: skyes bu zhes pa skal ba can /
NK034(ngi)003:3114: rnams kyis zhes pa rjes su zhugs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3115: 'di ltar bya zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra /
NK034(ngi)003:3116: bstan pa'i bu gcig nas gsungs bzhin /
NK034(ngi)003:3117: gsang chen yang gsang dam pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3119: gsang chen zhes pa zab la rgya che bas //
NK034(ngi)003:3120: de yang de bzhin gshegs pa rig pa mchog gi gdung sgrub /
NK034(ngi)003:3121: rigs drug 'khor ba rgyun gcod la 'dod pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3122: rang skad cig gis rdo rje sems dpa' ru bsgoms la /
NK034(ngi)003:3123: thugs dkyil rtsa lnga'i ngo bo pad+ma 'dab bzhi dbus dang lnga /
NK034(ngi)003:3124: dkar mthing ser dmar ljang pa ru /
NK034(ngi)003:3125: rigs lnga yab yum lnga skad cig dran rdzogs su bskyed la /
NK034(ngi)003:3132: a su n+ri du pre tri /
NK034(ngi)003:3133: rigs drug sa bon sbyang zhing rgyal ba'i snying po 'di la zhag bdun bsgrub bo //
NK034(ngi)003:3135: mo h'u t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah a ha ri ni sa /
NK034(ngi)003:3137: +amo sha ma dar te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:3138: +amo d+harma d+ha tu gar+b+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:3139: skyes bu de nyid 'das pa'i tshe na /
NK034(ngi)003:3140: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3141: longs sku nyi zla lta bu dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3142: sprul sku sa gzhi lta bus sems can gyi don 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3143: 'ja' dang 'od du 'khrug cing rus pa la ring bsrel dkar po /
NK034(ngi)003:3147: sha r+ai ram sran ma tsam /
NK034(ngi)003:3148: snying la sna lnga 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3149: 'di ni bsgrubs pas sangs rgya ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3150: yang gsang zhes pa snying thig gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3151: dam pa'o zhes pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra thos pas grol ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3155: tshe 'dir bsgom zhing nyams su blangs pas rtags mthar phyin te /
NK034(ngi)003:3156: zag pa med par bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa rdzogs so ////
NK034(ngi)003:3159: da ni le'u lnga pa 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:3160: e ma zhes pa'i don ni /
NK034(ngi)003:3163: dbyings mi 'gyur ba ngo mtshar che ba'i rang sgra'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3166: 'di ltar zhes pa thun mong gi rtags /
NK034(ngi)003:3167: 'byung 'dod ces pa 'gro ba 'dren pa'i don du /
NK034(ngi)003:3168: skyes bu gang zhes pa skal pa can /
NK034(ngi)003:3169: thabs kyi yan lag 'di lta bu //
NK034(ngi)003:3171: thabs kyi zhes pa 'gro ba 'dren pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3172: yan lag ces pa'i don ma nor ba la 'jug pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3173: 'di lta bu zhes pa bya thabs /
NK034(ngi)003:3174: rnam pa sna tshogs nyid la ni //
NK034(ngi)003:3176: rnam pa zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi rtags kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3177: sna tshogs zhes pa 'gro ba'i don du thun mong gi las /
NK034(ngi)003:3178: nyid la ni zhes pa 'di dag /
NK034(ngi)003:3179: 'di ltar de yi sngon du sbyang //
NK034(ngi)003:3182: de yi zhes pa thun mong gi las kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3183: sngon du sbyang zhes pa rang zhen pa log par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK034(ngi)003:3184: 'di ltar rang gis sngon ma sbyangs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3185: rang nyid 'dod pa'i dbang du shor nyen yod pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3186: sems kyis rim pa ci sbyangs pa //
NK034(ngi)003:3188: sems kyis zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3189: rim pa zhes pa bdun te /
NK034(ngi)003:3190: dang po 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa la bsams te byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3191: gnyis pa 'phral gyi bde sdug dang yun gyi bde ba la bsams te byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3192: gsum pa 'chi ba'i rkyen du ma la bsams te byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3193: bzhi pa tshe 'di'i bya ba thams cad byas pa
NK034(ngi)003:3194: don med du 'dug pa la bsams te byang chub
NK034(ngi)003:3195: kyi sems sbyang / lnga pa sangs rgyas kyi yon tan la bsams te byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3196: drug pa bla ma'i man ngag la bsams te byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3197: bdun pa mi rtog pa la bsams te byang chub kyi sems sbyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3198: ci sbyangs pa zhes pa nyi ma gsum gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig tu nyams su blangs pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3201: 'dis ni zhes pa sems sbyong bdun pos /
NK034(ngi)003:3202: mi rtag ces pa rgyud la khel te /
NK034(ngi)003:3204: byang chub kyi sems sbyangs pa dang pos 'khor ba las blo ldog /
NK034(ngi)003:3205: gnyis pas sdug bsngal las yid 'byung /
NK034(ngi)003:3206: gsum pas dad pa sngon du 'gro /
NK034(ngi)003:3207: bzhi pas bla ma'i gdams ngag la 'jug /
NK034(ngi)003:3208: lnga pas sgom pa la bsran tshugs /
NK034(ngi)003:3209: drug pas bya ba ngan pa la mi 'jug /
NK034(ngi)003:3210: bdun pas ting nge 'dzin gong nas gong du 'phel ba rnams so //
NK034(ngi)003:3211: ji ltar sgra yi rnal 'byor pas //
NK034(ngi)003:3213: ji ltar zhes pa mkhyen pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3215: rnal 'byor pas zhes pa sgra 'byung ba la chu'i rnal 'byor bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3216: sgra gnas pa la sa'i rnal 'byor bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3217: sgra 'jug pa la rlung gi rnal 'byor bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3218: sgra ldog pa me'i rnal 'byor bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3219: sa chu me rlung 'byung ba bzhi //
NK034(ngi)003:3221: sa chu zhes pa lam kham /
NK034(ngi)003:3222: me rlung zhes pa ram yam /
NK034(ngi)003:3223: 'byung ba bzhi zhes pa so so'i yig 'bru dang lha'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3224: sgra don rnams la goms pa yis //
NK034(ngi)003:3231: rnams la zhes pa lnga po la /
NK034(ngi)003:3232: goms pa yis zhes pa 'byung 'jug gnas ldog la /
NK034(ngi)003:3233: rigs drug rnams kyi rang skad kyis //
NK034(ngi)003:3236: rnams kyi zhes pa lha tshangs pa man chod /
NK034(ngi)003:3237: rang skad kyis zhes pa so so rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3240: mngon shes zhes pa 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3242: 'dis 'grub bo zhes pa 'byung ba bzhi'i sgra la brtag cing ha ri ni sa bzlas na /
NK034(ngi)003:3243: zhag rim dus ni rnam drug gis //
NK034(ngi)003:3245: zhag rim zhes pa tshes gcig nas bcu drug tshun chod lha'i skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3246: tshes bdun nas bcu gnyis tshun chod lha min skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3247: bcu gsum nas bco brgyad tshun chod mi'i skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3248: bcu dgu nas nyi shu bzhi tshun chod byol song gi skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3249: de nas zhag gsum yi dwags skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3250: de nas zhag gsum dmyal ba'i skad do //
NK034(ngi)003:3251: dus ni zhes pa lha'i 'jug pa dpyid zla ra ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3253: gnas pa ston zla ra ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3254: ldog pa dgun zla ra ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3257: rnam drug ces pa zhag re la dus chung drug ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3258: skya rengs shar nas nyi ma rtse shar lha'i skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3259: rtse shar nas dros po che tshun chod lha min skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3260: dros po che nas grib chen lhags tshun chod mi'i skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3261: grib chen lhags nas nyi ma dmar thag chod pa tshun chod byol song gi skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3262: nyi ma dmar thag chod nas nam ma phyed tshun chod yi dwags skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3263: nam ma phyed nas skya rengs shar ba tshun chod dmyal ba'i skad /
NK034(ngi)003:3264: mkha' 'gro lnga dang yang sbyar ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3265: de la sogs pa dang gang rung ba zhig gi skad lhang la byung ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3266: rlung 'byung 'jug gnas ldog la brtags pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3267: 'di yi skad kun rang dus shes //
NK034(ngi)003:3270: skad kun zhes pa rigs drug dang mkha' 'gro'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3271: rang dus shes zhes pa so so rang rang gi skad dang skal ba can gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3272: 'grus pa med par sus shes pa //
NK034(ngi)003:3274: 'grus pa zhes pa dus gnad la /
NK034(ngi)003:3275: med par zhes pa ma nor bar /
NK034(ngi)003:3280: da ltar zhes pa skye ba 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:3282: sems rgyud ji ltar shes par 'gyur //
NK034(ngi)003:3284: sems rgyud ces pa dga' mi dga' dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3285: yod med dang nam 'chi gar skye ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3286: ji ltar zhes pa de nyid mkhyen te /
NK034(ngi)003:3287: shes par 'gyur zhes pa mkha' 'gro dang rigs drug gi dus ma nor bar zhar la 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3288: gzhan gyi don byed sprul pa pos //
NK034(ngi)003:3291: don byed ces pa sdug bsngal las grol ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3292: sprul pa pos zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing sprul gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3293: 'di la sngon du ma sbyangs na //
NK034(ngi)003:3295: 'di la zhes pa sgra dang bzhi la dus bzhi /
NK034(ngi)003:3296: sngon zhes pa nyams su len pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3297: ma sbyangs na zhes pa yo gis /
NK034(ngi)003:3298: sprul pa'i sa bon 'jog par ni //
NK034(ngi)003:3301: sa bon zhes pa phan gnod kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3302: 'jog par ni zhes pa khyad par /
NK034(ngi)003:3303: nus pa nyid ni mi thob bo //
NK034(ngi)003:3305: nus pa zhes pa mngon shes kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3306: nyid ni zhes pa cig char /
NK034(ngi)003:3307: mi thob bo zhes pa bsgom longs med par thun mong gi mngon shes /
NK034(ngi)003:3308: yang dag pa'i mngon shes lu gu rgyud nyams su blangs pa las 'byung ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3309: des na 'byung ba'i sgra la bslab //
NK034(ngi)003:3311: des na zhes pa thun mong gi mngon shes 'dod na /
NK034(ngi)003:3312: 'byung ba'i zhes pa sa chu me rlung gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3313: sgra la bslab ces pa 'byung 'jug gnas ldog gi dus la /
NK034(ngi)003:3314: bya byed zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3316: bya byed ces pa bzo dang sgyu rtsal rtsis la sogs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3317: zhen pa zhes pa de dag la /
NK034(ngi)003:3318: bzlog pa'i phyir zhes pa thabs /
NK034(ngi)003:3319: lag ni bya byed sna tshogs bya //
NK034(ngi)003:3321: lag ni zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3322: bya byed ces pa gang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3323: sna tshogs bya zhes pa lag len la bldabs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3324: mkhar khang brtsigs shing 'jog pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3325: sa chu me rlung dang shing lcags la sogs pa'i phan pa rnams dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3326: gnod bya thams cad dgra grogs ma bu rtsi ba la sogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3327: de bzhin 'dus byas rnam pa yis //
NK034(ngi)003:3329: de bzhin zhes pa de'i zhar la /
NK034(ngi)003:3330: 'dus byas zhes pa 'jig pa'i chos can /
NK034(ngi)003:3331: rnam pa yis zhes pa thams cad byas pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3332: dbang po'i mngon zhen bzlog pa ste //
NK034(ngi)003:3335: mngon zhen zhes pa thog ma med pa nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3336: bzlog pa zhes pa sun thon par /
NK034(ngi)003:3337: yul rnams goms pa'i gnad kyis sbyangs //
NK034(ngi)003:3339: yul rnams zhes pa dbang po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3340: goms pa'i zhes pa de rnams la /
NK034(ngi)003:3341: gnad kyis sbyangs zhes pa zhen pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3342: ji ltar gnyid dang rmi lam du //
NK034(ngi)003:3345: gnyid dang zhes pa mtshan mo'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3346: rmi lam du zhes pa 'od gsal du bsre ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3347: dus bzhi 'byung ba'i gnad kyis dbye //
NK034(ngi)003:3349: dus bzhi zhes pa ston dpyid dbyar dgun no //
NK034(ngi)003:3354: gnad kyis dbye zhes pa sa'i dus la rig pa lu gu rgyud spyi bor bzung la nyal /
NK034(ngi)003:3355: chu'i dus la rig pa lu gu rgyud mgrin par bzung la nyal /
NK034(ngi)003:3356: me'i dus la rig pa lu gu rgyud snying khar bzung la nyal /
NK034(ngi)003:3357: rlung gi dus la rig pa lu gu rgyud lte bar bzung la nyal /
NK034(ngi)003:3358: tshad ni gnad la phebs pas bzung //
NK034(ngi)003:3360: tshad ni zhes pa sems bskyed pa dang tshogs gsog
NK034(ngi)003:3361: pa dang gsol ba 'debs pa sngon du btang ste
NK034(ngi)003:3362: / ci dang ci la yang rmi lam yin snyam
NK034(ngi)003:3363: pa this phur du byas pas rmi lam du shes
NK034(ngi)003:3364: / pa'o // gnad la zhes pa de nas dpe
NK034(ngi)003:3365: rtags don gsum gyi ngo sprod tsho la this phur
NK034(ngi)003:3366: / pa'o // du sbyangs pas / phebs pas bzung zhes pa nyin nub med tsa na /
NK034(ngi)003:3367: 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa thams cad zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor yin zhes ngag tu yang brjod /
NK034(ngi)003:3368: yid kyis kyang this phur du byas pas rmi lam du lu gu rgyud dang zhing khams zin te /
NK034(ngi)003:3369: snyam byed kyis lta bas myong byed kyis mthong ste ye yin la slebs pa zhes bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3370: theg pa thun mong pa dang snyam byed gcig kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:3371: myong byed dang ye yin pa gcig pas sprul pa la sogs pa ma dgos so //
NK034(ngi)003:3372: thig le phyi nang bslab bya'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3374: thig le zhes pa thabs shes rab gnyis kyi sa bon /
NK034(ngi)003:3375: phyi nang zhes pa blo che chung gis /
NK034(ngi)003:3376: bslab bya'i phyir zhes pa rlung la /
NK034(ngi)003:3377: de yang pho rlung sna bug g.yas nas rgyu /
NK034(ngi)003:3378: mo rlung sna bug g.yon la rgyu /
NK034(ngi)003:3379: yab yum gnyis med kyi rlung mnyam por rgyu /
NK034(ngi)003:3380: pho rlung gi dus su mi rtog bsgom /
NK034(ngi)003:3381: mo rlung gi dus su grol lam bsgom /
NK034(ngi)003:3382: gnyis med kyis dus su chags lam spyad /
NK034(ngi)003:3383: gang zag rnam pa gnyis don bya //
NK034(ngi)003:3385: gang zag ces pa nyams su len pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3386: rnam pa zhes pa blo che chung /
NK034(ngi)003:3387: gnyis don bya zhes pa grol lam dang chags lam
NK034(ngi)003:3388: gnyis las grol lam pas rang gi bde ba la
NK034(ngi)003:3390: 'od rig la brten nas dbab bzung ldog dgram bde
NK034(ngi)003:3391: stong dbyer med sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang basre'o
NK034(ngi)003:3392: // chags lam pas yab yum gnyis med kyi bde ba nyams su blangs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3393: de yang rig ma mtshan ldan la brten te thig le dbab /
NK034(ngi)003:3394: mtshan ldan ni dkar sangs 'phra ldem chung bar mngon pa ni bde gshegs rigs so //
NK034(ngi)003:3395: sngo sangs bshan pa rdo rje rigs /
NK034(ngi)003:3396: ser sangs gru bzhi rin chen rigs /
NK034(ngi)003:3397: dmar smug so legs skad snyan mig zla gam pad+ma'i rigs /
NK034(ngi)003:3398: lus che 'gros bul gom rlabs che cha cha nas che ba ni las kyi rigs /
NK034(ngi)003:3399: de rnams gang yin kyang dad pa dang brtse sems snying rje che ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3400: blo khog che zhing lta dgongs mtho ba ni mchog go //
NK034(ngi)003:3401: de lta bu la lta rgod 'dzing 'jib mnye snom pas phebs so //
NK034(ngi)003:3402: bsgom pa lha ste zhi khro gang mos su yab yum bskyed do //
NK034(ngi)003:3403: thig le 'dzin pa de ngo bo ste byung sa gnas sa 'gro sa lta ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3404: 'dren pa h+aum ste gsus pa sgal pa la sbyar /
NK034(ngi)003:3407: dmigs pa rtsa gsum na yar zho lud pa ltar spyi bor lan bdun bskyal /
NK034(ngi)003:3408: 'grems pa sprug ste rlung bzung nywa bzhi sgrim mgo lus sprug go //
NK034(ngi)003:3409: skyel so ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3410: rigs lnga tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3411: bcos ma 'dus byas bsgoms pa yis //
NK034(ngi)003:3413: bcos ma zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:3414: 'dus byas zhes pa lus 'dus byas lha yi bsgom /
NK034(ngi)003:3415: ngag 'dus byas h+aum ring h+aum thung /
NK034(ngi)003:3417: bsgom pa yis zhes pa yid dpyod /
NK034(ngi)003:3418: dang po sems g.yeng zhes pa dgag /
NK034(ngi)003:3421: sems g.yeng zhes pa ma chun pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3422: zhen pa dgag ces pa rigs chad pa thugs rjes
NK034(ngi)003:3423: bzung bas gdod rig pa mngon sum la nges shes
NK034(ngi)003:3424: skye'o // 'bras bu cig char ma yin pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3426: 'bras bu zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3427: cig char zhes pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:3428: ma yin pas zhes pa skye ba brgyud par byed do //
NK034(ngi)003:3429: snang ba rim gyis goms par bya //
NK034(ngi)003:3431: snang ba zhes pa gang zag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3432: rim gyis zhes pa dang po byang chub kyi sems sbyangs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3433: snang ba bden med du rtogs par bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3434: de nas bskyed rim bsgoms te sgra grags stong du rtogs par bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3435: de nas rtsa dang rlung bsgoms te /
NK034(ngi)003:3436: lam grol lam chags lam gyis snang ba bde stong du rtogs par bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3437: de nas mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i rig pa mi dran dgu dran 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:3438: phata byas te nyon mongs khyer chod /
NK034(ngi)003:3441: gding grol thog ste nam mkha' lta bur rtogs par bya /
NK034(ngi)003:3442: goms par bya zhes pa lo gnyis gsum du gong ma rnams la /
NK034(ngi)003:3443: mig sman la sogs sgo lnga yi //
NK034(ngi)003:3445: mig sman zhes pa dbang po dwangs byed kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3446: la sogs zhes pa bya thabs lnga /
NK034(ngi)003:3447: sgo lnga zhes pa gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3448: sman gyi rim pa sbyar bar bya //
NK034(ngi)003:3450: sman gyi zhes pa sgo lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3451: rim pa zhes pa so so gang 'dod /
NK034(ngi)003:3452: sbyar bar bya zhes pa dang po mig gi gzugs ni kha dog dang dbyibs so //
NK034(ngi)003:3454: btsod gdus pa'i khan d+ha dang a ru ru'i khan d+ha tsan dan dkar dmar gyi thang chu /
NK034(ngi)003:3455: bya nag mo'i sgo nga'i mar /
NK034(ngi)003:3456: gtsod kyi mig dang ra dkar mo'i 'o ma dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3457: de rnams rim par sbyar la /
NK034(ngi)003:3458: lcags kyi snod du zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig byibs /
NK034(ngi)003:3459: de nas zhag bdun pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3460: gser nas tsam dang g.yu nas tsam gnyis phye bar btags te gong gi rdzas la btab ste dkrugs /
NK034(ngi)003:3461: de nas gos kyis byibs te zhag bcu bzhi nas blta'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3462: de la bal sngo sob kyis yong ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3463: ma byung na phab zho phyed btab nas zhag dgu bzhag pas gong ltar 'ong ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3465: ril bu mtheb rdog tsam byas te bskam /
NK034(ngi)003:3466: de nas kha dog tu bsgyur ba ni ri lu gcig dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3467: skyer pa'i bar shun gyi khan d+ha ru ldong ros
NK034(ngi)003:3468: phul gang yung ba de dang mnyam pa gcig gdu
NK034(ngi)003:3469: / de btsags pa'i khu ba bya nag mo'i sgo nga'i ser po dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3470: bud med nu zho dang sbyar nas mig la nyi
NK034(ngi)003:3471: ma re la lan nyi shu rtsa gcig byugs na
NK034(ngi)003:3472: / nyi ma bdun gyi bar la mnyam pa nyid
NK034(ngi)003:3473: kyi snang bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do
NK034(ngi)003:3474: / // yang spyang tsher ma'i me tog lug mig pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3475: spang rgyan gyi me tog dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3476: man d+ha ra ba'i me tog rnams gdus pa'i khan d+ha dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3477: spang ma bya rgod kyi sor mo mi'i 'o mar sbyar nas gong ltar byugs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3478: chos kyi dbyings kyi snang bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3479: yang sin d+hu ra 'bri mog phyi rtsi smug po
NK034(ngi)003:3480: sbal rgyab kyi khu ba dang rgya shug 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)003:3481: gdus pa'i khan d+ha bya sgong mi'i 'o mar sbyar
NK034(ngi)003:3482: nas gong ltar mig la byugs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3483: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes snang bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3484: yang gong gi ril bu gcig dang bya rgod kyi brun dkar po dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3485: so bya'i sgo nga'i nang gi chu /
NK034(ngi)003:3486: ut+pala dkar po'i me tog spang rgyan dkar po shang
NK034(ngi)003:3487: shang dkar mo se ba'i me tog dkar po rnams
NK034(ngi)003:3489: bya sgong mi'i 'o mar sbyar la gong ltar mig la byugs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3490: me long lta bu'i ye shes snang bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3491: yang gong gi ril bu dang me tog lug ru dmar ser gnyis ka dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3492: thang shing tsan+dana gyi lo ma ram rgya skyegs kyi khu ba dang sbyar la /
NK034(ngi)003:3493: bya sgong mi'i 'o ma dang sbyar la gong ltar mig la byugs na /
NK034(ngi)003:3494: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes snang bar 'gyur ba la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3495: dbyibs ni d+ha ru ra'i 'bras bu bdun dang 'ol
NK034(ngi)003:3496: ma pi pi gcig tsan+dana dmar po'i thang chu khyor
NK034(ngi)003:3497: ba gang / khyi dkar po'i klad pa zho gcig 'dam gyi pad+ma dkar po drug dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3498: bya'i sgo nga'i mar srang phyed /
NK034(ngi)003:3499: chang bzang po bre do bre phyed du gdus pa'i khan d+ha rnams sbyar la /
NK034(ngi)003:3500: 'khar ba'i snod du blugs pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:3501: sa'i dong khru do'i 'og tu zla gcig la bzhag nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3502: de e langs kha bye nas bltas pas spu chung nyung 'bru tsam tal tal yar nas 'ong ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3503: de ma byung na sbrang rgod phul phyed dang do blugs nas zhag gsum mnan no //
NK034(ngi)003:3504: de nas ri lu sran ma tsam byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3505: ri lu gcig dang mtshon cha'i phye ma sbyar nas zos na thams cad mtshon char 'gyur /
NK034(ngi)003:3506: stag gi 'gram pa g.yas pa'i rus pa sbyar nas
NK034(ngi)003:3507: zos na snang ba thams cad stag tu 'gyur bar
NK034(ngi)003:3509: dud 'gro gang gis snang ba byed kyang de'i 'gram
NK034(ngi)003:3510: rus dang sbyar gyin zos pas der 'gyur bar the
NK034(ngi)003:3511: tshom med do // sa'i zhag dang sbyar na sa'i snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3512: tsan+dana gyi me stag dang sbyar na me'i snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3513: chab rom dang sbyar na rlung gi snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3514: chu sna bcu gcig dang sbyar na chu'i snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3515: lhang ma lhang tsher ma dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3516: thod le skor dang sbyar nas zos na /
NK034(ngi)003:3518: rang gi yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa'i sku shel las tshon gang ba byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3519: de'i sku dang sbyar nas zos na /
NK034(ngi)003:3520: snang ba thams cad lha'i skur 'char ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3521: yang lha bzo mkhas pas lhang ma lhang tsher ma
NK034(ngi)003:3522: la rma bya'i khrag gis yi dam gyi lha bris
NK034(ngi)003:3523: nas btsan dug gi dud pas bdug pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3524: 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i yi dam gyi lha ru 'ong
NK034(ngi)003:3525: ste de dang ri lu sbyar nas zos na 'ja'
NK034(ngi)003:3526: tshon dang lha'i sku ru snang ba thams cad du
NK034(ngi)003:3527: 'char ro // ri mo gang 'dod bris de bltas
NK034(ngi)003:3528: nas zos na gang 'dod du snang ba yin no
NK034(ngi)003:3529: 'char ro // // sgra ni bum ldir gyi rnga la brten pas nang gi nyams skye /
NK034(ngi)003:3530: rdza rnga kha mang la brten na phyi'i nyams skye /
NK034(ngi)003:3531: rnga dra ba rgyud mang la brten pas snang ba sna tshogs pa'i nyams skye /
NK034(ngi)003:3532: gling bu'i sgra la brten na shes pa gzhan la mi 'jug pa'i nyams skye /
NK034(ngi)003:3533: pi wang gi sgra rdo phag dang cha lang dang
NK034(ngi)003:3534: dung ting gi sgras rang bzhin du mi gnas dang
NK034(ngi)003:3535: / sgra'i dbyings kyi don rtogs te dape'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3536: don rna ba'i sgra ni sgra mngon sum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:3538: shing ka ra b+ai ra'i 'bras bu bdun zos nas nyal na /
NK034(ngi)003:3539: lha dang lha min gyi sgra thos so //
NK034(ngi)003:3540: sri shing gi 'bras bu'i nad phye dang zhim tse til dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3541: shing ka ra b+ai ra'i 'bras bu bdun gyi phye
NK034(ngi)003:3542: 'bru mar dang sbyar nas rna ba'i bug pa g.yas
NK034(ngi)003:3543: su blugs na dmyal ba'i sgra thos so //
NK034(ngi)003:3544: yang shing ka ra b+ai ra'i 'bras bu bdun dang shing ldem pa dang ma ha lde ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3545: 'brug rus kyi phye ma dang 'bru mar sbyar nas
NK034(ngi)003:3546: rna bug g.yon du blugs na yi dwags kyi sgra
NK034(ngi)003:3547: thos so // yang shing ka ra b+ai ra'i 'bras
NK034(ngi)003:3548: bu bdun dang rdo rje can gyi shing chu shing
NK034(ngi)003:3550: kha bral bre bo seng sdeng gi dbus snying gi
NK034(ngi)003:3551: rtse rnams 'bru mar dang sbyar nas rna ba gnyis
NK034(ngi)003:3552: kar blugs na byol song gi sgra thos so //
NK034(ngi)003:3553: gong gi sgra bzhi la slob pa'i dus su rdzas
NK034(ngi)003:3554: de lta bu dang sgra 'jug ldog gnas pa'i dus
NK034(ngi)003:3556: don cig char 'grub pa la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3557: dri ni gu gul dkar po rgya shug gi 'bras
NK034(ngi)003:3558: bu a ka ru'i phye ma dang ga bur gyi
NK034(ngi)003:3559: snying po dang / mu zi bya sgong gis brtul ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3560: shing byil pa'i rtsa ba nya'i klad pa 'ug pa'i mig /
NK034(ngi)003:3561: ri skegs kyi mjug rtse rma bya'i mgrin pa srin po'i sna'i rtse mor sbyar nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3562: ba glang pos zos te shi ba'i pho ba'i nang
NK034(ngi)003:3563: du blugs sbrang rgod khyor gang yang blugs spos sna
NK034(ngi)003:3564: tshogs kyi lo ma dang tsan+dana gyi lo mas byi
NK034(ngi)003:3565: bas la zhag bcu dgur mnan nas kha phye ba
NK034(ngi)003:3566: dang / sna'i rtse mor thig le gcig byas na
NK034(ngi)003:3567: bde ba dang mi rtog pa'i nyams skye ba la
NK034(ngi)003:3569: ro ni bu ram gyi shing smin pa sor bzhi bzhir gtubs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3570: sbrang rtsi'i snying po bre gang du btsos te them pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3571: til mar phul do btso de thon pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3572: rdo gtun nang du kha tshir byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3573: mar bzang po dang ga bur sran ma bdun dang mnyam pa gcig dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3574: mi rkang gdus pa'i snying po zho gnyis dang sbrang rgod phul gang til chang phul gang /
NK034(ngi)003:3575: de rnams dang chang sbyor ba yin te /
NK034(ngi)003:3576: rdza gsar pa phul dgu dgu shongs pa dgu byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3577: de nas 'bras btsos pa'i chang la phabs dang sbrang rgod zho gcig btab la de langs pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3578: rdza'i snod kha chung bar byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3580: khengs par byas la shing los kha bcad /
NK034(ngi)003:3581: de nas kha sas bcad de nas zhag nyi shu
NK034(ngi)003:3582: rtsa gcig na gcig gi nang du nas kyi chang
NK034(ngi)003:3583: bzang po dang / mi zhun rnying pa dang sbyar la blug /
NK034(ngi)003:3584: de nas de btsags la gcig tu bsre /
NK034(ngi)003:3585: de nas dgu'i mjug ma la de btsags pa phul gang 'ong ba byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3586: de phul phyed du gdu ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3587: gong ma rnams dang sbyar la /
NK034(ngi)003:3588: lce'i steng du thur mas lan nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bzhag na /
NK034(ngi)003:3589: nyi ma bdun gyi bar la ci yang yid la mi 'gyu ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3590: rang bzhin gyi bsam gtan la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3591: reg ni u rgyan gyi yul d+he ba res bya ba na /
NK034(ngi)003:3592: shing ma le kis bya ba lo ma g.yas su 'khyil ba zhig yod de /
NK034(ngi)003:3593: lo ma mthur du zug pa rtse mo gsum du gyes pa zhig yod /
NK034(ngi)003:3594: de blangs na de'i 'dab ma dang dom gyi snying
NK034(ngi)003:3595: khrag byugs te de rang gi snying khar sbyar na
NK034(ngi)003:3596: / de dang ma bral gyi bar du mi rtog pa rgyud la skye ba yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:3597: de ltar d+h+aa ki mtshan ldan dang rang nyid yo
NK034(ngi)003:3598: gis gcig la gcig lta ba ni gzugs kyi bde
NK034(ngi)003:3599: ba'o // rgod cing glu len pa ni sgra'i bde ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3600: tsan+dana dang du ru ka byugs nas snom res ni dri'i bde ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3601: bu ram dang ka ra mur res dang ster res dang lce 'jib res ni ro'i bde ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3602: khrus legs par byas te nu ma nyed res dang
NK034(ngi)003:3603: g.ya' dgag res dang pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru la mdzub gus
NK034(ngi)003:3604: reg reg dang / nor bu d+h+aa kis khas 'jib pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3605: g.yer ma dang sbrang rgod zer rgod gsum nor bu'i mgo la bskyon nas pad+mara bardzangasa na /
NK034(ngi)003:3606: ma 'gul kyang rang bzhin gyis reg pas bde ba 'ong ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3607: de'i phyir na gsang sngags pas 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la longs spyod nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3608: sgo lnga'i zhen pa log ste 'bras bu sangs rgyas pa yin pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3609: yab yum gnyis med kyi don la mkhas par bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3610: thig le ma shor bar bzung bas yum gyis thob 'agro'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3611: 'di kun gsang ba'i thabs yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:3613: 'di kun zhes pa 'dod yon lam du 'khyer ba'i chos /
NK034(ngi)003:3614: gsang ba'i zhes pa blo dman pa'i rigs la /
NK034(ngi)003:3615: thabs yin no zhes pa sgo lnga'i zhen pa dang bral te sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK034(ngi)003:3616: lam gyi rtags ni lus las ni //
NK034(ngi)003:3618: lam gyi zhes pa sangs rgya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3619: rtags ni zhes pa thun mong gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3620: lus las ni zhes pa rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3621: mngon par phyi rol snang 'gyur ba'i //
NK034(ngi)003:3624: phyi rol zhes pa lus kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3626: sman nyid dang ni de bzhin no //
NK034(ngi)003:3630: de bzhin no zhes pa las 'grub pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3631: de ltar 'dod pa brten pa'i yo gis lam gyi gnas 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bcad pa'i thabs ni /
NK034(ngi)003:3632: lan gcig la srin lag g.yon pa'i rtsa ba sre mo'i rgyus bas bacingasate /
NK034(ngi)003:3633: sbyor ba byas na 'khor ba 'phel mi srid do //
NK034(ngi)003:3634: gtan du bcad na tsan dan dkar po dang ti
NK034(ngi)003:3635: tsa dang gser nas tsam sbyangs pa'i g.ya' dang bsres
NK034(ngi)003:3636: la / skyes pa lto bkug nas tho rangs btung na /
NK034(ngi)003:3637: thig le nyams kyang 'khor ba 'phel mi srid do //
NK034(ngi)003:3638: ka ra zho gcig stag sha de dang mnyam pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3639: byang ba dug phyungs pa gsum rtsi bzhin du btags te /
NK034(ngi)003:3640: zhu mkhan chu phul gang la btab ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3641: bud med la lto stong la btang na /
NK034(ngi)003:3643: yang na ga bur gur kum rgya tshil rma bya'i snying rnams phye ma byas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3644: nor bu'i rtser byugs na thig le rdo rje'i bum
NK034(ngi)003:3645: par phyag rgya ma dang ma bral bar gnas pa
NK034(ngi)003:3646: yin no // 'o ma la lcags phye btab ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3647: nor bu'i bug par rdo khab len gyi ri lu
NK034(ngi)003:3648: bcug nas 'o ma la kha gtugs na 'o ma
NK034(ngi)003:3650: gnyer ma med par 'dod na mu tsi rta'i 'o
NK034(ngi)003:3651: mar btsos la de kham bu'i tshi gu'i mar dang
NK034(ngi)003:3652: rtsi mar dang ba dmar mo'i 'o ma dang bsres
NK034(ngi)003:3653: nas / lus dag par bkrus te rdzas khyab par
NK034(ngi)003:3654: phyugs shing btung na gzhon cing gnyer ma 'ong mi
NK034(ngi)003:3655: nas / srid do // skra dkar med par 'dod na /
NK034(ngi)003:3656: skra bzhar la dag par bkrus te a ru ra'i chu blug /
NK034(ngi)003:3657: de skam po dang nags mtshur chu blugs pas skra
NK034(ngi)003:3658: dkar nag por 'gyur ba la the tshom med do
NK034(ngi)003:3660: ma he'i dpral ba'i rus pa bya rgod kyi brun
NK034(ngi)003:3661: gyi dkar po cong zi 'brug rus rnams mnyam ste
NK034(ngi)003:3662: / rtsi bzhin btags la sbrang rtsi dang zho dang sbyar la ru sbal gyi khog par blugs la /
NK034(ngi)003:3663: gos kyis byibs te zhag bcu dgu mnan /
NK034(ngi)003:3664: de nas kha phye nas bltas pas dkar la gnag pa'i ri mo'am /
NK034(ngi)003:3666: yo gis zhag gsum du zas gzhan mi za bar 'o ma bskol ba btung ngo /
NK034(ngi)003:3667: de nas se'u shul du gong ma'i rdzas byug cing
NK034(ngi)003:3668: sbrang rtsis steng mnan de ltar yang yang byas na
NK034(ngi)003:3669: zla ba gcig na so'u skye'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3670: lo dus song tsa na rdzas byug cing /
NK034(ngi)003:3671: de'i steng du sbrang rtsi byug /
NK034(ngi)003:3672: de'i steng du zar ma'i mar byugs pas so dang
NK034(ngi)003:3673: so snying mkhregs shing mdog dang ldan par 'gyur ro
NK034(ngi)003:3674: // mtshan mo 'od 'phro zhing gos mi dgos par byed na /
NK034(ngi)003:3675: spyang tsher gyi rtse khrog chen gyi tshi ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3676: shug rtsi thang tshi rgya tsha ra tsha shang tsha dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3677: kha ru tsha lce myang tsha mu tshi /
NK034(ngi)003:3678: de cha mnyam pa rnams phye mar btags te /
NK034(ngi)003:3679: skyung ga'am bya mo nag mo'i sgo nga'i ser po dang tshi ba la btab ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3680: bag zan gyis dril la sla ngar mar nag phul gang de la thim par btso /
NK034(ngi)003:3681: de dang rdo sol ngar ldan gyi lcags phye dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3682: sbyar nas ras sam gos kyi thong ka la byugs na /
