NK034(ngi)003:3683: rlung phyogs sam phus gdab cing mchil ma btab na /
NK034(ngi)003:3684: 'od me bdun gyi tshad tsam du gsal zhing gos mi dgos te drod 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3685: 'tshigs pa tsam byung na sa nu'i chu blug go //
NK034(ngi)003:3686: ma shi ba dang shi ba'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:3688: mu tig dang mu men shel dngul chu ze tsha zho re sbyar te /
NK034(ngi)003:3689: rdza gsar ba'i nang du ra dkar mo'i 'o ma phul gang dang bcas te blugs la /
NK034(ngi)003:3690: kha legs par bcad la 'ba' chas gril te kham sas gril /
NK034(ngi)003:3691: yang na ba'i gci bas gril /
NK034(ngi)003:3692: de thab khung du bcug la sol ba spungs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3693: sbud pa gnyis kyis res mos bus /
NK034(ngi)003:3694: lan gsum du bsreg cing bltas pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3695: rtags ni lteng lteng mig gis mi bzod na phebs pa yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:3696: gal te de ltar ma byung na /
NK034(ngi)003:3697: star bu sran ma bdun dang mnyam pa blug /
NK034(ngi)003:3698: gong ltar bsregs pas gtan la phebs so //
NK034(ngi)003:3699: de nas gong ma'i rdzas dang ring bsrel khyi lud mes bsregs pa gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3700: sbyar nas rang gar 'dod par byugs pa dang mnyam par /
NK034(ngi)003:3701: de nas gdung yang de dang mnyam par 'brul lo //
NK034(ngi)003:3702: glang po che'i rus pa'am thod pa'am rus pa la gong ma'i sku bris te /
NK034(ngi)003:3704: yang na bse ru'i nang dang sbyar te /
NK034(ngi)003:3705: stag gi rkan phug sha chen dang sbyar nas byugs na mchod rten 'ong ngo //
NK034(ngi)003:3706: yang na yo gar 'dug pa'i chur tsha ba d+ha ka ta sha'i rtsa ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3707: ha shad phye ma rnams dang spos dkar sbyar te /
NK034(ngi)003:3708: chos 'chad dus na dud pa btang bas 'ja' tshon 'khrug cing 'jug par 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3709: yang na yo gi yis spru ma 'om bu seng ldeng dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3710: rgya shug tsan+dana lo ma dang lan tsh+wa bya rgod
NK034(ngi)003:3711: rkang mar rnams legs par sbyar nas rang gis lus
NK034(ngi)003:3712: la byugs na / dud 'gro'i tshogs rnams 'dus shing phyag dang bskor ba byed par 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3713: yo gis spyod pa rtsom pa'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:3714: ku ku ra tsa mi yong bar byed na /
NK034(ngi)003:3715: sbrang rgod bu ram 'bri'i klad pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3716: khyi sbyor ba byed pa'i dus su khyi mo'i stu bkab la phying pa slan te /
NK034(ngi)003:3717: de la khyi'i sa bon 'dzags pa rnams 'byar ba 'ong ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3718: de bkog la gong gi rdzas dang bsres nas sngags
NK034(ngi)003:3719: 'di stong tsho bzhi bzlas pa lus la cor cor
NK034(ngi)003:3720: du bsrel lo // tsa tsa tso tso /
NK034(ngi)003:3725: zhes bzlas te khyi byung ba dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3726: rang gi rkang pa'i 'og nas sa spar gang blangs te khyi'i phyogs su gtor ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3727: des ni khyi thams cad mjug ma bsil zhing 'dug par 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3728: ri la bsgom zhing lam 'grul skyel ma bya ba'i phyir /
NK034(ngi)003:3729: chom rkun jag pa 'ching ba ni /
NK034(ngi)003:3730: ba spru ba rang 'thag lte phye nyung dkar gsum bsres la /
NK034(ngi)003:3734: de nas dgra byung ba dang rdzas gtor cing sngags 'di bzlas so //
NK034(ngi)003:3739: is kro ta y+aa dan sod byas pas smra mi shes so //
NK034(ngi)003:3744: byas pas snying gi mi dran no //
NK034(ngi)003:3749: su tri yam zhes chu gtsang ma la btab ste jag pa la gtor na grol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:3750: yo gi la mtshon gyis mi chod par byed na /
NK034(ngi)003:3751: zhag bdun sngags 'di la rang lus mer bsgoms la bzlas so //
NK034(ngi)003:3755: dgos dus su sa gtsang ma la brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas te /
NK034(ngi)003:3757: dgra'i mtshon gyi phyogs su gtor na mtshon kha 'ching zhing phig par mi 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3758: yang yo gi du ru ka'i dmag dang mis mi mthong bar byed na /
NK034(ngi)003:3759: mun pa nag por bsgrubs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3760: skyes pa grir shi ba'i pags pa sha dang ro
NK034(ngi)003:3761: bsregs pa'i sbur nag gnyis rtsi bzhin du btags te
NK034(ngi)003:3762: / rwa nang du sngags 'dis zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig tu bsgrub bo //
NK034(ngi)003:3763: +amo na mo ru tri ya na mo /
NK034(ngi)003:3764: hi ri mi ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:3765: nam dgos pa'i dus su smin phrag la byugs na sus kyang mi mthong ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3766: slar phar 'joms nus par the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3770: 'jig rten zhes pa sor bzhag dang phyin ci log gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3771: drang don du zhes pa yang dag pa'i don la /
NK034(ngi)003:3772: skal ba can gyi spyod yul lo //
NK034(ngi)003:3774: skal ba zhes pa tshogs bsags pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3775: can gyi zhes pa tshe 'di la /
NK034(ngi)003:3776: spyod yul lo zhes pa mchog rang 'dod dang bral ba'i yo gi'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3777: 'di yi thabs ni sna tshogs pas //
NK034(ngi)003:3779: 'di yi zhes pa bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:3780: thabs ni zhes pa mchog dang thun mong gnyis ka'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3782: bla ma mtshan ldan dang e ka /
NK034(ngi)003:3783: rig ma mtshan ldan dang d+hu yi /
NK034(ngi)003:3784: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ring bsrel dang t+r+ai /
NK034(ngi)003:3785: skye ba bdun pa'i sha dang rtag tu ngu dang tsi ri /
NK034(ngi)003:3786: dum gcig b+han+d+ha bzang po dang pan tsa /
NK034(ngi)003:3787: dri med shel sgong dwangs po dang tsha tu /
NK034(ngi)003:3788: bstan pa'i rang btsas sangs rgyas sas gcig po dang tse na /
NK034(ngi)003:3789: de rnams 'dzom na nor bu dbang gi rgyal po yin pa dang tsha d+h+au /
NK034(ngi)003:3790: dmigs pa gang 'dod la gtad cing /
NK034(ngi)003:3791: gsol ba btab pa dang g+ha da /
NK034(ngi)003:3792: bsams pa yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i tshe h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:3795: bstan pa'i bu gcig thod par bzhugs su gsol /
NK034(ngi)003:3796: dar sna lngas gril la gang 'dod pa'i mchod pa
NK034(ngi)003:3797: 'bul zhing gsol ba btab ste tshar gsum gsung bsgrags
NK034(ngi)003:3798: na mi 'grub re ni na ra kan /
NK034(ngi)003:3799: sna tshogs pas zhes pa 'di la brten pa'i las tshogs thug pa med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3800: khyad par sems can gyi don du char 'bebs na
NK034(ngi)003:3801: 'brug shing nam mkha' ma mthong ba dang chu shing
NK034(ngi)003:3802: gnyis las phur pa sor bzhi las mi thung ba
NK034(ngi)003:3803: re byas te / de gnyis ras gtsang ma'i khug mar bcug ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3804: char 'bebs pa'i dus su dkon mchog dang mkha' 'gro
NK034(ngi)003:3805: dang chos skyong dang klu gtor rgyas par btang ste
NK034(ngi)003:3806: / phur pa gnyis la thag pa btags la nam
NK034(ngi)003:3807: mkha' ma mthong bar 'byung ba chu'i nyi ma dwangs
NK034(ngi)003:3808: / dus su / chu mig tu bcug nas gcig
NK034(ngi)003:3809: gis bstan pa'i bu gcig ral gri'i lce yis bklag
NK034(ngi)003:3810: / dus su / cing / gcig gis sbrul sha bsreg cing sngags 'di bzlas so //
NK034(ngi)003:3811: ha ri ni d+h+aa ki tsa ri char phob phob /
NK034(ngi)003:3812: kham kham n+aa ga ra tsa phan tsa b+ha ri sha ya phob phob /
NK034(ngi)003:3814: ches na phur pa bton te gong gi rang khug tu sbas pas chad do //
NK034(ngi)003:3815: gzhan gyi 'dod zhen mtha' dgag phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3817: gzhan gyi zhes pa theg pa thun mong ba /
NK034(ngi)003:3818: 'dod zhen zhes pa thun mong gi sgrub rtags kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3819: mtha' dgag phyir zhes pa sangs rgyas pa'i sngon du /
NK034(ngi)003:3820: rab tu gsang bar byung ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3822: rab tu zhes pa thun mong gi tshig tsam rlung phyogs tsam du yang /
NK034(ngi)003:3823: gsang bar zhes pa log lta can theg pa thun
NK034(ngi)003:3824: mong gi chos bdag can du ma gtogs pa rnams
NK034(ngi)003:3825: la / byung ba'o zhes pa ye gdod ma nas rang babs su chos nyid kyi rang sgrar ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3826: 'gro ba'i don du thun mong gi las bstan pa'i le'u ste lnga pa rdzogs so ////
NK034(ngi)003:3829: da ni le'u drug pa 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:3830: khams la bslab pa'i thabs yod pas //
NK034(ngi)003:3832: khams la zhes pa me rlung nam mkha'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3833: de dag thams cad 'dus pa byang sems dkar dmar ro //
NK034(ngi)003:3834: bslab pa'i zhes pa zung 'jug la /
NK034(ngi)003:3835: thabs yod pas zhes pa sangs rgya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3836: dran rdzogs phyag rgya'i ngang du sbyor //
NK034(ngi)003:3838: dran rdzogs zhes pa skad cig la /
NK034(ngi)003:3839: phyag rgya'i zhes pa las dam tshig chos phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3840: ngang du sbyor zhes pa dbugs la sleb cing btags pa tsam gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3841: dbang po'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3843: dbang po'i zhes pa sgo lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3844: zhen pa zhes pa rang rgyud pa ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3845: bzlog pa'i phyir zhes pa rigs lnga yum lngar /
NK034(ngi)003:3848: nyon mongs pa'i bdud rang sar dag par byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3849: phung po'i zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3851: phung po'i zhen pa zhes pa gzugs tshor ba 'du shes 'du byed rnam par shes pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3852: zhen pa zhes pa rang rgyud pa de /
NK034(ngi)003:3853: bzlog pa'i phyir zhes pa rigs lnga yab lnga /
NK034(ngi)003:3854: b+he ga ra na so gad gling //
NK034(ngi)003:3856: phung po'i bdud rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3857: yul kun zhen pa bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3859: yul kun zhes pa gzugs sgra dri ro reg go //
NK034(ngi)003:3860: zhen pa zhes pa rang rgyud pa de /
NK034(ngi)003:3861: bzlog pa'i phyir zhes pa zhing khams su /
NK034(ngi)003:3862: pu k+aa ri la b+ha d+hu tri //
NK034(ngi)003:3864: lha'i bu'i bdud rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3865: sems kyi dngos po spur ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3867: sems kyi zhes pa mi dran dgu dran 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:3868: dngos po zhes pa sku gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:3869: spur ba'i phyir zhes pa ka dag tu /
NK034(ngi)003:3870: ram pa ka la sa mi khye //
NK034(ngi)003:3872: 'chi bdag gi bdud rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3873: byung tshor gnas su gcod pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3875: byung tshor zhes pa bde sdug gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3876: gnas su zhes pa gzhi la /
NK034(ngi)003:3877: gcod pa'i phyir zhes pa dngos med du /
NK034(ngi)003:3878: ma tang phar pher ras mi ti //
NK034(ngi)003:3880: kun gzhi rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3881: 'dus tshogs snang ba ngos gzung phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3883: 'dus tshogs zhes pa 'khor 'das kyi chos ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3884: snang ba zhes pa mngon sum /
NK034(ngi)003:3885: ngos bzung phyir zhes pa rang snang du /
NK034(ngi)003:3886: ba da rek+ta sa mig rlung //
NK034(ngi)003:3888: rang snang rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3889: rig pa btson rar gzhug pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3891: rig pa zhes pa mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i rig pa mi dran dgu dran 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:3892: btson rar zhes pa gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:3893: gzhug pa'i phyir zhes pa zab pa'i gnad la brten nas /
NK034(ngi)003:3894: a ke ra na b+ha tseg sha /
NK034(ngi)003:3896: phyir mi ldog par byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3897: 'khrul pa'i rang rgyud khungs bcad phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3899: 'khrul pa'i zhes pa khams gsum gyisemasa can /
NK034(ngi)003:3900: rang rgyud ces pa dngos por 'dzin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:3901: khungs bcad phyir zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:3902: ya ri mu ta sa g+hu le //
NK034(ngi)003:3904: khams gsum rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3905: rigs drug rim gyis bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3908: rim gyis zhes pa gong nas gong ste /
NK034(ngi)003:3909: sdig can nyan thos rnams dang mnyam pas mngon no //
NK034(ngi)003:3910: bsgral ba'i phyir zhes pa 'khor ba las /
NK034(ngi)003:3911: ya sing ra rlung pa la ya //
NK034(ngi)003:3913: rigs drug rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3914: 'khor ba dong nas gdon pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3916: 'khor ba zhes pa ngan song gsum dang /
NK034(ngi)003:3917: dong nas zhes pa zhe 'jigs shing gting ring ba thon dus med pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3918: gdon pa'i phyir zhes pa byin brlabs rang babs 'dis /
NK034(ngi)003:3919: ma ma ko ling sa m+aa ta //
NK034(ngi)003:3921: ngan song dong nas sprug par byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3922: mi shi ba'i dus su yang rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor bzhengs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3923: snying po 'di dzab tu bgrang zhing /
NK034(ngi)003:3924: zhag drug la tshe 'das dmigs pas rim pa bzhin rigs drug las drangs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3925: bdun pa la 'od gsal gyi dkyil 'khor thig le chen po ltar bzhengs te /
NK034(ngi)003:3926: rdzogs pa rang byung gi lam bstan pa'i tshig rnams kyis ngo sprad pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3927: nam mkha' la 'aja'i tshogs 'khrugs shing tshe 'das grol ba la the tshom med do //
NK034(ngi)003:3928: chos can thur du gzhug pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3931: thur du zhes pa don 'gyur ba med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3932: gzhug pa'i phyir zhes pa thig le nyag gcig la /
NK034(ngi)003:3933: g+ha ring yam pa ri mam ti //
NK034(ngi)003:3935: yang dag don la skyel bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3936: rol pa'i byung khungs spur ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3937: rol pa'i zhes pa chos nyid kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3938: byung khungs zhes pa dang po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3939: spur ba'i phyir zhes pa nam mkha' la mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:3940: bu ga sing ha pha g+ha la //
NK034(ngi)003:3942: rang shar rang grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3943: zhen pa'i phreng thag gcad pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3945: zhen pa'i zhes pa 'khor ba las /
NK034(ngi)003:3947: gcad pa'i phyir zhes pa yul rig snang du /
NK034(ngi)003:3948: ra mi si pi khe ta pa //
NK034(ngi)003:3950: zhen yul dbyings su grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3951: lug rgyud ar la gtad pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3953: lug rgyud ces pa zung 'jug gnyis med du 'brel chags pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3954: ar la zhes pa yol sgrib med par /
NK034(ngi)003:3955: gtad pa'i phyir zhes pa nyams len gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:3956: bi khu ma la pa tam ki //
NK034(ngi)003:3958: nyams gong nas gong du 'phel zhing grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3959: lha yi phyag rgya lta ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3961: lha'i zhes pa rig sku rigs lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3963: lta ba'i phyir zhes pa mthong byed kyi rig pas /
NK034(ngi)003:3964: sa m+aa nyi ba d+he ra pa //
NK034(ngi)003:3966: rig pa tshad la phebs shing zhing khams shes byed kyi rig par grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3967: lta sgom log pa dag bya'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3969: lta sgom zhes pa mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i rig pa rig stong zung 'jug gi /
NK034(ngi)003:3971: dag bya'i phyir zhes pa ye bsrung chen po'i dam tshig gis /
NK034(ngi)003:3974: rdo rje sems dpa'i rig pa la rang rdzogs su grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3975: sa lam dus gcig gcad pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3977: sa lam zhes pa theg pa dgu'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3978: dus gcig ces pa don mthong ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3979: gcad pa'i phyir zhes pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:3980: g+he ba su g+har rna ma yee //
NK034(ngi)003:3982: sa lam chig rdzogs grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3983: yid dpyod lta ba khungs gcad phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3985: yid dpyod ces pa don ma rtogs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:3986: lta ba zhes pa rang bzhin gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:3987: khungs gcad phyir zhes pa rig pa'i rdo rje lu gu rgyud du /
NK034(ngi)003:3988: d+harma pa ti sa g+hu li //
NK034(ngi)003:3990: gol sa thams cad rang thog tu grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3991: sku gsum lam du blang ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:3993: sku gsum zhes pa chos sku longs sku sprul sku'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3994: lam du zhes pa lta sgom spyod pa'i dus su /
NK034(ngi)003:3995: blang ba'i phyir zhes pa rig pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:3996: ra smi sa m+aa kha rgad tshe //
NK034(ngi)003:3998: sku gsum lam du chod cing 'dzin pa rang sar grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:3999: snang ba dngos su blang ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:4001: snang ba zhes pa chos nyid mngon sum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4002: dngos su zhes pa yid dpyod ma yin par /
NK034(ngi)003:4003: blang ba'i phyir zhes pa rang snang lhun grub tu /
NK034(ngi)003:4004: ru pa sa mi mi ta lam //
NK034(ngi)003:4006: cer grol dus mnyam ma grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4007: sgra yi zhen pa mtha' gcad phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:4010: zhen pa zhes pa rang rgyud du /
NK034(ngi)003:4011: mtha' gcad phyir zhes pa brjod du med par /
NK034(ngi)003:4012: nga tig pa yam ka li sa //
NK034(ngi)003:4014: brjod med tshig 'das su grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4015: bsam gtan chen po'i sa gnon phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:4017: bsam gtan zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum la /
NK034(ngi)003:4018: chen po'i zhes pa gong na med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4019: sa non phyir zhes pa bcu drug rdzogs chen rang bzhin gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4020: ga tsha ba la sa i tam //
NK034(ngi)003:4022: sa lam chig chod la grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4023: phrin las mtha' ru dbyung ba'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:4025: phrin las zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4026: mtha' ru zhes pa tshe 'di'i mtha' dbugs chad pa dang /
NK034(ngi)003:4027: dbyung ba'i phyir zhes pa rtsol med lhun grub tu /
NK034(ngi)003:4028: karma e ka a nu sa //
NK034(ngi)003:4030: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi mdzad par grol ba'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4031: sangs rgyas mngon zhen bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:4033: sangs rgyas zhes pa 'khrul pa sangs pa'i bar ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4034: ye shes rgyas pa'i rang snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4035: mngon zhen zhes pa theg pa thun mong bas rang byung du ma shes te /
NK034(ngi)003:4036: yid bsgom bag chags kyis thob par 'dod pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:4037: bzlog pa'i phyir zhes pa sku gsum rang snang rang byung du /
NK034(ngi)003:4038: sang kri ma ma karma ta //
NK034(ngi)003:4040: sku gsum ka dag tu grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4041: rgyal sras rnams kyi gnas btsal phyir //
NK034(ngi)003:4043: rgyal sras zhes pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rigs 'dzin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4044: rnams kyi zhes pa zag bcas mi snang bar phung po lhag med du gshegs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4045: gnas btsal phyir zhes pa ngo bo skye ba med pa'i gnas ngos gzung dang bral /
NK034(ngi)003:4046: rang bzhin 'grib pa med pa'i gnas phyi nang dang bral /
NK034(ngi)003:4047: thugs rje 'gag pa med pa'i gnas nye ring dang bral ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4048: de gsum la 'dzin pa med pa'i gnas ka nas dag pa sems can rnams kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4049: nga la khe pa ki li sa //
NK034(ngi)003:4051: 'di nyid btags cing dbugs la sleb tshad grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4052: 'di kun rang shugs tshig tu byung //
NK034(ngi)003:4054: 'di kun zhes pa gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4055: rang shugs zhes pa stong rig ma 'gag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4056: tshig tu byung zhes pa sems can grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4057: zhes pa kun bzang yab yum gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4058: re res grol bar byed pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra thig le nyi shu rtsa lnga pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4059: +amo lus grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4060: +aahngaga grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4061: h+aum yid grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4062: lnga ldan rdo rje'i lte ba thig le mthing ka la bri'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4063: yab kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa ni /
NK034(ngi)003:4064: e ma ki r+ai ki r+ai /
NK034(ngi)003:4065: mas d+ha b+ha li b+aa li /
NK034(ngi)003:4066: sa mi ta su ru su ru /
NK034(ngi)003:4067: kun d+ha li ma su ma su /
NK034(ngi)003:4068: e ka ra su li b+has ta ye /
NK034(ngi)003:4069: tsa ki ra b+hu li ta lce ye /
NK034(ngi)003:4070: sa mun ta tsa ye su g+ha ye /
NK034(ngi)003:4071: b+hi ti las na b+ha g+hu li ye /
NK034(ngi)003:4072: sa ka ri d+hu ka ni /
NK034(ngi)003:4073: ma ta ri b+he te na /
NK034(ngi)003:4074: pa ra li hi sa na /
NK034(ngi)003:4075: ma khar te ke la na sam /
NK034(ngi)003:4076: sam b+hu ra ta me ka tsa ra tam pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4077: u rgya g+ha ta ra e pa sha na /
NK034(ngi)003:4078: na ra b+hi hi sa g+hu ti pa y+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:4079: g+hu ra g+hu ra pha ga kha ra na la ma /
NK034(ngi)003:4080: na ra na r+aa i thar sa da lam /
NK034(ngi)003:4081: sir na sir na b+he sa b+he sa ras pa la /
NK034(ngi)003:4082: b+hud+d+ha b+hud+d+ha b+hud tshi sha sa kye lam /
NK034(ngi)003:4090: gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud du grol bar byed pa'i snying po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4091: tshig bar nyi shu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4092: yum kun tu bzang mo'i dgongs pa ni /
NK034(ngi)003:4094: sa mi ta su ru su ru /
NK034(ngi)003:4096: i ki ri li b+hi ta ye /
NK034(ngi)003:4097: tsa ka b+hu li ta lce ye /
NK034(ngi)003:4098: sa mun ta tsar+ya su g+ha y+ae /
NK034(ngi)003:4099: b+hi ti san b+ha na g+hu y+ae /
NK034(ngi)003:4101: d+ha ka ma h+aa b+ho re /
NK034(ngi)003:4102: ta na pa ra pa li d+hi /
NK034(ngi)003:4103: san khar ta ke la na sam b+hu d+ha ra ta /
NK034(ngi)003:4104: e ka tsa ra sa b+ha sa tam /
NK034(ngi)003:4105: ta pa sur+ya g+ha ta ra a /
NK034(ngi)003:4108: ma smin pa g+hu ti la /
NK034(ngi)003:4109: ta ya g+hu ra g+hu ra /
NK034(ngi)003:4110: rlangs ga kha ba ra na lam /
NK034(ngi)003:4112: e tha ra pa ta lam /
NK034(ngi)003:4113: sirna sirna b+he sa ra sa pa lam /
NK034(ngi)003:4121: mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i rig pa 'gyu stong cing med
NK034(ngi)003:4122: du grol bar byed pa'i snying po tshig bar nyi
NK034(ngi)003:4124: gnyis thig le'i dbyings la bri'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4125: longs sku zhi khro'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4127: rigs drug klong du grol bar byed pa'i snying po thig le drug pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4128: sprul sku 'gag pa med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4136: am +aah skye ba med par grol bar byed pa'i snying po tshig bar brgyad pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4144: k+shah 'gag pa med par grol bar byed pa'i snying po tshig bar brgyad pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4145: bstan pa thams cad mi 'gyur ba'i dgongs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4146: ye d+har+m+aa he tu pra b+h+aa ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4148: sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba data /
NK034(ngi)003:4149: tesh+aany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e bam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:4150: gnas pa rgyun du grol bar byed pa'i snying po tshig bar bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4151: de ltar 'ja' tshon lha sku ring bsrel gyi snying
NK034(ngi)003:4152: po mi 'dra ba brgyad po la phrin las mtha'
NK034(ngi)003:4153: rgyas shing sham bu ni nad dang gdon dang 'jigs
NK034(ngi)003:4154: pa brgyad dang / sgrib pa thams cad rig par zhi ba sh+aan tim ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:4155: tshe dang bsod nams dang zhing khams thams cad rig
NK034(ngi)003:4156: par rgyas par gyur cig push+tim ku ru ye s+w+aa
NK034(ngi)003:4157: h+aa / dgra bgegs dang sangs rgyas dang chos dang
NK034(ngi)003:4158: dge 'dun dang 'khor 'das rig pa'i dbang du sdus
NK034(ngi)003:4159: shig p+aa sham ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:4160: dug lnga dug gsum rig pa'i ngang du m+aa ra ya sod sod s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:4161: zhes pa dang ye shes rnam pa lngas bskor ba ni gzhi mi 'gyur ba'i thig le chen po'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4162: zhes btags pas grol ba'i snying po bstan pa'i le'u ste drug pa rdzogs ////
NK034(ngi)003:4163: da ni le'u bdun pa 'grol te /
NK034(ngi)003:4164: e ma hoh zhes pa'i don ni /
NK034(ngi)003:4165: e zhes pa chos sku 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4166: ma zhes pa longs sku 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4167: hohzhesa pa sprul sku 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4169: de ltar 'dus ma byas kyi rang sgra 'dus ma byas pas ngo mtshar che'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4170: bcom pa dang ni ldan pa dang //
NK034(ngi)003:4172: bcom pa zhes pa ma rig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4173: dang ni zhes pa dug lnga dug gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:4174: ldan pa dang zhes pa sku gsum ye shes lnga dang /
NK034(ngi)003:4175: 'das pa yang dag lam yin no //
NK034(ngi)003:4177: 'das pa zhes pa ma rig pa las /
NK034(ngi)003:4178: yang dag ces pa rig pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4179: lam yin no zhes pa ka dag gi /
NK034(ngi)003:4180: 'di tshig lam min gdams pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4182: 'di tshig ces pa sangs rgyas gcig pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4183: lam min zhes pa da bsgrub dgos pa lta bu min pas so //
NK034(ngi)003:4184: gdams pa yin zhes pa gsum 'dus ma byas 'phrad pas chog pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4185: bstan cing bshad med brjod ma yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4187: bstan cing zhes pa dngos por /
NK034(ngi)003:4189: brjod ma yin zhes pa ston pa gang gis kyang /
NK034(ngi)003:4190: gdams pa ma yin byin rlabs yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4192: gdams pa zhes pa sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4193: ma yin zhes pa dang po nas /
NK034(ngi)003:4194: byin rlabs yin zhes pa 'dus ma byas pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4195: bris shing bkod med rang byung yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4197: bris shing zhes pa yi ge ris su /
NK034(ngi)003:4198: bkod med ces pa gang zag gis /
NK034(ngi)003:4199: rang byung yin zhes pa sangs rgyas sgam pos ma mdzad /
NK034(ngi)003:4200: sems can sgrin pos ma bcos te byas pa med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4201: gnas dang dus med sngon thog yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4203: gnas dang zhes pa gong du /
NK034(ngi)003:4204: dus med ces pa 'das ma 'ongs da lta gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:4205: sngon thog yin zhes pa dran pa kun gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4206: chos med snying po thugs gsang yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4208: chos med zhes pa ston pas gsungs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4209: snying po zhes pa bstan pa thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4210: thugs gsang yin zhes pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4211: sus kyang nyan med rang shar yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4213: sus kyang zhes pa phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4214: nyan med ces pa rna ba'i dbang pos /
NK034(ngi)003:4215: rang shar yin zhes pa thig le nyag gcig tu /
NK034(ngi)003:4216: thos pa med cing rang bsgrags yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4218: thos pa zhes pa rna ba'i dbang pos /
NK034(ngi)003:4219: med cing zhes pa 'byung bzhi rang sdeb kyi sgra /
NK034(ngi)003:4220: rang bsgrags yin zhes pa sgra 'dus ma byas chos nyid mngon sum mo //
NK034(ngi)003:4221: byas pas 'di kun ma yin tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:4223: byas pas zhes pa yid dpyod tshig gis bshad mi shes so //
NK034(ngi)003:4224: 'di kun zhes pa bstan pa thams cad kyi bu gcig po'i tshig /
NK034(ngi)003:4225: ma yin tshig ces pa 'dus ma byas /
NK034(ngi)003:4228: 'di yod ces pa chos nyid kyi rang sgra /
NK034(ngi)003:4229: 'dus ma byas sangs rgyas sras gcig po /
NK034(ngi)003:4231: sangs rgyas yin zhes pa ma bral gong reg pas grol ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4232: ba mo la nyi ma phog pa lta bus /
NK034(ngi)003:4233: pha rol mthong ba'i gsang chen lam //
NK034(ngi)003:4235: pha rol zhes pa 'khrul snang rang 'gags la sa
NK034(ngi)003:4236: rdo ri brag rtsi shing nags tshal skye shi bor
NK034(ngi)003:4237: len 'dis / mthong ba'i zhes pa sku gsum ye rdzogs ye shes lnga ldan gyi snang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4238: gsang chen lam zhes pa ma bsgoms rgyud btags pa'i
NK034(ngi)003:4239: byin rlabs kyis yon tan rang babs su byung ba
NK034(ngi)003:4240: nam zla dros pa lta bu'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4241: sems yod ma yin sprul pa yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4243: sems yod ces pas zin med pa'i 'gro ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4244: yod pa la med par sems /
NK034(ngi)003:4245: med pa la yod par sems 'dus byas 'jig pa'i chos can /
NK034(ngi)003:4246: ma yin zhes pa rgyud 'di yod pa'i skal ba can te /
NK034(ngi)003:4247: sprul pa yin zhes pa 'dus ma byas kun bzang yab yum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4250: 'khor ba'i zhes pa khams gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:4251: spyi mdud ces pa gzung 'dzin gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:4252: grol ba'o zhes pa rgyud 'dis dbugs la sleb pa
NK034(ngi)003:4253: tsam gyis mun khung du mar me bteg pa'am mkha'
NK034(ngi)003:4254: la nyi ma shar ba ltar /
NK034(ngi)003:4255: shes bya ma yin lam sna thag /
NK034(ngi)003:4257: shes bya zhes pa yid dpyod kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4259: lam sna thag ces pa rgyud 'di 'phrad pa dang lam bsgrod pa dus mnyam pas so //
NK034(ngi)003:4260: stong pa ma yin mngon sum yul //
NK034(ngi)003:4262: stong pa zhes pa cang med chad lta /
NK034(ngi)003:4264: mngon sum yul zhes pa sku gsum yid dpyod la rag ma lus pas /
NK034(ngi)003:4265: yod med ma yin thabs gsang ba //
NK034(ngi)003:4267: yod med ces pa rtag chad gnyis /
NK034(ngi)003:4269: thabs gsang ba zhes pa btags grol mthong grol ltas grol rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:4270: lha med 'di la sngags yod min //
NK034(ngi)003:4272: lha med ces pa blos byas yid bsgom gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4274: sngags yod min zhes pa ming brjod yi ge dang bral bas bzlas pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4275: pha rol phyin pa drug gi gzhi //
NK034(ngi)003:4277: pha rol zhes pa rtsol byas drug gi /
NK034(ngi)003:4278: phyin pa zhes pa rtsol med /
NK034(ngi)003:4279: drug gi gzhi zhes pa sku gsum rang chas kyi sbyin pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4280: 'od lnga dri med kyi tshul khrims /
NK034(ngi)003:4281: nyon mongs rang grol gyi bzod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4283: 'gyu ba dngos med kyi bsam gtan /
NK034(ngi)003:4284: chos zad ka dag gi shes rab bo //
NK034(ngi)003:4285: bsnyen gnas la sogs 'di tshul lo //
NK034(ngi)003:4287: bsnyen gnas zhes pa lus ngag yid gsum dkon mchog gsum la bsnyen pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4288: sku gsum 'du 'bral med pa la gnas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4289: la sogs zhes pa nyis brgya lnga bcu'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4291: de bzhin du yang bye brag smra //
NK034(ngi)003:4293: de bzhin zhes pa tshul gyi dbye ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4295: bye brag smra zhes pa nyan thos pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4296: don dam kun rdzob gzugs kyis so //
NK034(ngi)003:4298: don dam zhes pa don dam gyi don dam dang kun rdzob kyi don dam mo //
NK034(ngi)003:4299: kun rdzob ces pa kun rdzob kyi kun rdzob dang kun rdzob kyi don dam mo //
NK034(ngi)003:4300: gzugs kyis so zhes pa snod bcud gnyis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4301: rgyud kyi rtsa ba 'di nyid rang //
NK034(ngi)003:4303: rgyud kyi zhes pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4304: rtsa ba zhes pa thams cad kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4305: 'di nyid rang zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:4308: lha yi zhes pa phyi nang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:4309: rnal 'byor zhes pa bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4310: 'di sngags yin zhes pa ma bzlas pa'i srog /
NK034(ngi)003:4311: lung chen rnams kyi dam pa 'di //
NK034(ngi)003:4313: lung chen zhes pa mdo rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:4314: rnams kyi zhes pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4315: dam pa 'di zhes pa snying po /
NK034(ngi)003:4316: chos rnams ro gcig 'dres pa'i rten //
NK034(ngi)003:4318: chos rnams zhes pa theg pa dgu'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4319: ro gcig ces pa sku gsum du /
NK034(ngi)003:4320: 'dres pa'i rten zhes pa gnyis med spang blang med par /
NK034(ngi)003:4321: sku gsung thugs kyi dbye ba yis //
NK034(ngi)003:4323: sku gsung zhes pa mdun rgyab tu med par rang gsal brjod du med par chad pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4324: thugs kyi zhes pa 'khrul ma myong ba'i dngos med do //
NK034(ngi)003:4325: dbye ba yis zhes pa snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad la /
NK034(ngi)003:4326: bla med 'khor lo bskor ba'i gnas //
NK034(ngi)003:4328: bla med ces pa gsang ba /
NK034(ngi)003:4329: 'khor lo zhes pa sku gsum gyi chos /
NK034(ngi)003:4330: bskor ba'i gnas zhes pa sku bzhi'i ye shes lnga'i ra bas /
NK034(ngi)003:4331: dbang po rnams kyi dmigs gtad yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4334: rnams kyi zhes pa 'gro ba ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4335: dmigs gtad yin zhes pa 'phyugs so med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4336: shes rab rnams kyi rtogs pa'i gnas //
NK034(ngi)003:4338: shes rab ces pa yang dag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4339: rnams kyi zhes pa gcod byed sgrol byed 'byed byed 'du byed la sogs pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4340: rtogs pa'i gnas zhes pa sku gsum lhun grub tu /
NK034(ngi)003:4341: sku gsum lam du slong ba'i rten //
NK034(ngi)003:4343: sku gsum zhes pa chos sku skye ma myongs pas mtha' dang bral /
NK034(ngi)003:4344: longs sku 'grib ma myongs pas zhi khror gsal /
NK034(ngi)003:4345: sprul sku 'gag ma myongs pas kun la khyab /
NK034(ngi)003:4346: lam du zhes pa skal ba can gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:4347: slong ba'i rten zhes pa mngon sum du /
NK034(ngi)003:4348: thig le mngon du 'byin pa'i mig /
NK034(ngi)003:4350: thig le zhes pa sku gsum lhun grub kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4351: mngon du zhes pa dbang po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4352: 'byin pa'i mig ces pa cer mthong sangs rgyas su /
NK034(ngi)003:4353: thar ba'i skas kun slong bar byed //
NK034(ngi)003:4355: thar pa'i zhes pa khams gsum las /
NK034(ngi)003:4356: skas kun zhes pa sku gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4357: slong bar byed ces pa 'khor 'das rang dwangs su /
NK034(ngi)003:4358: lam du 'jug pa'i sa mkhan yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4360: lam du zhes pa yang dag pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4361: 'jug pa'i zhes pa 'gro ba sems can rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:4362: sa mkhan yin zhes pa ma nor bar byed pa ste /
NK034(ngi)003:4363: gzhi ma nor ba ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum /
NK034(ngi)003:4364: lam ma nor ba sgron ma bzhi /
NK034(ngi)003:4365: 'bras bu ma nor ba sku gsum 'dzin zad ka nas dag go //
NK034(ngi)003:4366: skal ldan 'dzin pa'i lcags kyur snang //
NK034(ngi)003:4368: skal ldan zhes pa sangs rgya ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4369: 'dzin pa'i zhes pa btags pa tsam gyis /
NK034(ngi)003:4370: lcags kyur snang zhes pa byin rlabs mngon du /
NK034(ngi)003:4371: chos sku rang 'jog gnas lugs yin //
NK034(ngi)003:4373: chos sku zhes pa thig le nyag gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:4374: rang 'jog ces pa sems can kun la che chung med par /
NK034(ngi)003:4375: gnas lugs yin zhes pa ye gdod ma nas /
NK034(ngi)003:4376: sangs rgyas kun gyis phyag byed gnas //
NK034(ngi)003:4378: sangs rgyas zhes pa sku gsum lam du sangs nas 'bras bu ka dag tu rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4379: kun gyi zhes pa 'das ma 'ongs da ltar /
NK034(ngi)003:4380: phyag byed gnas zhes pa sangs rgyas sras gcig po 'di /
NK034(ngi)003:4381: yul rnams gcod pa'i ral grir snang //
NK034(ngi)003:4383: yul rnams zhes pa dbang po sgo lnga'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4384: gcod pa'i zhes pa rang sar /
NK034(ngi)003:4385: ral grir snang zhes pa reg gcod btags pas grol ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4386: grol ba rnams ni 'di nyid la //
NK034(ngi)003:4388: grol ba zhes pa mthar thug yang dag par /
NK034(ngi)003:4389: rnams ni zhes pa zhing khams rang dag tu sangs rgyas pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4390: 'di nyid la zhes pa rgyud bstan pa'i bu gcig /
NK034(ngi)003:4391: rnam par brten nas grol ba'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4393: rnam par zhes pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4394: brten nas zhes pa 'gro ba sems can rnams /
NK034(ngi)003:4395: grol ba'o zhes pa ka dag tu /
NK034(ngi)003:4396: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bu gcig po //
NK034(ngi)003:4398: sangs rgyas zhes pa ma rig pa sangs rig pa ye shes su rgyas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4399: thams cad kyi zhes pa 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gyi sangs rgyas /
NK034(ngi)003:4400: bu gcig po zhes pa bstan pa 'phel bar byed pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4401: bstan pa rnams kyi btsas su rang byung ba //
NK034(ngi)003:4403: bstan pas zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4404: rnams kyi zhes pa mdo rgyud /
NK034(ngi)003:4405: btsas su zhes pa phyis kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4406: rang byung ba zhes ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum las /
NK034(ngi)003:4407: rang byung gi yi ge chen por bskal pa kun gyi thog mar rang byung /
NK034(ngi)003:4409: rang byung gi zhes pa chos nyid rang sgras sus kyang byas pa med pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4410: yi ge zhes pa gdul bya so so rang rang gi /
NK034(ngi)003:4411: chen por zhes pa lhun gyis grub pa'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4412: bskal pa zhes pa grangs las 'das pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4413: kun gyi zhes pa ma lus pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4414: thog mar zhes pa dang po /
NK034(ngi)003:4415: rang byung zhes pa ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje las /
NK034(ngi)003:4416: byin brlabs las rang bkod pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4418: byin brlabs zhes pa sku gsum gyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4419: rang bkod pa zhes pa yi ge rigs ni gcig pa tha dad du /
NK034(ngi)003:4420: sprul pa sku'i sa bon 'phel bar byed pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4422: sprul zhes pa sangs rgyas kyi /
NK034(ngi)003:4423: sku'i zhes pa bstan pa'i bdag po'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4424: sa bon zhes pa rgyu sems can la /
NK034(ngi)003:4427: byed pa zhes pa rgyud sangs rgyas sras gcig po 'di dngos so //
NK034(ngi)003:4430: rab tu zhes pa 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du /
NK034(ngi)003:4431: dkon pa'i tshig ces pa skal ba can 'ga' tsam ma gtogs pa /
NK034(ngi)003:4432: su dag dang 'phrad par mi 'gyur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:4433: zhes rgyud 'dus ma byas par bstan pa'i le'u ste bdun pa rdzogs so ////
NK034(ngi)003:4437: las zad skal ldan sems kyi bu //
NK034(ngi)003:4438: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK034(ngi)003:4439: thun mong man ngag bsam 'das kyang //
NK034(ngi)003:4440: mchog gi man ngag sras gcig po //
NK034(ngi)003:4441: 'di las zab pa zhing khams ni //
NK034(ngi)003:4442: mtha' med dag na yod re kan //
NK034(ngi)003:4443: des na dga' rab brgyud par bcas //
NK034(ngi)003:4444: yang dag mngon sangs rgya bar 'gyur //
NK034(ngi)003:4445: ci phyir rig pa dngos kyi gnad //
NK034(ngi)003:4446: 'di la yod do sa m+aa ya //
NK034(ngi)003:4447: sngags srung rgyal mo lnga la gtad //
NK034(ngi)003:4448: skal ldan rnams dang 'phrad par shog /
NK034(ngi)003:4449: le'u re la gtor tshogs re //
NK034(ngi)003:4450: bla ma yi dam sngags srung mchod //
NK034(ngi)003:4451: spros bcas dang ni spros pa med //
NK034(ngi)003:4452: shin tu spros med rab spros med //
NK034(ngi)003:4453: dbang bzhi dag ni ma thob par //
NK034(ngi)003:4454: bstan cing bshad par mi bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4455: rgyud rgyal sangs rgyas sras gcig gi //
NK034(ngi)003:4457: khams gsum sems can gnas dag nas //
NK034(ngi)003:4458: sku gsum ka nas dag gyur cig /
NK034(ngi)003:4459: bstan pa'i bu gcig 'di med na //
NK034(ngi)003:4460: bsgrubs kyang yun ring don med 'gyangs //
NK034(ngi)003:4461: des na 'di nyid mthing shun la //
NK034(ngi)003:4462: ston pa'i kha dog gser gyis 'bri //
NK034(ngi)003:4463: yig mgo ma log dar snas dril //
NK034(ngi)003:4464: spyi bo mgrin pa snying gar bcang //
NK034(ngi)003:4465: de nyid grol bar the tshom med //
NK034(ngi)003:4466: thig le chen bo'i btags grol ni //
NK034(ngi)003:4467: mthing shun bre zhabs lhag tsam la //
NK034(ngi)003:4468: dngul lam mtshal gyis mu khyud ni //
NK034(ngi)003:4469: thig le dape'u chung lta bur bskor //
NK034(ngi)003:4470: dbus su lnga ldan rdo rje 'bri //
NK034(ngi)003:4471: phyi rim mu khyud ye shes lnga //
NK034(ngi)003:4472: snying po gser gyis 'bri bar bya //
NK034(ngi)003:4473: btags grol 'dus pa thig le che //
NK034(ngi)003:4474: dbyings gsum rig pa'i mthongs na gsal //
NK034(ngi)003:4475: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs las phyung //
NK034(ngi)003:4476: dga' rab rdo rje bdag gis go //
NK034(ngi)003:4477: de la rab tu gnas pa ni //
NK034(ngi)003:4478: tshes brgyad rgyal 'dzom dus na bya //
NK034(ngi)003:4479: yang na zla stong dag la'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4480: thig le chen pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK034(ngi)003:4481: nas kyi tshom bu bkod pa la //
NK034(ngi)003:4482: bla ma rigs lnga yab yum bskyed //
NK034(ngi)003:4483: tshogs dang gtor ma mchod pa 'bul //
NK034(ngi)003:4484: bgegs gtor btang la gsol ba gdab //
NK034(ngi)003:4485: thig le chen po'i snying po rnams //
NK034(ngi)003:4486: bargya'am nyi shu rtsa gcig gdon //
NK034(ngi)003:4487: bkra shis brjod cing me tog gtor //
NK034(ngi)003:4488: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rab 'dus nas //
NK034(ngi)003:4489: btags grol 'od lnga'i gong bu yi //
NK034(ngi)003:4490: rigs lnga tshom bu nyid du bsgom //
NK034(ngi)003:4491: de ni rab tu gnas pa'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4492: de nas skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dang //
NK034(ngi)003:4493: dge bsnyen sdom pa dpog par bya //
NK034(ngi)003:4494: sdom med rnams la mi dgos so //
NK034(ngi)003:4495: de nas rgyud de tshar gcig bklag /
NK034(ngi)003:4496: de nas skal ldan de nyid kyis //
NK034(ngi)003:4497: phyag ni brgya rtsa btsal bya zhing //
NK034(ngi)003:4498: gser gyi man+dala lan dgu dbul //
NK034(ngi)003:4499: rgyud dang thig le spyi bor bzhag /
NK034(ngi)003:4500: de las 'od byung snod bcud gang //
NK034(ngi)003:4501: tshig 'dis gsol gdab dbang bskur ro //
NK034(ngi)003:4502: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig pos /
NK034(ngi)003:4504: lus byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK034(ngi)003:4510: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par byin gyis brlab tu gsol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:4511: g+ha dza k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK034(ngi)003:4512: de nas rgyud nyid mgrin par bzhag /
NK034(ngi)003:4513: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig pos /
NK034(ngi)003:4515: ngag byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK034(ngi)003:4517: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par byin gyis brlab tu gsol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:4518: g+ha tsa w+aaka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah de nas rgyud snying khar bzhag /
NK034(ngi)003:4519: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig pos /
NK034(ngi)003:4521: yid byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK034(ngi)003:4523: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs dang gnyis su med par byin gyis brlab tu gsol lo //
NK034(ngi)003:4524: d+har+m+aa tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK034(ngi)003:4525: de nas rgyud nyid lte bar bzhag /
NK034(ngi)003:4526: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig pos bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i /
NK034(ngi)003:4527: lus ngag yid gsum byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK034(ngi)003:4533: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK034(ngi)003:4534: phrin las dang bcas pas byin gyis brlab tu gsol
NK034(ngi)003:4535: lo // k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta d+har+m+aa karma a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK034(ngi)003:4536: de nas thig le'i snying po rnams tshar gsum bklag go //
NK034(ngi)003:4537: de nas gnas bzhir dbang bskur te //
NK034(ngi)003:4538: dpon slob gnyis kyi tshig 'di nyid //
NK034(ngi)003:4539: lan gsum brjod la dar snas dril //
NK034(ngi)003:4540: drod dang ma bral bcang bar bya //
NK034(ngi)003:4541: phyogs bcu'i bla ma sangs rgyas rnams //
NK034(ngi)003:4542: ma lus brtse bas dgongs su gsol //
NK034(ngi)003:4543: bdag gis sems can don du ni //
NK034(ngi)003:4544: rgyud btags 'di bzhugs byin rlabs kyis //
NK034(ngi)003:4545: bdag mthong thos dang dran pa dang //
NK034(ngi)003:4546: mchod dang bstod dang smra yang rung //
NK034(ngi)003:4547: reg par gyur ba'i sems can rnams //
NK034(ngi)003:4548: myur du mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK034(ngi)003:4549: bslab bya ni 'di dbugs la sleb dgos pas rbab
NK034(ngi)003:4550: dang chu dang 'chi ba'i rkyen dang gar 'chi cha
NK034(ngi)003:4551: med pas ma bral bar bcang bar bya'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4552: 'di btags nas dge ba ci byas pa brjod las 'das par 'phel bas /
NK034(ngi)003:4553: dge ba'i las grub tshad sems can gyi don du byed par gal che'o //
NK034(ngi)003:4554: 'di btags nas sdig pa bsags na yang brjod las
NK034(ngi)003:4555: 'das par 'phel 'gro bas shin tu 'dzem pa gal
NK034(ngi)003:4556: che'o // 'di nyid bzhugs pa'i skal ba can de
NK034(ngi)003:4557: ni sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i mchod rten du
NK034(ngi)003:4558: che'o // rigs par bya'o // skabs skabs su dri zhim po yang 'thul bar byed do //
NK034(ngi)003:4559: de ni lha dang mkha' 'gro mas mchod par yong ba yin pas /
NK034(ngi)003:4561: rab tu gsang ba'i man ngag skal ldan gyi tsit+tara d+ha thim /
NK034(ngi)003:4562: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rjes mdzad pa sras gcig rgyud kyi 'grel pa rdzogs so ////
